  <para style="h">Jenesis</para>
  <para style="toc1">Jenesis</para>
  <para style="toc2">Jenesis</para>
  <para style="toc3">Jen</para>
  <para style="mt1">Jenesis</para>
  <para style="mt4">(Mosis dere ya nʼafọ 1450–1410 tupu a mụọ Kraịst)</para>
  <para style="imt">Ihe dị nʼime ya</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ihe dị nʼime ya:</para>
  <para style="im">E dere ihe dị nʼakwụkwọ Jenesis maka ịkọwa otu ihe niile siri malite. A kọwara na ọ bụ Chineke kere eluigwe niile na ụwa, kọwaa na e kere mmadụ nʼoyiyi Chineke, meekwa ya ka ọ nọdụ nʼebe dị nnọọ mma. A kọwara otu mmehie si bata nʼụwa, na otu Chineke si gbooro mmadụ mehiere megide iwu Onye kere ya mkpa nzọpụta. Nʼime akwụkwọ a, a ga-agụta otu ibi obi ndị mmadụ si malite, otu ọrụ ǹka niile si bido, na otu asụsụ dị iche iche si malitekwa. A ga-agụta ebe mba dị iche iche si pụta. Akwụkwọ a kọkwara akụkọ banyere mba ndị Juu, otu o si bido site nʼaka Ebraham, Aịzik na Jekọb, kọwaakwa otu ndị Juu si biri nʼala Ijipt.</para>
  <para style="iot">Usoro e si dee ya:</para>
  <para style="io1">Okike eluigwe na ụwa <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 1-2">1–2</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Nnupu isi na mmalite mmehie <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 3-4">3–4</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Akụkọ gbasara ibi ndụ ndị mmadụ ruo nʼoge uju mmiri <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 5-9">5–9</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Mgbasa ụmụ mmadụ nʼelu ụwa <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 10-11">10–11</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Akụkọ ndụ Ebraham <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 12:1-25:18">12:1–25:18</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Akụkọ ndụ Aịzik <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 25:19-26:35">25:19–26:35</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Akụkọ ndụ Jekọb na Ịsọ <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 27:1-37:1">27:1–37:1</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Akụkọ ndụ Josef <char style="ior"><ref loc="GEN 37:2-50:26">37:2–50:26</ref></char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="GEN 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Mmalite ihe niile</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 1:1"/>Na mmalite Chineke kere eluigwe na ụwa. <verse eid="GEN 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 1:2"/>Ụwa bụ ihe na-enweghị ụdịdị ọbụla, bụrụkwa ihe tọgbọrọ nʼefu. Ọchịchịrị gbara nʼelu ogbu mmiri dị omimi. Mmụọ nke Chineke na-erugharị nʼelu ogbu mmiri ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 1:3"/>Mgbe ahụ Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka ìhè dị,” ìhè dịkwara. <verse eid="GEN 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 1:4"/>Chineke hụrụ na ìhè ahụ mara mma. Ọ kpara oke nʼetiti ìhè na ọchịchịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 1:5"/>Chineke kpọrọ ìhè ahụ Ehihie, kpọọ ọchịchịrị ahụ Abalị. Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke mbụ.<verse eid="GEN 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 1:6"/>Chineke kwukwara sị, “Ka mbara pụta nke ga-ekewapụ mmiri dị nʼelu mbara ahụ site na mmiri nke dị nʼokpuru mbara ahụ” <verse eid="GEN 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 1:7"/>Ya mere, Chineke mere mbara, kewapụ mmiri dị nʼokpuru mbara ahụ site na mmiri nke dị nʼelu mbara ahụ. O sikwa otu a dịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 1:8"/>Mbara ahụ ka Chineke kpọrọ mbara eluigwe. Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke abụọ.<verse eid="GEN 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 1:9"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka mmiri dị nʼokpuru mbara eluigwe chịkọta onwe ha ọnụ nʼotu ebe, ka ala akọrọ pụta.” O sikwa otu a dịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 1:10"/>Chineke kpọrọ ala akọrọ ahụ “ala,” kpọọ mmiri ahụ chịkọtara onwe ha ọnụ “osimiri.” Chineke lere anya hụ na ha dị mma.<verse eid="GEN 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 1:11"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka ala pupụta ahịhịa ndụ dị iche iche: ahịhịa na-amịpụta mkpụrụ, na osisi dị nʼelu ala nke na-amịpụta mkpụrụ, nke mkpụrụ ọkụkụ ya dị nʼime ya, dịka ụdịdị ha dị iche iche si dị.” O sikwa otu a dịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 1:12"/>Ala puputara ahịhịa ndụ dị iche iche: ahịhịa na-amịpụta mkpụrụ dịka ụdịdị ha si dị, na osisi na-amịpụta mkpụrụ, nke mkpụrụ ọkụkụ ya dị nʼime ya, dịka ụdịdị ha si dị. Chineke lere anya hụ na ọ dị mma. <verse eid="GEN 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 1:13"/>Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke atọ.<verse eid="GEN 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 1:14"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka ìhè nke na-enye ìhè dịrị na mbara eluigwe, ikewapụ ehihie site nʼabalị. Ka ha bụrụ ihe ama igosi oge dị iche iche, ụbọchị dị iche iche, na afọ dị iche iche. <verse eid="GEN 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 1:15"/>Ka ha bụrụ ìhè na mbara eluigwe inye ìhè nʼelu ụwa.” O si otu a dịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 1:16"/>Chineke mere ìhè ukwu abụọ, nke kacha ịdị ukwu ka ọ bụrụ nke ga-achị ehihie, ma nke dị nta ka ọ bụrụ nke ga-achị abalị. O mekwara kpakpando dị iche iche. <verse eid="GEN 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 1:17"/>Chineke debere ha na mbara eluigwe inye ìhè nʼụwa, <verse eid="GEN 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 1:18"/>ịchị ehihie na abalị na ịkpa oke nʼetiti ìhè na ọchịchịrị. Chineke lere anya hụ na ọ dị mma. <verse eid="GEN 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 1:19"/>Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke anọ.<verse eid="GEN 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 1:20"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka mmiri jupụta nʼihe ndị na-eku ume, ka ụmụ anụ ufe fegharịkwa nʼelu ụwa, ma nʼelu mbara igwe.” <verse eid="GEN 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 1:21"/>Ya mere Chineke kere anụ ukwu niile bi na mmiri, na anụ niile nwere ndụ bi na mmiri, na ụdị ihe ọbụla nwere ndụ na-akpụgharị akpụgharị ndị jupụtara na mmiri, dịka ụdịdị ha si dị, na anụ ufe niile dịka ụdịdị ha si dị. Chineke lere anya hụ na ọ dị mma. <verse eid="GEN 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 1:22"/>Chineke gọziri ha, sị ha, “Mụbaanụ, dịkwanụ ukwuu nʼọnụọgụgụ, jupụtanụ osimiri niile. Ka anụ ufe dịkwa ukwuu nʼọnụọgụgụ nʼelu ụwa.” <verse eid="GEN 1:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 1:23"/>Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke ise.<verse eid="GEN 1:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 1:24"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka ala wepụta ụmụ anụ dị iche iche nwere ndụ dịka ụdịdị ha si dị: anụ ụlọ, anụ na-akpụgharị nʼala, na anụ ọhịa, nke ọbụla dịka ụdịdị ya si dị.” O si otu a dịrị. <verse eid="GEN 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 1:25"/>Chineke mere ụmụ anụ ọhịa, dịka ụdịdị ha si dị, mee anụ ụlọ, dịka ụdịdị ha si dị, na anụ niile nwere ndụ nke na-akpụgharị nʼala dịka ụdịdị ha si dị. Chineke lere anya hụ na ọ dị mma.<verse eid="GEN 1:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 1:26"/>Mgbe ahụ, Chineke kwuru sị, “Ka anyị mee mmadụ nʼoyiyi anyị, dịka ụdịdị anyị si dị, ka ha chịa azụ niile nke osimiri, na anụ ufe niile nke eluigwe, na anụ ụlọ niile, na anụ ọhịa niile, na ihe niile e kere eke nwere ndụ nke na-akpụ akpụ nʼala.”<verse eid="GEN 1:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 1:27"/>Ya mere, Chineke kere mmadụ nʼoyiyi nke ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 1:27">nʼoyiyi Chineke ka o kere ha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 1:27">nwoke na nwanyị ka o kere ha.<verse eid="GEN 1:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 1:28"/>Chineke gọziri ha sị ha, “Mịanụ mkpụrụ, mụbaanụ, jupụtanụ nʼụwa, meenụ ka ihe niile dịrị nʼokpuru unu. Chịanụ azụ niile nke osimiri na anụ ufe niile nke eluigwe na ihe niile e kere dị ndụ nke na-akpụgharị akpụgharị nʼala.”<verse eid="GEN 1:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 1:29"/>Mgbe ahụ, Chineke sịrị “Enyela m unu ahịhịa ubi niile na-amị mkpụrụ dị nʼelu ụwa, na osisi ọbụla mịrị mkpụrụ, nke mkpụrụ ọkụkụ ya dị nʼime ha, ka ha bụrụ ihe oriri gị. <verse eid="GEN 1:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 1:30"/>Ma ụmụ anụmanụ niile na anụ ufe niile, na anụ niile e kere eke na-akpụgharị akpụgharị nʼala, anụ ọbụla nwere ndụ nʼime ha ka m na-enye ahịhịa ndụ niile ka ọ bụrụ ihe oriri ha.”<verse eid="GEN 1:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 1:31"/>Chineke legharịrị anya nʼihe o kere, hụ na ọ dị ezi mma. Uhuruchi dị, ụtụtụ dịkwa. Ọ bụrụ ụbọchị nke isii.<verse eid="GEN 1:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="GEN 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="GEN 2"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 2:1"/>Otu a ka e si rụzuo ọrụ ike eluigwe na ụwa na ihe niile dị nʼime ha.<verse eid="GEN 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 2:2"/>Nʼụbọchị nke asaa, Chineke kwụsịrị ọrụ ya nke ọ na-arụ, o zukwara ike site nʼọrụ ya niile. <verse eid="GEN 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 2:3"/>Chineke gọziri ụbọchị nke asaa ahụ mee ya ka ọ bụrụ ụbọchị dị nsọ, nʼihi na ọ bụ nʼụbọchị ahụ ka ọ zuru ike site nʼọrụ nke ike ihe niile.<verse eid="GEN 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Adam na Iiv</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 2:4"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro okike eluigwe na ụwa mgbe e kere ha, nʼụbọchị ahụ mgbe <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kere eluigwe na ụwa.<verse eid="GEN 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 2:5"/>Ahịhịa ọbụla epupụtabeghị nʼọhịa, o nwekwaghị ihe ubi ọbụla sitere nʼala pupụta, nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke ezitebeghị mmiri ozuzo nʼelu ụwa, o nwekwaghị mmadụ ọbụla nọ na-arụ ọrụ ubi, <verse eid="GEN 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 2:6"/>ma mmiri si nʼala na-asọpụta na-asọ nʼelu ala niile. <verse eid="GEN 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 2:7"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kpụrụ mmadụ site nʼaja nke ala, kunye ya ume ndụ nʼimi ya, nke mere ka mmadụ ghọọ ihe dị ndụ.<verse eid="GEN 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 2:8"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kụrụ ubi a gbara ogige nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ, nʼIden. O tinyere mmadụ ahụ ọ kpụrụ nʼime ubi a. <verse eid="GEN 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 2:9"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke mere ka osisi dị iche iche si nʼala pupụta, osisi ndị dị mma ile anya na nke dịkwa mma iri eri. Nʼetiti ogige a, e nwere osisi na-enye ndụ, na osisi nke ịmata ihe ọma na ihe ọjọọ.<verse eid="GEN 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 2:10"/>E nwere iyi si nʼIden na-asọpụta na-asọbanye nʼime ogige ahụ ime ka ala ahụ nwee mmiri. Site nʼebe ahụ, iyi a kewara nwee ngalaba anọ. <verse eid="GEN 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 2:11"/>Aha ngalaba nke mbụ bụ Paịshọn. Ọ sọọrọ ogologo gafee ala niile nke Havila, ebe a na-enweta ọlaedo. <verse eid="GEN 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 2:12"/>(Ọlaedo dị nʼala ahụ mara mma. Eso osisi na-esi isi ụtọ na nkume dị oke ọnụahịa a na-akpọ ọniks dịkwa nʼebe ahụ.) <verse eid="GEN 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 2:13"/>Aha ngalaba nke abụọ bụ Gaihọn. O sitere nʼala Kush<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Kush bụ aha e ji maara ala ndị Sụdan </char><char style="ft" closed="false">maọbụ </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Itiopia nʼasụsụ ndị Hibru. </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mgbe ọbụla e kwuru banyere Kush nʼakwụkwọ ọgbụgba ndụ ochie, ọ bụ ala ahụ ka a na-ekwu ihe banyere ya.</char></note> gafee. <verse eid="GEN 2:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 2:14"/>Aha osimiri nke atọ bụ Taịgris. Ọ na-asọla nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ nke ala Ashọ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ashọ na Asịrịa bụ otu ihe</char></note> Aha osimiri nke anọ bụ Yufretis.<verse eid="GEN 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 2:15"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke weere mmadụ ahụ tinye ya nʼogige Iden, ka ọ na-akọ ya ma bụrụkwa onye na-elekọta ya. <verse eid="GEN 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 2:16"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nyere mmadụ ahụ iwu sị ya “I nwere ike iri mkpụrụ osisi niile dị nʼubi a, <verse eid="GEN 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 2:17"/>ma ị gaghị eri mkpụrụ si nʼosisi ịmata ihe ọma na ihe ọjọọ. Nʼihi na ụbọchị i riri ya ị ga-anwụrịrị.”<verse eid="GEN 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 2:18"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kwuru sị, “Ọ dịghị mma ka nwoke nọrọ naanị ya. Aga m emere ya onye inyeaka nke kwesiri ya.”<verse eid="GEN 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 2:19"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke sitere nʼala kpụọ ụmụ anụmanụ niile nke ọhịa na ụmụ anụ ufe niile nke eluigwe. O dutere ha ka ọ mara ihe mmadụ ahụ ga-akpọ ha. Ihe ọbụla mmadụ ahụ kpọrọ ihe ọbụla ndị a nwere ndụ, nke ahụ bụkwa aha ya. <verse eid="GEN 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 2:20"/>Ya mere, mmadụ ahụ nyere anụ ụlọ niile na anụ ufe niile na anụ ọhịa niile aha.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 2:20">Ma nʼebe Adam nọ, o nweghị onye inyeaka kwesiri ya. <verse eid="GEN 2:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 2:21"/>Ya mere, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke mere ka nwoke ahụ daa nʼụra. Mgbe ọ nọ na-arahụ ụra, o wepụtara otu ọgịrịga site na ngụ dị ya nʼahụ, mechikwaa ebe o si wepụta ya. <verse eid="GEN 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 2:22"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke ji otu ọgịrịga o si nʼahụ nwoke ahụ wepụta, mee nwanyị, dutere ya nwoke ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 2:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 2:23"/>Nwoke ahụ kwuru sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 2:23">“Nke a bụ ọkpụkpụ si nʼọkpụkpụ m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 2:23">na anụ ahụ si nʼahụ m,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 2:23">a ga-akpọ ya ‘nwanyị,’</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 2:23">nʼihi na e si nʼime nwoke wepụta ya.”<verse eid="GEN 2:23"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 2:24"/>Ọ bụ nke a mere nwoke ga-eji hapụ nne na nna ya, e jikọta ya na nwunye ya, ha ga-abụ otu anụ ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 2:25"/>Nwoke ahụ na nwunye ya gba ọtọ, ma ihere emeghị ha.<verse eid="GEN 2:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="GEN 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Mmehie na Ọdịda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 3:1"/>Agwọ dị aghụghọ karịa ụmụ anụ ọhịa niile <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kere. Ọ bịakwutere nwanyị ahụ sị ya, “Ọ bụ ezie na Chineke sị unu erila mkpụrụ si nʼosisi niile dị nʼogige a?”<verse eid="GEN 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 3:2"/>Nwanyị ahụ zara sị ya, “Anyị nwere ike rie mkpụrụ si nʼosisi niile dị nʼogige a <verse eid="GEN 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 3:3"/>ma Chineke kwuru sị, ‘Unu erila mkpụrụ si nʼosisi dị nʼetiti ogige a, unu emetụkwala ya aka, ka unu ghara ịnwụ.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 3:4"/>Agwọ gwara nwanyị ahụ sị, “Unu agaghị anwụ. <verse eid="GEN 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 3:5"/>Nʼihi na Chineke maara na ọ bụrụ na unu erie ya, anya unu ga-emeghe, unu ga-amata ezi ihe na ajọ ihe.”<verse eid="GEN 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 3:6"/>Nwanyị ahụ hụrụ na mkpụrụ si nʼosisi ahụ dị mma iri eri, na ọ dị mma nʼanya, na ọ bụ osisi mara mma e si enweta amamihe. Ọ ghọọrọ mkpụrụ ahụ rie, nyekwa di ya, onye nke na ya nọ, o rie. <verse eid="GEN 3:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 3:7"/>Mgbe ahụ, anya ha abụọ meghere, ha chọpụtara na ha gba ọtọ. Ya mere, ha dụkọtara ahịhịa fiig, jiri ya mere onwe ha akwa.<verse eid="GEN 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 3:8"/>Mgbe nwoke ahụ na nwunye ya nụrụ ụda njegharị <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nʼogige ahụ nʼoge uhuruchi, ha zoro onwe ha site nʼebe <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nọ nʼetiti osisi ndị dị nʼogige ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 3:9"/>Ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke kpọrọ nwoke ahụ oku sị ya, “Ebee ka ị nọ?”<verse eid="GEN 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 3:10"/>Ọ zara si, “Anụrụ m ụda ụkwụ gị nʼogige, nʼihi ya, atụrụ m ụjọ, ebe ọ bụ na m gba ọtọ. Ezokwara m onwe m.”<verse eid="GEN 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 3:11"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke jụrụ ya sị, “Onye gwara gị na ị gba ọtọ? I riela mkpụrụ si nʼosisi ahụ m nyere gị iwu sị gị erila?”<verse eid="GEN 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 3:12"/>Nwoke ahụ sịrị, “Nwanyị ahụ i mere ka mụ na ya nọdụ, ọ bụ ya nyere m mkpụrụ sitere nʼosisi ahụ, m rie.”<verse eid="GEN 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 3:13"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke sịrị nwanyị ahụ, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 3:13">Nwanyị ahụ zara sị, “Ọ bụ agwọ ghọgburu m, mee m ka m rie ya.”<verse eid="GEN 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ikpe Ọmụma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 3:14"/>Ya mere, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke gwara agwọ ahụ sị, “Nʼihi ihe a i mere,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:14">“Ihe a bụrụ ọnụ ka ị bụ nʼetiti anụ ụlọ niile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:14">na nʼetiti anụ ọhịa niile.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:14">Afọ gị ka ị ga-eji na-aga ije,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:14">aja ka ị ga na-eri</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:14">ogologo ụbọchị ndụ gị niile.<verse eid="GEN 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 3:15"/>Aga m eme ka iro</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:15">dịrị nʼetiti gị na nwanyị ahụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:15">nʼetiti mkpụrụ gị na mkpụrụ ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:15">mkpụrụ ya ga-etipịa gị isi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:15">gị onwe gị ga-ata ya arụ nʼikiri ụkwụ.”<verse eid="GEN 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 3:16"/>Ọ gwara nwanyị ahụ sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:16">“Aga m eme ka ihe mgbu nke ịmụ nwa gị baa ụba nke ukwuu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:16">ọ bụ site nʼihe mgbu ka ị ga-eji mụpụta ụmụ gị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:16">Ọchịchọ nke obi gị ga-adị nʼaka di gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:16">ọ bụ ya ga-achịkwa gị.”<verse eid="GEN 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 3:17"/>Ọ gwara Adam sị, “Nʼihi na ị ṅara nwunye gị ntị, rie mkpụrụ site nʼosisi ahụ m nyere gị iwu sị, ‘Gị erila mkpụrụ sitere na ya,’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:17">“Ala bụ ihe a bụrụ ọnụ nʼihi gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:17">site nʼoke ndọgbu nʼọrụ ka ị ga-eri ihe si na ya pụta</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:17">ogologo ụbọchị ndụ gị niile.<verse eid="GEN 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 3:18"/>Ọ ga-erupụtara gị ogwu na uke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:18">ị ga-erikwa ahịhịa nke ubi.<verse eid="GEN 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 3:19"/>Site nʼọsụsọ nke ga-agbapụta gị nʼihu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:19">ka ị ga-eri nri gị</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:19">tutu ruo mgbe ị lọghachiri nʼala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:19">ebe ọ bụ site nʼala ka e si mepụta gị</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 3:19">nʼihi na aja ka ị bụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 3:19">nʼaja ka ị ga-alaghachikwa.”<verse eid="GEN 3:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 3:20"/>Adam<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Nwoke ahụ</char></note> gụrụ nwunye ya Iiv,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Eleghị anya Iiv pụtara Ịdị ndụ</char></note> nʼihi na ọ bụ nne mmadụ niile dị ndụ.<verse eid="GEN 3:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 3:21"/>Emesịa, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke weere akpụkpọ anụ meere Adam na nwunye ya uwe oyiyi. <verse eid="GEN 3:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 3:22"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke sịrị, “Lee, mmadụ adịla ka onye ọbụla nʼime anyị site nʼịmata ihe ọma na ihe ọjọọ. Ugbu a, ka ọ gharakwa ị setịpụ aka ya ghọrọ mkpụrụ osisi ahụ na-enye ndụ rie, si otu a dịrị ndụ ruo mgbe ebighị ebi.” <verse eid="GEN 3:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 3:23"/>Nʼihi nke a, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke chụpụrụ ya site nʼogige Iden ka ọ gaa na-arụ ọrụ nʼala e si wepụta ya. <verse eid="GEN 3:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 3:24"/>Mgbe ọ chụpụrụ mmadụ, o dochiri nʼọwụwa anyanwụ nke ogige Iden ndị mmụọ ozi dị ike a na-akpọ Cherubim, na mma agha na-acha ọkụ, ka ha na-eche ọnụ ụzọ e si aba nʼebe osisi ahụ na-enye ndụ dị nche.<verse eid="GEN 3:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="GEN 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Ken na Ebel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 4:1"/>Emesịa, Adam na nwunye ya Iiv dinakọrọ dịka di na nwunye. Iiv tụụrụ ime mụọ nwa nwoke, onye ha gụrụ Ken. Iiv sịrị, “Site nʼinyeaka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, amụtala m nwa nwoke!” <verse eid="GEN 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 4:2"/>Emesịa Iiv mụtara nwanne ya nwoke Ebel.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 4:2">Ebel ghọrọ onye na-azụ igwe atụrụ. Ma Ken ghọrọ onye ọrụ ubi. <verse eid="GEN 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 4:3"/>Mgbe ụfọdụ oge gasịrị, Ken wetaara <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ụfọdụ ihe ubi ya dịka onyinye. <verse eid="GEN 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 4:4"/>Ma Ebel, ya onwe ya nyekwara onyinye site nʼigwe ewu na atụrụ ya e bụ ụzọ mụọ, nke mara abụba. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nabatara Ebel na onyinye ya, <verse eid="GEN 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 4:5"/>ma ọ nabataghị Ken na onyinye ya. Nke a wutere Ken, mee ka o wee iwe dị ukwuu. Ihu ya agbarụọ.<verse eid="GEN 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 4:6"/>Ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> jụrụ ya sị, “Gịnị mere i ji ewe iwe? Gịnị mere ihu gị ji gbarụọ? <verse eid="GEN 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 4:7"/>Ọ bụrụ na i mee ihe ziri ezi, agaghị anabata gị? Ọ bụrụkwanụ na ị jụ ime ihe ziri ezi, mmehie nọ nʼọnụ ụzọ na-eche gị ịla gị nʼiyi. Lezie anya hụ na i meriri ya.”<verse eid="GEN 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 4:8"/>Ken gwara nwanne ya Ebel sị, “Bịa soro m ka anyị banye ọhịa.” Mgbe ha nọ nʼebe ahụ, Ken jidere nwanne ya gbuo ya.<verse eid="GEN 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 4:9"/>Emesịa, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> jụrụ Ken ajụjụ sị, “Ebee ka Ebel nwanne gị nwoke nọ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 4:9">Ọ zaghachiri, “Amaghị m. Abụ m onye nche nwanne m?”<verse eid="GEN 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 4:10"/>Ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị ya, “Gịnị ka i mere? Gee ntị, ọbara nwanne gị na-akpọku m site nʼala. <verse eid="GEN 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 4:11"/>Site ugbu a gaa nʼihu ị bụrụla onye a bụrụ ọnụ, na onye e si nʼala chụpụ, ala ahụ meghepụrụ ọnụ ya nabata ọbara nwanne gị, site nʼaka gị. <verse eid="GEN 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 4:12"/>Mgbe ị kụrụ ihe ọbụla nʼime ya, ala agaghị enye gị mkpụrụ ya nʼuju. Site ugbu a gaa nʼihu, ị ga-abụ onye na-awagharị awagharị na onye na-abaghị nʼihe nʼụwa.”<verse eid="GEN 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 4:13"/>Ken zara <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, “Ntaramahụhụ i nyere m dị ukwuu karịa nke m nwere ike ibu. <verse eid="GEN 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 4:14"/>Ugbu a, abụ m onye i si nʼala ubi ya chụpụ. Abụkwa m onye i si nʼihu gị chụpụ. Bido taa aga m abụ onye na-awagharị awagharị nʼime ụwa. Onye ọbụla hụkwara m ga-egbu m.”<verse eid="GEN 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 4:15"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị ya, “O nweghị onye ga-egbu gị, nʼihi na aga m atụkwasịrị onye ọbụla metụrụ gị aka ntaramahụhụ okpukpu asaa karịa nke m nyere gị.” Ya mere, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kara Ken akara iji gbochie onye ọbụla hụrụ ya igbu ya. <verse eid="GEN 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 4:16"/>Ken sitere nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> pụọ gaa biri nʼala Nọd,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Nọd </char><char style="ft" closed="false">pụtara </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Awagharị </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nke a dị nʼamaokwu <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 4:12">4:12</ref>,<ref loc="GEN 4:16">16</ref></char></char></note> obodo dị nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ Iden.<verse eid="GEN 4:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 4:17"/>Ken na nwunye ya dinakọrọ, nwunye ya tụụrụ ime mụta nwa nwoke aha ya bụ Enọk. Nʼoge a, Ken nọ na-ewu otu obodo ọ gụrụ Enọk, nke bụ aha nwa ya nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 4:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 4:18"/>Enọk bụ nna Irad, Irad bụ nna Mehujael, Mehujael bụ nna Metusael, Metusael abụrụ nna Lamek.<verse eid="GEN 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 4:19"/>Lamek lụrụ ụmụ nwanyị abụọ. Aha nwunye ya nke mbụ bụ Ada. Aha nke ọzọ bụ Zila. <verse eid="GEN 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 4:20"/>Ada mụtara Jabal, onye bụ nna ndị na-azụ anụ ụlọ, na ndị na-ebi nʼụlọ ikwu. <verse eid="GEN 4:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 4:21"/>Aha nwanne ya nwoke bụ Jubal, onye mbụ bụ nna ndị na-akpọ ụbọ akwara, na ndị na-afụ opi. <verse eid="GEN 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 4:22"/>Zila, mụtara otu nwa nwoke aha ya bụ Tubal Ken, onye bụ nna ndị niile na-akpụ ihe dị iche iche e ji bronz maọbụ igwe kpụọ. Aha nwanne nwanyị Tubal Ken bụ Naama.<verse eid="GEN 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 4:23"/>Lamek kpọrọ ndị nwunye ya sị ha,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 4:23">“Geenụ m ntị, Ada na Zila,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 4:23">unu ndị nwunye Lamek, nụrụ okwu sị m nʼọnụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 4:23">Egbuola m otu nwoke nʼihi na ọ merụrụ m ahụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 4:23">otu nwokorobịa nʼihi na ọ mehịara m ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 4:24"/>Ọ bụrụ na a ga-abọtara Ken ọbọ ugboro asaa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 4:24">mgbe ahụ, a ga-abọtara Lamek ọbọ iri ugboro asaa na asaa.”<verse eid="GEN 4:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 4:25"/>Adam na Iiv dinakọrọ ọzọ, Iiv tụụrụ ime mụta nwa nwoke ọ gụrụ Set. Nʼihi na Iiv kwuru sị, “Chineke enyela m nwa nwoke ọzọ nʼọnọdụ Ebel onye Ken gburu.” <verse eid="GEN 4:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 4:26"/>Set mụtara nwa nwoke gụọ ya Enọsh.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 4:26">Nʼoge ahụ ka ụmụ mmadụ bidoro ịkpọku aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 4:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="GEN 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Site nʼAdam ruo Noa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 5:1"/>Nke a bụ usoro ihe ndepụta banyere agbụrụ Adam.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 5:1"/>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 5:1">Mgbe Chineke kere mmadụ, o kere ya nʼoyiyi Chineke. <verse eid="GEN 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 5:2"/>O kere ha nwoke na nwanyị, gọziekwa ha. Mgbe e kere ha, ọ kpọrọ ha mmadụ.<verse eid="GEN 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 5:3"/>Mgbe Adam gbara narị afọ na iri afọ atọ, ọ mụrụ nwa ya nwoke nʼoyiyi nke ya, na nʼụdịdị nke ya. Ọ gụrụ ya Set. <verse eid="GEN 5:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 5:4"/>Site nʼoge a mụrụ Set, Adam dịrị ndụ narị afọ asatọ ọzọ, ọ mụrụ ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 5:5"/>Adam nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ itoolu na iri afọ atọ.<verse eid="GEN 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 5:6"/>Set gbara narị afọ na ise mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Enọsh, <verse eid="GEN 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 5:7"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Enọsh, Set dịrị ndụ ruo narị afọ asatọ na asaa ọzọ, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 5:8"/>Set nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ itoolu na iri afọ na abụọ.<verse eid="GEN 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 5:9"/>Mgbe Enọsh gbara iri afọ itoolu, ọ ghọrọ nna Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 5:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 5:10"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Kenan, Enọsh dịrị ndụ narị afọ asatọ na iri afọ na ise, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 5:11"/>Enọsh nwụkwara mgbe ọ nọzuru narị afọ itoolu na afọ ise.<verse eid="GEN 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 5:12"/>Mgbe Kenan gbara iri afọ asaa ka ọ ghọrọ nna Mahalalel. <verse eid="GEN 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 5:13"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Mahalalel, Kenan dịrị ndụ narị afọ asatọ na iri afọ anọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 5:14"/>Kenan nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ itoolu na afọ iri.<verse eid="GEN 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 5:15"/>Mgbe Mahalalel gbara iri afọ isii na afọ ise ka ọ ghọrọ nna Jared. <verse eid="GEN 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 5:16"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Jared, Mahalalel dịrị ndụ narị afọ asatọ na iri afọ atọ, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 5:17"/>Mahalalel nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ asatọ na iri afọ itoolu na ise.<verse eid="GEN 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 5:18"/>Mgbe Jared dị narị afọ na iri afọ isii na abụọ ka ọ ghọrọ nna Enọk. <verse eid="GEN 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 5:19"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Enọk, Jared dịrị ndụ narị afọ asatọ ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 5:20"/>Jared nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ itoolu na iri afọ isii na abụọ.<verse eid="GEN 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 5:21"/>Mgbe Enọk gbara iri afọ isii na afọ ise ka ọ ghọrọ nna Metusela. <verse eid="GEN 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 5:22"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Metusela, Enọk soro ụzọ Chineke narị afọ atọ. Nʼoge a, ọ mụtara ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 5:23"/>Ọnụọgụgụ nke afọ niile Enọk biri ndụ, bụ narị afọ atọ na iri afọ isii na ise. <verse eid="GEN 5:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 5:24"/>Enọk soro ụzọ Chineke ruo na a hụkwaghị ya nʼihi na Chineke kpọọrọ ya.<verse eid="GEN 5:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 5:25"/>Mgbe Metusela gbara narị afọ na iri afọ asatọ na asaa ka ọ ghọrọ nna Lamek. <verse eid="GEN 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 5:26"/>Mgbe ọ ghọchara nna Lamek, Metusela dịrị ndụ narị afọ asaa na iri afọ asatọ na abụọ ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 5:27"/>Metusela nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ itoolu na iri afọ isii na itoolu.<verse eid="GEN 5:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 5:28"/>Mgbe Lamek gbara narị afọ na iri afọ asatọ na abụọ ka ọ mụtara nwa nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 5:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 5:29"/>Lamek gụrụ ya Noa, nʼihi na ọ sịrị: “Ọ ga-akasị anyị obi nʼime oke ọrụ na ndọgbu anyị na-adọgbu onwe anyị nʼọrụ nʼala a <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> bụrụ ọnụ.” <verse eid="GEN 5:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 5:30"/>Mgbe a mụsịrị Noa, Lamek dịrị ndụ narị afọ ise na iri afọ itoolu na ise ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom. <verse eid="GEN 5:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 5:31"/>Lamek nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ asaa na iri afọ asaa na asaa.<verse eid="GEN 5:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 5:32"/>Mgbe Noa gbara narị afọ ise ọ ghọrọ nna Shem, Ham na Jafet.<verse eid="GEN 5:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="GEN 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Ajọ omume dị nʼime Ụwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 6:1"/>Mgbe ndị mmadụ bidoro mụbaa nʼụwa, mgbe a mụtakwaara ha ọtụtụ ụmụ ndị inyom, <verse eid="GEN 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 6:2"/>ka ụmụ ndị ikom Chineke bidoro ilekwasị ụmụ ndị inyom ndị mmadụ anya, hụ na ha mara mma. Ha duuru ndị inyom ọbụla masịrị ha ka ha bụrụ nwunye ha. <verse eid="GEN 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 6:3"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sịrị, “Mmụọ m na mmadụ agaghị anọgide nʼịgba mgba nʼime mmadụ ruo ebighị ebi, nʼihi na mmadụ efu ka ọ bụ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Mmụọ m agaghị adịgide nʼime mmadụ ruo ebighị ebi nʼihi na ha bụ ihe rụrụ arụ.</char></note> Ọnụọgụgụ ndụ ya ga-abụ narị afọ na iri afọ abụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 6:4"/>Ndị Nefilim nọ nʼụwa nʼoge ahụ, ma nʼoge sotere ya mgbe ahụ, ụmụ ndị ikom Chineke na-abakwuru ndị inyom ụmụ mmadụ, site na mmekọrịta dị otu a mụọ ụmụ. Ndị a bụ ndị dike mgbe ochie ahụ, ndị a ma ama.<verse eid="GEN 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 6:5"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> hụrụ otu ịba ụba nke ajọ omume mmadụ si dị ukwuu, hụkwa na echiche uche nke obi ya niile dị naanị nʼime ihe ọjọọ, mgbe niile. <verse eid="GEN 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 6:6"/>O wutere <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nke ukwuu na o kere mmadụ, mkpụrụobi ya jupụtakwara nʼihe mgbu. <verse eid="GEN 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 6:7"/>Nʼihi ya, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sịrị, “Aga m esi nʼụwa kpochapụ mmadụ niile m kere eke. E e, mmadụ na anụmanụ niile, na ihe e kere eke na-akpụgharị nʼelu ala, na anụ ufe niile. Nʼihi na o wutere m na m kere ha.” <verse eid="GEN 6:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 6:8"/>Ma Noa nwetara ihuọma nʼanya <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Noa na uju mmiri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 6:9"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro ndụ Noa na ezinaụlọ ya.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 6:9"/>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 6:9">Noa bụ onye ezi omume. Onye na-enweghị ịta ụta ọbụla nʼetiti ndị bi nʼoge ya. O mere ihe nʼụzọ Chineke chọrọ ya. <verse eid="GEN 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 6:10"/>Noa mụtara ụmụ ndị ikom atọ aha ha bụ, Shem, Ham, na Jafet.<verse eid="GEN 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 6:11"/>Ma nʼanya Chineke, ụwa bụ ihe rụrụ arụ, jupụtakwa nʼihe ike. <verse eid="GEN 6:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 6:12"/>Chineke hụrụ otu ụwa si jọgbuo onwe ya na njọ, hụkwa na ụmụ mmadụ bụ ndị ihe ọjọọ riri ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 6:13"/>Chineke sịrị Noa, “Aga m ebibi ihe niile bụ mmadụ, nʼihi na ụwa jupụtara nʼihe ike nʼihi omume mmadụ. E e, aga m ebibi ụwa na ndị niile nọ nʼime ya. <verse eid="GEN 6:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 6:14"/>Ya mere, jiri osisi gofa wuore onwe gị ụgbọ mmiri. Rụnye ọtụtụ ọnụụlọ nʼime ya. Jiri korota techie elu ya na ime ya. <verse eid="GEN 6:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 6:15"/>Otu a ka i ga-esi wuo ya: mee ka ogologo ụgbọ mmiri ahụ dịrị narị mita na iri mita anọ, obosara ya dịrị iri mita abụọ na atọ, ịdị elu ya dịrị mita iri na atọ na ọkara. <verse eid="GEN 6:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 6:16"/>Meere ụgbọ mmiri ahụ ihe e ji ekpuchi elu ya. Mekwa oghere ga-adị ọkara mita site nʼebe ihe mkpuchi elu ụgbọ mmiri ahụ gbadata. Tinye ọnụ ụzọ nʼakụkụ ụgbọ mmiri ahụ, ma rụọkwa okpukpu nkwasa atọ, nke ala ala, nke etiti na nke elu elu. <verse eid="GEN 6:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 6:17"/>Nʼihi na aga m eweta uju mmiri nʼụwa, ibibi ihe niile nwere ndụ dị nʼokpuru eluigwe. Ihe niile e kere eke na-eku ume ndụ ga-anwụ. Ihe niile nọ nʼụwa ga-ala nʼiyi. <verse eid="GEN 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 6:18"/>Ma aga m eme ka ọgbụgba ndụ m dịrị gị. Ị ga-abanye nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ, gị na ụmụ gị ndị ikom, na nwunye gị, na ndị nwunye ụmụ gị ndị ikom. <verse eid="GEN 6:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 6:19"/>Ị ga-ewebata ihe niile e kere eke dị ndụ, abụọ abụọ, oke na nwunye, ichebe ha ndụ. <verse eid="GEN 6:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 6:20"/>Ụdị nnụnụ dị iche iche, abụọ abụọ, na ụdị anụmanụ ọbụla dị iche iche, na ụdị anụ na-akpụ akpụ dị iche iche, ga-abịakwute gị ka i debe ha ndụ. <verse eid="GEN 6:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 6:21"/>Ị ga-ewebata ụdị nri dị iche iche a na-eri eri, chịkọtaa ha ka ọ bụrụ nri nke gị na nke ha.”<verse eid="GEN 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 6:22"/>Noa mere ihe niile dịka Chineke nyere ya iwu ime.<verse eid="GEN 6:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="GEN 7"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 7:1"/>Mgbe ụbọchị ahụ zuru, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kpọrọ Noa sị ya, “Baa nʼime ụgbọ mmiri, gị na ezinaụlọ gị niile, nʼihi na nʼime ndị niile bi nʼọgbọ a, ọ bụ naanị gị bụ onye ezi omume m hụrụ. <verse eid="GEN 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 7:2"/>Kpọrọ ụmụ anụmanụ ndị a a gụrụ dịka ndị dị ọcha, dịka ụdị ha si dị asaa asaa, oke na nwunye. Otu a kwa, kpọrọkwa ụmụ anụmanụ ndị a gụrụ dịka ndị na-adịghị ọcha, dịka ụdị ha si dị, abụọ abụọ, oke na nwunye, <verse eid="GEN 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 7:3"/>na ụmụ anụ ufe asaa asaa, dịka ụdị ha si dị, oke na nwunye, maka idebe ụdị ndị a niile ndụ nʼụwa. <verse eid="GEN 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 7:4"/>Nʼihi na ụbọchị asaa site taa, aga m ezidata mmiri ozuzo nʼụwa. Mmiri a ga-ezo iri ụbọchị anọ, ehihie na abalị. Aga m ekpochapụ site nʼelu ụwa ihe niile nwere ndụ nke m kere.”<verse eid="GEN 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 7:5"/>Ya mere, Noa mere ihe niile <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nyere ya nʼiwu.<verse eid="GEN 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 7:6"/>Noa gbara narị afọ isii mgbe mmiri ukwu a bidoro izo nʼelu ụwa. <verse eid="GEN 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 7:7"/>Noa banyere nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ, ya na ụmụ ya ndị ikom na nwunye ya, na ndị nwunye ụmụ ya ndị ikom ịgbanarị uju mmiri ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 7:8"/>Ụmụ anụmanụ ndị dị ọcha, na ndị na-adịghị ọcha, abụọ abụọ, tinyere anụ ufe na ihe niile e kere eke na-akpụgharị nʼala, abụọ abụọ kwa, <verse eid="GEN 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 7:9"/>oke na nwunye, bịakwutere Noa soro ya banye nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ, dịka Chineke nyere Noa nʼiwu. <verse eid="GEN 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 7:10"/>Mgbe abalị asaa gafere, uju mmiri ahụ bịakwasịrị ụwa.<verse eid="GEN 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 7:11"/>Nʼafọ narị isii nke ndụ Noa, nʼọnwa nke abụọ, nʼụbọchị nke iri na asaa, bụ ụbọchị isi iyi niile dị nʼime ime ala nupụtara nʼelu ala, mmiri niile dị na mbara eluigwe ka a hapụrụ ka ha wụdata nʼụwa. <verse eid="GEN 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 7:12"/>Mmiri zogịdere na-esepụghị aka iri ụbọchị anọ, ehihie na abalị.<verse eid="GEN 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 7:13"/>Nʼụbọchị ahụ kpomkwem, Noa banyere nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ, ya na Shem, Ham na Jafet, bụ ụmụ Noa, na nwunye Noa, na ndị nwunye atọ nke ụmụ ya. <verse eid="GEN 7:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 7:14"/>Ha onwe ha, na anụ ọhịa ọbụla, nʼụdị ya, na anụ ụlọ ọbụla, nʼụdị ya na ihe ọbụla e kere eke na-akpụgharị nʼala, nʼụdị ya, na anụ ufe ọbụla nʼụdị ya, na aha nnụnụ ọbụla na ihe ọbụla nwere nku. <verse eid="GEN 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 7:15"/>Ha bịakwutere Noa nʼime ụgbọ mmiri ahụ, abụọ abụọ site nʼihe niile ọbụla e kere eke, nke nwere ume ndụ nʼime ha. <verse eid="GEN 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 7:16"/>Ma ndị banyerenụ bụ oke na nwunye, site na ihe niile nwere ndụ dịka Chineke nyere ya nʼiwu. Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mechiri ọnụ ụzọ dị nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 7:17"/>Uju mmiri nọgidere nʼụwa iri ụbọchị anọ. Mgbe mmiri ndị a na-aba ụba, ha buliri ụgbọ mmiri ahụ elu site nʼelu ala. <verse eid="GEN 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 7:18"/>Mmiri ndị a toro na-ala elu na-abawanyekwa ụba nʼelu ụwa. Ụgbọ mmiri ahụ segooro nʼelu mmiri. <verse eid="GEN 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 7:19"/>Mmiri ndị ahụ toro laa elu kpuchie ugwu ukwu niile dị nʼokpuru mbara eluigwe. <verse eid="GEN 7:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 7:20"/>Mmiri ndị a toro kpuchiri ugwu niile, ruo na ịla elu mmiri ndị a site nʼelu ugwu ukwu niile ruru mita asaa. <verse eid="GEN 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 7:21"/>Ihe niile nwere ndụ nke na-ejegharị nʼelu ụwa kubiri ume. Anụ ufe, na anụ ụlọ, na anụ ọhịa, na ihe niile e kere eke jupụtara nʼụwa, na ụmụ mmadụ niile. <verse eid="GEN 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 7:22"/>Ee, ihe niile na-eku ume nke bi nʼelu ala nwụrụ. <verse eid="GEN 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 7:23"/>Ihe niile nwere ume ndụ nʼelu ụwa ka e kpochapụrụ. Mmadụ na anụmanụ, na anụ na-akpụgharị nʼala na nnụnụ niile. A lara ha niile nʼiyi. Ma ọ bụ naanị Noa na ndị niile so ya nọdụ nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ ka a hapụrụ ndụ.<verse eid="GEN 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 7:24"/>Narị ụbọchị na iri ụbọchị ise ka mmiri dọọrọ nʼelu ụwa dum.<verse eid="GEN 7:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="GEN 8"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 8:1"/>Ma Chineke chetara Noa na ụmụ anụ ọhịa niile, na ụmụ anụ ụlọ niile so ya nọdụ nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ. O zitere ifufe, mee ka o fee nʼelu mmiri ahụ ime ka mmiri ahụ bido ịta. <verse eid="GEN 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 8:2"/>A kpọchiri isi iyi mmiri niile dị nʼime ime ala, kpọchiekwa ọnụ ụzọ mmiri ozuzo nke mbara eluigwe. Mmiri kwụsịrị isi na mbara eluigwe na-ezokwasị ụwa. <verse eid="GEN 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 8:3"/>Mmiri ahụ dị nʼụwa ji nwayọọ na-ata. Mgbe narị ụbọchị na iri ụbọchị ise gafesịrị, mmiri ahụ atalatala. <verse eid="GEN 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 8:4"/>Nʼụbọchị iri na asaa nke ọnwa asaa, ụgbọ mmiri ahụ gara nọkwasị nʼelu ugwu Ararat. <verse eid="GEN 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 8:5"/>Mmiri a gara nʼihu na-ata ruo ọnwa nke iri. Nʼụbọchị nke mbụ nke ọnwa iri, e bidoro ịhụ elu ugwu ndị ọzọ anya.<verse eid="GEN 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 8:6"/>Mgbe iri ụbọchị anọ gafere, Noa meghere oghereikuku ọ rụnyere nʼakụkụ ụgbọ mmiri ahụ, <verse eid="GEN 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 8:7"/>site nʼebe ahụ zipụ otu ugolọma nke na-efepụ na-efebatakwa, tutu ruo mgbe mmiri kọrọ nʼelu ala. <verse eid="GEN 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 8:8"/>Emesịa, o zipụrụ otu nduru iji mata ma mmiri ọ kọọla nʼala, <verse eid="GEN 8:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 8:9"/>ma nduru ahụ achọtaghị ebe o nwere ike ibe, nʼihi na mmiri ka tojuru elu ụwa niile. Nʼihi ya, nduru ahụ lọghachikwutere Noa nʼime ụgbọ ahụ. Noa setịpụrụ aka ya nwụbata nduru ahụ nʼụgbọ. <verse eid="GEN 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 8:10"/>Mgbe abalị asaa gafere, Noa zipụrụ nduru ahụ ọzọ <verse eid="GEN 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 8:11"/>Nʼoge anyasị, nduru a lọghachiri. Ọ kpụ akwụkwọ oliv ọhụrụ ọ kụbitere nʼọnụ ya. Nke a gosiri Noa na mmiri ahụ ataala nʼelu ala. <verse eid="GEN 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 8:12"/>Mgbe abalị asaa gafere, Noa zipụkwara nduru ahụ ọzọ. Ma nʼoge a, ọ lọtakwaghị ọzọ.<verse eid="GEN 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 8:13"/>Nʼụbọchị mbụ nke ọnwa mbụ nʼafọ narị isii na otu nke ndụ Noa, mmiri ahụ atachaala nʼelu ala. Mgbe ahụ, Noa kpughepụrụ ihe mkpuchi nke ụgbọ mmiri ahụ, hụ na mmiri atachaala nʼelu ala. <verse eid="GEN 8:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 8:14"/>Ma ọ bụ nʼụbọchị iri abụọ na asaa nke ọnwa abụọ ka mmiri ji takọrọchaa nʼelu ala.<verse eid="GEN 8:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 8:15"/>Mgbe ahụ, Chineke gwara Noa okwu sị ya, <verse eid="GEN 8:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 8:16"/>“Site nʼụgbọ mmiri pụta, gị na nwunye gị, na ụmụ gị ndị ikom, na ndị nwunye ụmụ gị ndị ikom. <verse eid="GEN 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 8:17"/>Kpọpụta anụ niile dị ndụ nke gị na ha nọ, anụ ufe, na ụmụ anụmanụ, na ihe e kere eke niile na-akpụgharị nʼala, ka ha gaa nʼụwa mụọ ọmụmụ, baa ụba, jupụta nʼelu ya.”<verse eid="GEN 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 8:18"/>Ya mere, Noa si nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ pụta, ya na ụmụ ya, na nwunye ya, na ndị nwunye ụmụ ya. <verse eid="GEN 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 8:19"/>Ma anụmanụ niile ọbụla nke dị ndụ, na ihe niile na-akpụgharị nʼala, na anụ ufe niile, ihe niile na-ejegharị nʼụwa, ka ụdị ha si dị, sitere nʼụgbọ mmiri ahụ pụta.<verse eid="GEN 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 8:20"/>Mgbe ahụ, Noa wuru ebe ịchụ aja<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Aja mbụ a chụrụ nʼAkwụkwọ Nsọ nye Onyenwe anyị bụ aja nsure ọkụ Noa chụrụ, mgbe o ji anụmanụ a na-ewepụghị ihe ọbụla nʼahụ ya chụọ aja.</char></note> nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Ọ họọrọ site nʼanụ ụlọ ndị dị ọcha na anụ ufe ndị dị ọcha chụọ aja nsure ọkụ. <verse eid="GEN 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 8:21"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nụrụ isisi ụtọ nke aja nsure ọkụ ahụ kwuo nʼobi ya sị, “Agaghị m abụ ala ọnụ ọzọ nʼihi mmadụ, ebe ọ bụ na izuzu obi mmadụ bụ ime ihe ọjọọ site na mgbe ọ bụ nwata, agakwaghị m ala ihe niile e kere eke na-eku ume ndụ iyi ọzọ, dịka m mere.<verse eid="GEN 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 8:22"/>“Ogologo oge niile ụwa ga-anọgide,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 8:22">oge ịkụ mkpụrụ na oge iwe ihe ubi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 8:22">oge oyi na oge okpomọkụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 8:22">ọkọchị na udu mmiri,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 8:22">ehihie na abalị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 8:22">agaghị ebi.”<verse eid="GEN 8:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="GEN 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọgbụgba Ndụ Chineke na Noa gbara</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 9:1"/>Mgbe ihe ndị a gasịrị, Chineke gọziri Noa na ụmụ ya sị ha: “Mụọnụ, baanụ, jupụtanụ nʼụwa. <verse eid="GEN 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 9:2"/>Egwu unu na ụjọ unu ga-adakwasị anụmanụ niile nke ụwa nke dị ndụ, na anụ ufe niile nke eluigwe, na ihe e kere eke niile na-akpụgharị nʼala, na azụ niile dị nʼosimiri. Ewerela m ha niile nyefee unu nʼaka. <verse eid="GEN 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 9:3"/>Ihe ọbụla dị ndụ nke na-ejegharị ejegharị ga-abụ nri unu. Enyela m unu ihe niile ugbu a dịka m si nye unu ahịhịa ndụ niile.<verse eid="GEN 9:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 9:4"/>“Ma unu agaghị eri anụ ọbụla nke ọbara ndụ ya dị ya nʼahụ. <verse eid="GEN 9:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 9:5"/>Ma gbasara ọbara ndụ unu, unu ga-asara ọnụ unu nʼihu m. Anụmanụ ọbụla ga-asara ọnụ ya nʼihu m. Mmadụ ọbụla kwa ga-asara ọnụ ya nʼihu m banyere ndụ mmadụ ibe ya.<verse eid="GEN 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 9:6"/>“Onye ọbụla wufuru ọbara mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:6">nʼaka mmadụ ka a ga-awụfu ọbara nke ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 9:6">nʼihi nʼoyiyi Chineke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:6">ka Chineke mere mmadụ.<verse eid="GEN 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 9:7"/>Ma unu onwe unu, mịanụ mkpụrụ, mụbaanụ, jupụtanụ ụwa, baakwanụ ụba nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 9:8"/>Chineke gwara Noa na ụmụ ya sị, <verse eid="GEN 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 9:9"/>“Ugbu a, ana m ehiwe ọgbụgba ndụ nʼetiti mụ na unu, na nʼetiti agbụrụ unu ndị ga-anọchi unu, <verse eid="GEN 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 9:10"/>na nʼetiti ihe niile nwere ndụ nke unu na ha so, ụmụ anụ ufe, na ụmụ anụ ụlọ, na ụmụ anụ ọhịa niile, ndị ahụ niile so unu si nʼụgbọ mmiri pụta, bụ ihe niile nwere ndụ nʼụwa. <verse eid="GEN 9:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 9:11"/>Ebe ọ bụ na m ehiwela ọgbụgba ndụ m nʼetiti mụ na unu, ọ gaghị emekwa ọzọ na a ga-eji uju mmiri kpochapụ ihe niile e kere eke, ọ gaghị emekwa ọzọ na a ga-eji uju mmiri bibie ụwa.”<verse eid="GEN 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 9:12"/>Chineke kwuru sị, “Nke a bụ ihe ama nke ọgbụgba ndụ nke m na-etinye nʼetiti mụ na unu, na nʼetiti ihe niile nwere ndụ so unu, ọgbụgba ndụ nke ga-adị nye ọgbọ niile na-abịa nʼihu. <verse eid="GEN 9:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 9:13"/>Etinyela m eke na egwurugwu m na mbara eluigwe, ka ọ bụrụ ihe ama nke ọgbụgba ndụ dị nʼetiti mụ na ụwa. <verse eid="GEN 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 9:14"/>Mgbe ọbụla m zitere igwe ojii nʼụwa, ọ bụrụ na eke na egwurugwu apụta ìhè na mbara eluigwe, <verse eid="GEN 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 9:15"/>aga m echeta ọgbụgba ndụ m mere ka ọ dịrị nʼetiti mụ na unu, na nʼetiti mụ na ihe niile nwere ndụ site nʼihe niile e kere eke. Ọ gaghị emekwa ọzọ na mmiri ga-aghọ uju mmiri ibibi ihe niile nwere ndụ. <verse eid="GEN 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 9:16"/>Mgbe ọbụla eke na egwurugwu pụtara nʼigwe ojii, aga m ahụ ya cheta ọgbụgba ndụ ebighị ebi nke dị nʼetiti Chineke na ihe niile nwere ndụ site nʼihe niile e kere eke nọ nʼelu ụwa.”<verse eid="GEN 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 9:17"/>Chineke gwara Noa sị, “Nke a bụ ihe ama ọgbụgba ndụ ahụ m hiwere nʼetiti mụ na ihe niile nwere ndụ nʼụwa.”<verse eid="GEN 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụ ndị ikom Noa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 9:18"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Noa ndị si nʼụgbọ mmiri pụta bụ Shem, Ham na Jafet. (Ham bụ nna Kenan.) <verse eid="GEN 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 9:19"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ ndị ikom atọ Noa mụrụ. Ọ bụ site na ha ka ndị mmadụ niile gbasara nʼụwa niile si pụta.<verse eid="GEN 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 9:20"/>Noa, onye ọrụ ubi, bidoro ịkụ ubi vaịnị a gbara ogige. <verse eid="GEN 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 9:21"/>Mgbe ọ ṅụrụ mmanya si nʼubi a, ṅụbiga ya oke, ọ gbaara ọtọ dinaa ala nʼime ụlọ ikwu ya. <verse eid="GEN 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 9:22"/>Ham, nna Kenan, hụrụ ọtọ nna ya, gaa kọọrọ ụmụnne ya abụọ nọ nʼezi ihe ọ hụrụ. <verse eid="GEN 9:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 9:23"/>Ma Shem na Jafet weere akwa tụkwasị nʼubu ha, were azụ jere ije ruo nʼebe nna ha nọ, hapụ akwa ahụ ka ọ dakwasị nna ha kpuchikwaa ọtọ ya. Ma ha chepuru ihu nʼebe ọzọ mgbe ha na-eme nke a, nʼihi ya, ha elekwasịghị ọtọ nna ha anya.<verse eid="GEN 9:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 9:24"/>Mgbe Noa si nʼụra mmanya ya bilie, chọpụta ihe nwa ya nwoke nke nta mere, <verse eid="GEN 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 9:25"/>o kwuru sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 9:25">“Onye a bụrụ ọnụ ka Kenan bụ!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:25">Ohu ndị ohu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:25">ka ọ ga-abụrụ ụmụnne ya.”<verse eid="GEN 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 9:26"/>Ọ sịkwara,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 9:26">“Ngọzị dịrị <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke Shem.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:26">Ka Kenan bụrụ ohu Shem.<verse eid="GEN 9:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 9:27"/>Ka Chineke mee ka ebe obibi Jafet saa mbara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:27">ka Jafet biri nʼụlọ ikwu Shem,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 9:27">meekwa ka Kenan bụrụ ohu ya.”<verse eid="GEN 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 9:28"/>Mgbe uju mmiri ahụ gabigachara, Noa biri ndụ narị afọ atọ na iri afọ ise ọzọ. <verse eid="GEN 9:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 9:29"/>Ọnụọgụgụ afọ Noa niile mgbe ọ nwụrụ, bụ narị afọ itoolu na iri afọ ise.<verse eid="GEN 9:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="GEN 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Usoro ọmụmụ ụmụ Noa</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 10:1"/>Ndị a bụ akụkọ banyere Shem, Ham na Jafet, ụmụ ndị ikom atọ Noa mụrụ. Ha onwe ha mụtara ụmụ nke aka ha, mgbe uju mmiri gafesịrị.<verse eid="GEN 10:1"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Ụmụ Jafet</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 10:2"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Jafet bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:2">Goma, Magog, Madai, Javan, Tubal, Meshek na Tiras.<verse eid="GEN 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 10:3"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Goma bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:3">Ashkenaz, Rifat na Togama.<verse eid="GEN 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 10:4"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Javan bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:4">Elisha, Tashish, Kitim na Rodanim. <verse eid="GEN 10:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 10:5"/>(Site nʼagbụrụ ndị a bi nʼakụkụ mmiri ka e nwetara mba dị iche iche, nʼagbụrụ ha nʼime obodo ha dị iche iche, ndị ọbụla nʼime ha nwekwara asụsụ nke ha.)<verse eid="GEN 10:5"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Ụmụ Ham</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 10:6"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Ham bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:6">Kush,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Kush na-ekwu banyere ala dị nʼugwu ugwu Naịl, nʼala Itiopia, nakwa ala Sụdan. Mizraim bụ maka ndị Ijipt, ebe Put na-ekwu banyere ndị Libiya, maọbụ ndị bi gburugburu ala Sọmalia.</char></note> Ijipt, Put na Kenan.<verse eid="GEN 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 10:7"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Kush<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ọ bụ nʼime ala Arab ka mba asaa ndị Kush dị.</char></note> bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:7">Seba, Havila, Sabta, Raama na Sabteka.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 10:7">Ụmụ ndị ikom Raama bụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:7">Sheba na Dedan.<verse eid="GEN 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 10:8"/>Kush bụ nna Nimrọd, onye mesịrị bụrụ dike nʼagha nʼụwa. <verse eid="GEN 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 10:9"/>Ọ bụ dike nʼịchụ nta, nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Ọ bụ nke a mere e ji na-ekwu okwu na-asị, “Ị dị ka Nimrọd, dike nʼịchụ nta, nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.” <verse eid="GEN 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 10:10"/>Obodo ndị bụ mmalite alaeze ya bụ, Babel,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Babilọn</char></note> Erek, Akad na Kalne, ndị dị nʼala Shaịna.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Shaịna bụ ala Babilọn ochie.</char></note> <verse eid="GEN 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 10:11"/>Site nʼala ahụ ọ gara Asịrịa, ebe o wuru obodo Ninive na Rehobọt Ia, na Kala, <verse eid="GEN 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 10:12"/>na Resin, nke dị nʼetiti Ninive na Kala, ya bụ obodo ukwu ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 10:13"/>Ijipt bụ nna ndị</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:13">Lud, ndị Anam, ndị Lehab, ndị Naftuh, <verse eid="GEN 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 10:14"/>ndị Patrus, ndị Kasluh (onye ndị Filistia<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ndị Filistia bụ mba si nʼagbụrụ (agwara ụgwa) abụọ, otu agbụrụ sitere nʼEshịa, ebe nke ọzọ bụ agbụrụ ndị Ọcha. Njem mbụ ha duuru ha gaa ala Kriit, ebe ha gara biri. <char style="xt"><ref loc="JER 47:4">Jer 47:4</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 9:7">Ems 9:7</ref></char> Emesịa, ha busoro ndị Ijipt agha na senchuri nke iri na atọ, ma bichie ala ha. Mgbe e sitere nʼala Ijipt chụpụ ha, ha gara biri nʼakụkụ ọnụ mmiri ala Kenan.</char></note> sitere na ya) na ndị Kafto.<verse eid="GEN 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 10:15"/>Kenan bụ nna</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:15">Saịdọn, ọkpara ya, na ndị Het, <verse eid="GEN 10:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 10:16"/>ndị Jebus, ndị Amọrait, ndị Gigash, <verse eid="GEN 10:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 10:17"/>ndị Hiv, ndị Aka, ndị Sini, <verse eid="GEN 10:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 10:18"/>ndị Avad, ndị Zema na ndị Hamat.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:18">Emesịa, ndị ikwu Kenan gbasara, <verse eid="GEN 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 10:19"/>oke ala ndị Kenan sitere na Saịdọn ruo Gera, gbatịa ruo Gaza, ruokwa Sọdọm, Gọmọra, Adma na Zeboiim, nke dị nso Lasha.<verse eid="GEN 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 10:20"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Ham, dịka ikwu ha na asụsụ ha si dị, nʼoke ala ebe ha bi, na obodo ha dị iche iche.<verse eid="GEN 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Ụmụ Shem</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 10:21"/>A mụụrụ Shem ụmụ ndị ikom, onye nwanne nwoke nke tọrọ ya bụ Jafet. Ọ bụkwa nna nna ochie ụmụ ndị ikom niile Eba mụtara.<verse eid="GEN 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 10:22"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Shem bụ</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:22">Elam,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:22 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Aha ochie e ji mara Asịrịa.</char></note> Ashua, Apakshad, Lud na Aram.<verse eid="GEN 10:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 10:23"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Aram bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:23">Uz, Hul, Geta na Meshek.<verse eid="GEN 10:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 10:24"/>Apakshad bụ nna Shela,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:24">Shela bụrụ nna Eba.<verse eid="GEN 10:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 10:25"/>Eba mụtara ụmụ ndị ikom abụọ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:25">Aha otu nʼime ha bụ Peleg, nʼihi na ọ bụ nʼoge ndụ ya ka e kewara ụwa. Aha nwanne ya nwoke bụ Joktan.<verse eid="GEN 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 10:26"/>Joktan bụ nna</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 10:26">Almodad, Shelef, Hazamavet, Jera, <verse eid="GEN 10:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 10:27"/>Hadoram, Ụzal, Dikla, <verse eid="GEN 10:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 10:28"/>Obal, Abimael, Sheba, <verse eid="GEN 10:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 10:29"/>Ọfịa, Havila na Jobab. Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Joktan.<verse eid="GEN 10:29"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 10:30"/>Akụkụ ala ha bi gbasapụrụ site na Mesha ruo Sefa nʼala ugwu ugwu nke ọwụwa anyanwụ.<verse eid="GEN 10:30"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 10:31"/>Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Shem, dịka ikwu ha na asụsụ ha si dị, nʼoke ala ebe ha dị, na obodo ha dị iche iche.<verse eid="GEN 10:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 10:32"/>Ndị a bụ ndị ikwu ụmụ Noa ndị ikom dịka usoro ọmụmụ ha si dị, dịka ha si biri na mba dị iche iche. Ọ bụ site na ndị a ka mba niile si gbasasịa ruo akụkụ niile nke ụwa mgbe uju mmiri ahụ gafechara.<verse eid="GEN 10:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="GEN 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Ụlọ elu Babel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 11:1"/>Nʼoge ahụ, ụwa niile nwere naanị otu asụsụ, okwu niile bụkwa otu. <verse eid="GEN 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 11:2"/>Mgbe ndị mmadụ gbasara nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ ha chọtara ala dị larịị na Shaịna biri nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 11:3"/>Ha gwarịtara onwe ha okwu sị, “Bịanụ ka anyị kpụọ brik,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Aja ụrọ</char></note> kpọọ ha ọkụ nke ọma.” Ya mere, ha kpụrụ brik kama nkume, jirikwa bitumen kama ụrọ. <verse eid="GEN 11:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 11:4"/>Mgbe ahụ, ha kwuru sị, “Bịanụ ka anyị wuore onwe anyị obodo na ụlọ elu, nke elu ya ga-eru nʼeluigwe, ka anyị si otu a meere onwe anyị aha, ka anyị ghara ịbụ ndị a ga-agbasa nʼụwa niile.”<verse eid="GEN 11:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 11:5"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> rịdatara hụ obodo ahụ na ụlọ elu ahụ ndị mmadụ na-ewu. <verse eid="GEN 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 11:6"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sịrị, “Lee! Ọ bụrụ na ha malitere ime ihe dị otu a, ugbu a ha bụ otu ndị, nweekwa otu asụsụ, o nweghị ihe ha zubere ime nke ha na-apụghị ime. <verse eid="GEN 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 11:7"/>Ngwa, ka anyị rịda gaa gbarụọ asụsụ ha, ka onye o bụla ghara ịghọta asụsụ ibe ya.”<verse eid="GEN 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 11:8"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mere ka ha gbasaa nʼelu ụwa niile. Ha kwụsịkwara iwu obodo ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 11:9"/>Ọ bụkwa nke a mere e ji kpọọ obodo ahụ Babel<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Babel ya bụ Babilọn </char><char style="ft" closed="false">pụtara </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ọgbaaghara nʼasụsụ Hibru.</char></note> nʼihi na ọ bụ nʼebe ahụ ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> wetara ọgbaaghara nʼasụsụ ndị niile bi nʼụwa. Ọ bụkwa nʼebe ahụ ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> si gbasasịa ha nʼelu ụwa dum.<verse eid="GEN 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Site na Shem ruo Ebram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 11:10"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro ezinaụlọ Shem.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 11:10"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 11:10">Mgbe afọ abụọ gafechara site nʼoge uju mmiri ahụ, nʼoge Shem gbara narị afọ, ọ mụtara Apakshad. <verse eid="GEN 11:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 11:11"/>Shem dịrị ndụ, mgbe ọ mụsịrị Apakshad, narị afọ ise ọzọ, mụtakwa ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 11:12"/>Mgbe Apakshad gbara iri afọ atọ na ise, ọ mụtara Shela. <verse eid="GEN 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 11:13"/>Mgbe ọ mụchara Shela, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ anọ na atọ ọzọ, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 11:14"/>Shela gbara iri afọ atọ mgbe ọ mụrụ nwa ya nwoke Eba. <verse eid="GEN 11:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 11:15"/>Mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Eba, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ anọ na atọ, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 11:16"/>Eba gbara iri afọ atọ na anọ mgbe ọ mụrụ Peleg. <verse eid="GEN 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 11:17"/>Mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Peleg, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ anọ na iri atọ ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 11:18"/>Peleg gbara iri afọ atọ mgbe ọ mụrụ Reu. <verse eid="GEN 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 11:19"/>Emesịa, mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Reu, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ abụọ na itoolu ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 11:20"/>Reu gbara iri afọ atọ na abụọ mgbe ọ mụrụ Serug. <verse eid="GEN 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 11:21"/>Emesịa, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ abụọ na asaa ọzọ, mgbe ọ mụsịrị Serug, ọ mụtakwara ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 11:22"/>Serug gbara iri afọ atọ mgbe ọ mụrụ Nahọ. <verse eid="GEN 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 11:23"/>Emesịa, mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Nahọ, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ abụọ ọzọ mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 11:24"/>Nahọ gbara iri afọ abụọ na itoolu mgbe ọ mụrụ Tera. <verse eid="GEN 11:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 11:25"/>Emesịa, mgbe ọ ghọrọ nna Tera, ọ dịrị ndụ narị afọ na afọ iri na itoolu ọzọ, mụta ụmụ ndị ikom na ụmụ ndị inyom.<verse eid="GEN 11:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 11:26"/>Mgbe Tera gbara iri afọ asaa, ọ ghọrọ nna Ebram, Nahọ na Haran.<verse eid="GEN 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ezinaụlọ Ebram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 11:27"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ gbasara usoro ezinaụlọ Tera.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 11:27"/>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 11:27">Tera ghọrọ nna Ebram, Nahọ na Haran. Haran ghọrọ nna Lọt. <verse eid="GEN 11:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 11:28"/>Haran nwụrụ nʼihu nna ya Tera nʼala ebe a nọ mụọ ya, nke bụ na Ụọ, obodo ndị Kaldịa. <verse eid="GEN 11:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 11:29"/>Ebram na Nahọ lụrụ nwunye. Aha nwunye Ebram bụ Serai ma aha nwunye Nahọ bụ Milka. Milka bụ nwa Haran, onye bụ nna Milka na Iska. <verse eid="GEN 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 11:30"/>Ma Serai bụ nwanyị aga, ọ mụtaghị nwa ọbụla.<verse eid="GEN 11:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 11:31"/>Tera kpọrọ nwa ya Ebram, na nwa nwa ya Lọt, onye bụ nwa Haran,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:31 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Haran bụ aha mmadụ, bụrụkwa aha obodo dị nʼala Mesopotamịa. Obodo e ji ife ọnwa mara, dị ka a makwaara obodo Ụọ.</char></note> na nwunye nwa ya Serai, bụ nwunye Ebram, duru ha hapụ Ụọ, obodo ndị Kaldịa, pụọ gawa nʼala Kenan. Ma mgbe ha bịarutere nʼobodo Haran, ha kwụsịrị biri nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 11:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 11:32"/>Ọ bụ nʼobodo Haran ka Tera nọ nwụọ, mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ abụọ na ise.<verse eid="GEN 11:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="GEN 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọkpụkpọ Ebram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 12:1"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara Ebram okwu sị, “Site nʼobodo gị, sikwa na ụmụnna gị na ezinaụlọ nna gị, gaa nʼala m ga-egosi gị.<verse eid="GEN 12:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 12:2"/>“Aga m eme gị mba ukwu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 12:2">aga m agọzi gị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 12:2">aga m eme ka aha gị dị ukwuu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 12:2">ị ga-abụ ngọzị.<verse eid="GEN 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 12:3"/>Aga m agọzi ndị na-agọzi gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 12:3">ma onye ọbụla kọchara gị ka m ga-akọcha;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 12:3">a ga-agọzikwa agbụrụ niile nọ nʼụwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 12:3">site na gị.”<verse eid="GEN 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 12:4"/>Ya mere, Ebram hapụrụ gaa dịka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara ya. Lọt sokwa ya. Ebram agbaala iri afọ asaa na ise mgbe o si na Haran bulie ije. <verse eid="GEN 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 12:5"/>O duru nwunye ya Serai na Lọt nwa nwanne ya, chịkọtakwa akụ niile ha kpakọbara, na ndị ohu niile ha nwetara nʼala Haran, chee ihu ịga nʼala Kenan. Emesịa ha rutere nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 12:6"/>Ebram jere ije nʼime ala Kenan jeruo nʼebe osisi ukwu More, nke dị nʼobodo Shekem. Ndị Kenan bi nʼala ahụ nʼoge ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 12:7"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mere ka Ebram hụ ya anya, ọ sịrị, “Aga m enye mkpụrụ gị ala a.” Ya mere, Ebram wuru ebe ịchụ aja nʼebe ahụ nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> onye gosiri ya onwe ya.<verse eid="GEN 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 12:8"/>Emesịa, Ebram hapụrụ ebe ahụ chee ihu nʼala ugwu dị nʼọwụwa anyanwụ Betel, maa ụlọ ikwu ya. Obodo Betel dị nʼakụkụ ọdịda anyanwụ, ma obodo Ai dị nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ ebe ọ mara ụlọ ikwu ya. Nʼebe nsọ ahụ Ebram wuru ebe ịchụ aja, nọrọ nʼebe ahụ kpọkuo aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 12:9"/>Ọzọ, Ebram si nʼebe ahụ pụọ gaa ije rute Negev.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ihe aha a pụtara bụ “ala kpọrọ nkụ.” Nke a bụ nʼihi ala ahụ tọgbọrọ nʼefu, gbatịa gbadaa ndịda Jerusalem, nʼụzọ ọzara.</char></note><verse eid="GEN 12:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ebram ejee Ijipt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 12:10"/>Nʼoge ahụ, oke ụnwụ dara nʼala ahụ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 26:1">Jen 26:1</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 41:56">41:56</ref></char></char></note> Nʼihi ya, Ebram hapụrụ ala ahụ gaa nʼala<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼoge a, ụkọ mmiri ozuzo e metụtabeghị ihe ubi nʼala Ijipt, nʼihi na ha na-esite na iyi ha rụrụ na-agba ubi ha mmiri.</char></note> Ijipt, ebe o biri nwa oge. <verse eid="GEN 12:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 12:11"/>Ma mgbe ha na-akwado ịbanye ala Ijipt, ọ gwara Serai nwunye ya sị, “Amaara m na ị bụ nwanyị mara mma. <verse eid="GEN 12:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 12:12"/>Mgbe ndị Ijipt ga-ahụ gị, ha ga-asị, ‘Onye a bụ nwunye ya.’ Mgbe ahụ, ha ga-egbu m ma hapụ gị ndụ. <verse eid="GEN 12:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 12:13"/>Gwa ha na ị bụ nwanne m nwanyị, ka ha meso m mmeso ọma nʼihi gị. Ha ga-echebekwa m ndụ nʼihi gị.”<verse eid="GEN 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 12:14"/>Mgbe Ebram rutere Ijipt, ndị Ijipt hụrụ na nwunye ya bụ nwanyị mara mma. <verse eid="GEN 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 12:15"/>Mgbe ndị ozi Fero hụrụ ya, ha toro ya nʼihu Fero. Nʼihi nke a, ha kpọbatara Serai nʼụlọeze Fero. <verse eid="GEN 12:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 12:16"/>Fero mesoro Ebram mmeso ọma nʼihi nwunye ya. Ebram nwetara igwe atụrụ, na ehi, na nne ịnyịnya ibu, oke na nwunye, na ndị ohu ndị nwoke na ndị nwanyị, na ịnyịnya kamel.<verse eid="GEN 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 12:17"/>Ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> jiri ajọọ ọrịa tie Fero na ndị ezinaụlọ ya ihe otiti nʼihi Serai nwunye Ebram. <verse eid="GEN 12:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 12:18"/>Mgbe ahụ, Fero kpọrọ Ebram sị ya, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere? Gịnị mere ị gwaghị m na ọ bụ nwunye gị? <verse eid="GEN 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 12:19"/>Gịnị mere i ji sị na ọ bụ nwanne gị nwanyị, si otu a mee m ka m kpọrọ ya ka ọ bụrụ nwunye m? Ugbu a, lee nwunye gị, kpọrọ ya laa.” <verse eid="GEN 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 12:20"/>Fero nyere iwu banyere Ebram na ndị ikom so ya. Ha zilagara ya, ya na nwunye ya, na ihe niile o nwere.<verse eid="GEN 12:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="GEN 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Nkewa Ebram na Lọt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 13:1"/>Ebram na nwunye, na ihe niile ha nwere hapụrụ ala Ijipt, gaa ije bịaruo Negev. Lọt sokwa ha. <verse eid="GEN 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 13:2"/>Nʼoge a, Ebram aghọọla ọgaranya dị ukwuu, onye nwere akụnụba nke ọtụtụ anụ ụlọ, na ọlaọcha, na ọlaedo.<verse eid="GEN 13:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 13:3"/>Ha sitere na Negev pụọ ije site nʼotu ebe ruo nʼebe ọzọ tutu ha erute Betel, nʼebe dị nʼetiti Betel na Ai, ebe ọ mara ụlọ ikwu ya na mbụ. <verse eid="GEN 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 13:4"/>Nʼebe nsọ o wukwara ebe ịchụ aja na mbụ, nʼebe ahụ Ebram kpọkuru aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 13:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 13:5"/>Ugbu a Lọt, onye ya na Ebram so na njem ya, bụkwa onye nwere akụnụba nke igwe ewu na atụrụ, na igwe ehi, na ọtụtụ ụlọ ikwu. <verse eid="GEN 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 13:6"/>Ma ala ebe ha nọ ezurughị ha mgbe ha nọkọrọ ọnụ nʼihi na ihe onwunwe ha dị ukwuu ruo na ha enweghị ike ịnọkọ ọnụ. <verse eid="GEN 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 13:7"/>Nke a mere esemokwu ji dapụta nʼetiti ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ Ebram na ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ Lọt. Ndị Kenan na ndị Periz bikwa nʼala ahụ nʼoge ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 13:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 13:8"/>Ya mere Ebram gwara Lọt sị, “Biko, ka esemokwu ghara ịdị nʼetiti mụ na gị, maọbụ nʼetiti ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ m na ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ gị, nʼihi na anyị bụ ụmụnne. <verse eid="GEN 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 13:9"/>Lee, ọ bụ na ala a niile adịghị nʼihu gị? Ka anyị kewaa. Ọ bụrụ na ị gaa nʼakụkụ aka ekpe, aga m aga nʼakụkụ aka nri. Ma ọ bụrụ na i gaa nʼakụkụ aka nri gị, aga m aga nʼakụkụ aka ekpe.”<verse eid="GEN 13:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 13:10"/>Lọt lelitere anya hụ na mbara ala Jọdan bụ ala mmiri na-ezokwasị nke ọma, ala dịka ubi a gbara ogige <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, dịka ala ndị Ijipt nke dị na nso nso Zoa. (Ihe a mere tupu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ebibie obodo Sọdọm na Gọmọra.) <verse eid="GEN 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 13:11"/>Ya mere, Lọt họọrọ nye onwe ya mbara ala Jọdan niile, chee ihu ịga nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ. Ya na Ebram kewara. <verse eid="GEN 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 13:12"/>Ebram nọdụrụ nʼala Kenan, ma Lọt gara biri nʼetiti obodo ndị ahụ dị na mbara ala. Ọ mara ụlọ ikwu ya nso nso obodo Sọdọm. <verse eid="GEN 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 13:13"/>Ma ndị Sọdọm bụ ndị obi tara mmiri, ndị na-emehie nke ukwuu megide <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 13:14"/>Mgbe Lọt siri nʼebe ahụ pụọ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara Ebram okwu sị ya, “Site nʼebe ahụ ị nọ lelie anya gị, lee anya nʼugwu na ndịda, nʼọwụwa anyanwụ na ọdịda anyanwụ. <verse eid="GEN 13:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 13:15"/>Ala ahụ niile ị hụrụ ka m ga-enye gị na mkpụrụ gị ruo mgbe ebighị ebi. <verse eid="GEN 13:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 13:16"/>Aga m eme ka mkpụrụ gị baa ụba dịka aja dị nʼala. Ọ bụrụ na mmadụ enwe ike ịgụta ọnụọgụgụ aja dị nʼala, ha ga-enwe ike gụta ọnụọgụgụ mkpụrụ gị. <verse eid="GEN 13:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 13:17"/>Bilie jegharịa nʼala ahụ niile nʼakụkụ ya ọbụla, nʼihi na ana m enye gị ha niile.”<verse eid="GEN 13:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 13:18"/>Ya mere, Ebram bugharịrị ụlọ ikwu ya, gaa biri nʼakụkụ osisi ukwu Mamre nke dị na Hebrọn. O wuru ebe ịchụ aja nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 13:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="GEN 14"/>
  <para style="s1">Ebram anapụta Lọt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 14:1"/>Nʼoge ahụ kwa, Amrafel, eze Shaịna, na Ariok, eze ndị Elasa, na Kedoloma eze Elam, na Tidal eze Goiim, <verse eid="GEN 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 14:2"/>buru agha megide Bera eze Sọdọm, na Biasha eze Gọmọra, na Shịnab, eze Adma, na Shemeba eze Zeboiim, na eze obodo Bela (ya bụ Zoa). <verse eid="GEN 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 14:3"/>Ndị eze obodo ndị a: Sọdọm, Gọmọra, Adma, Zeboiim na Bela, jikọtara ndị agha ha ọnụ na Ndagwurugwu Sidim (ya bụ, ndagwurugwu osimiri nnu ahụ). <verse eid="GEN 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 14:4"/>Ha fere ofufe nʼokpuru ọchịchị eze Kedoloma afọ iri na abụọ, ma nʼafọ nke iri na atọ, ha nupuru isi.<verse eid="GEN 14:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 14:5"/>Nʼafọ nke iri na anọ, eze Kedoloma na ndị eze ya na ha jikọrọ ọnụ buru agha megide ma merie ndị Refaim<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">14:5 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Refaim </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Aha a Refaim pụtara </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ndị ọ gbaa dimkpa <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 15:20">Jen 15:20</ref></char></char></note> bi nʼAshterọt Kenaim na ndị Zuzim bi na Ham na ndị Emim bi Kiriatem na Shave, <verse eid="GEN 14:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 14:6"/>na ndị Hor nʼobodo ugwu Sia, ruo obodo El Paran, nke dị nʼakụkụ ọzara. <verse eid="GEN 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 14:7"/>Mgbe ahụ, ha chigharịrị azụ gaa En Mishpat (ya bụ Kadesh). Ha meriri ala niile nke ndị Amalek nakwa ndị Amọrait bi na Hazezọn Tama.<verse eid="GEN 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 14:8"/>Mgbe ahụ kwa, ndị agha ndị eze obodo Sọdọm na eze Gọmọra, na eze Adma, na eze Zeboiim, na eze Bela (ya bụ Zoa) pụrụ doo onwe ha nʼusoro ibu agha na Ndagwurugwu Sidim, <verse eid="GEN 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 14:9"/>imegide Kedoloma eze Elam, Tidal eze Goiim, Amrafel eze Shaịna na Ariok eze Elasa. Ya bụ eze ise buru agha megide eze anọ. <verse eid="GEN 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 14:10"/>Ma Ndagwurugwu Sidim jupụtara nʼolulu apịtị. Mgbe ndị agha eze Sọdọm na Gọmọra bidoro ịgba ọsọ. Ụfọdụ nʼime ha dabanyere nʼime olulu ndị a, ma ndị fọdụrụ gbapụrụ ọsọ gbaga nʼugwu. <verse eid="GEN 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 14:11"/>Ma eze anọ ndị a banyere nʼime obodo Sọdọm na Gọmọra bukọrọ akụ ha, na ihe oriri ha niile laa. <verse eid="GEN 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 14:12"/>Ha buuru Lọt, nwa nwanne Ebram, onye bi na Sọdọm na ihe niile o nwere, buru ha na-ala ebe ha si bịa.<verse eid="GEN 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 14:13"/>Ma otu onye gbara ọsọ ndụ site nʼebe ahụ gara kọọrọ Ebram onye Hibru ihe mere. Nʼoge a, Ebram bi nʼebe dị nso nʼosisi ukwu nke Mamre, onye Amọrị, nwanne Eshkọl na Anea, ndị ha na Ebram gbara ndụ. <verse eid="GEN 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 14:14"/>Mgbe Ebram nụrụ na adọrọla Lọt nwa nwanne ya nʼagha, ọ kpọkọtara ndị ikom a zụrụ azụ na-ejere ya ozi, ndị a mụrụ nʼụlọ ya. Ọnụọgụgụ ha dị narị ndị ikom atọ na iri na asatọ, ha chụrụ ndị agha ahụ ọsọ tutu ha erute Dan. <verse eid="GEN 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 14:15"/>Nʼabalị, Ebram kere ndị agha ya ibuso ndị ahụ agha. O meriri ha, chụọ ha ọsọ, chụruo ha Hoba, nke dị nʼakụkụ ugwu Damaskọs. <verse eid="GEN 14:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 14:16"/>Ebram nwetaghachiri ihe niile ahụ ha dọtara nʼagha, dulata nwanne ya Lọt, na ihe onwunwe ya niile, tinyere ndị inyom, na ndị ọzọ niile a dọtara nʼagha.<verse eid="GEN 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Melkizedek agọzie Ebram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 14:17"/>Mgbe Ebram si na mmeri ahụ o meriri Kedoloma na eze ndị ọzọ ahụ na-alọta, eze Sọdọm bịara zute ya na Ndagwurugwu Shave (nke a na-akpọ Ndagwurugwu Eze).<verse eid="GEN 14:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 14:18"/>Melkizedek, eze<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">14:18 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Salem </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Eleghị anya, nke bụ aha ochie e ji mara obodo Jerusalem.</char></note> Salem, onye nchụaja Chineke nke kachasị ihe niile elu, wepụtara achịcha na mmanya, <verse eid="GEN 14:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 14:19"/>ọ gọziri Ebram sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 14:19">“Ngọzị dịrị Ebram site nʼaka Chineke nke kachasị ihe niile elu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 14:19">Onye kere eluigwe na ụwa.<verse eid="GEN 14:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 14:20"/>Ngọzị dịkwara Chineke nke kachasị ihe niile elu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 14:20">onye weere ndị iro gị nyefee gị nʼaka.”</para>
  <para style="m" vid="GEN 14:20">Mgbe ahụ, Ebram nyere ya otu ụzọ nʼime ụzọ iri nke ihe niile.<verse eid="GEN 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 14:21"/>Eze Sọdọm gwara Ebram sị, “Nyeghachi m naanị ndị mmadụ, ma debere onwe gị ihe ndị ọzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 14:22"/>Ma Ebram zara eze Sọdọm sị, “Eweliri m aka m elu ṅụọ iyi nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nke kachasị ihe niile elu, Onye kere eluigwe na ụwa, sị <verse eid="GEN 14:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 14:23"/>na agaghị m esi nʼaka gị were ihe ọbụla bụ nke gị, ọ bụladị eriri maọbụ eriri akpụkpọụkwụ. Ka ị ghara ị sị, ‘Ọ bụ m mere ka Ebram baa ọgaranya.’ <verse eid="GEN 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 14:24"/>Naanị ihe m ga-anara bụ ihe ụmụ okorobịa m ndị a riri, ya na oke ruuru Anea, na Eshkọl, na Mamre so m gaa. Nye ha oke ruuru ha.”<verse eid="GEN 14:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="GEN 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọgbụgba Ndụ Chineke na Ebram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 15:1"/>Mgbe nke a gasịrị, okwu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ruru Ebram site nʼọhụ, sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 15:1">“Atụla egwu, Ebram</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 15:1">Abụ m ọta gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 15:1">ụgwọ ọrụ dị ukwu nke i nwere.”<verse eid="GEN 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 15:2"/>Ma Ebram zara sị ya, “Gị, Onye kachasị ihe niile elu, bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, gịnị bụ ihe ị ga-enye m ebe ọ bụ na m amụtaghị nwa? Lee, ọ bụ Elieza, onye Damaskọs, ga-eketa akụ m niile.” <verse eid="GEN 15:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 15:3"/>Ebram gara nʼihu kwuo sị, “Ebe ọ bụ na m amụtaghị ụmụ, ọ bụ ohu nọ nʼụlọ m ga-eketa akụ m.”<verse eid="GEN 15:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 15:4"/>Ma okwu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> rutere ya, “Nwoke a agaghị eketa ihe i nwere, kama nwa nwoke nke ga-esi nʼahụ gị pụta ga-eketa ihe i nwere.” <verse eid="GEN 15:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 15:5"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kpọpụtara Ebram nʼezi sị ya, “Lelie anya gị elu na mbara eluigwe, gụọ kpakpando niile ị hụrụ ọnụ, ma ị ga-enwe ike ịgụta ha.” Ọ gwara ya sị, “Otu a ka mkpụrụ gị ga-adị. A gaghị agụta ha ọnụ.”<verse eid="GEN 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 15:6"/>Ebram kweere nʼihe <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kwuru. Nʼihi nke a, a gụnyere ya okwukwe a dịka ezi omume.<verse eid="GEN 15:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 15:7"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwakwara ya sị, “Mụ onwe m bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, onye si nʼala Ụọ nke ndị Kaldịa kpọpụta gị, inye gị ala a ka ọ bụrụ ihe nweta gị.”<verse eid="GEN 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 15:8"/>Ma Ebram zara sị, “Biko, Onye kachasị ihe niile elu, bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> olee otu m ga-esi mara na m ga-enweta ya?”<verse eid="GEN 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 15:9"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị ya, “Wetara m nwa nne ehi gbara afọ atọ, na nne ewu gbara afọ atọ, na ebule gbara afọ atọ, na nduru, na nwa kpalakwukwu.”<verse eid="GEN 15:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 15:10"/>Ebram wetaara ya ihe ndị a niile bọwaa ha ụzọ abụọ, doo ha nʼusoro ka otu akụkụ chee akụkụ nke ọzọ ihu. Ma ọ bọwaghị ụmụ nnụnụ ndị ahụ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼọgbụgba ndụ niile a na-eji anụmanụ a chụọ aja. Ndị ahụ gbara ndụ na-esi nʼetiti anụ ndị ahụ a kpọwara ọkara abụọ gafee, maka imesi ọgbụgba ndụ dị otu a ike. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 15:17">Jen 15:17</ref>; <ref loc="JER 34:18">Jer 34:18</ref></char></char></note> <verse eid="GEN 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 15:11"/>Mgbe anụ ufe fekwasịrị ozu anụ ndị ahụ, Ebram chụpụrụ ha.<verse eid="GEN 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 15:12"/>Mgbe anwụ bidoro ịda, Ebram dara nʼoke ụra, oke ụjọ na oke ọchịchịrị dakwasịrị ya. <verse eid="GEN 15:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 15:13"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara ya sị, “Mata nke ọma na ụmụ ụmụ gị ga-anọ dịka ndị ọbịa nʼala na-abụghị nke ha. A ga-edo ha ọnọdụ dịka ndị ohu, mejọọ ha narị afọ anọ. <verse eid="GEN 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 15:14"/>Ma aga m ata mba ahụ ha na-efe dịka ohu ahụhụ. Nʼikpeazụ, ha ga-eji ọtụtụ akụ si nʼebe ahụ pụta. <verse eid="GEN 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 15:15"/>Ma ị ga-anwụ nʼudo. A ga-eli gị mgbe ị kara ezi nka. <verse eid="GEN 15:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 15:16"/>Mgbe ọgbọ anọ gasịrị, ụmụ ụmụ gị ga-alọtakwa nʼala a. Nʼihi na mmehie ndị Amọrait erubeghị nʼuju ya.”<verse eid="GEN 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 15:17"/>Mgbe anwụ dara, mgbe ọchịchịrị gbachiri ebe niile, ite ọkụ na-akwụ anwụrụ ọkụ nke nwere ọwa na-enwu ọkụ si nʼetiti ibe anụ ndị ahụ gafee. <verse eid="GEN 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 15:18"/>Nʼụbọchị ahụ ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> na Ebram gbara ndụ. Ọ sị, “Ndị agbụrụ gị ka m ga-enye ala ndị a, malite nʼiyi ndị Ijipt ruo nʼiyi ukwu Yufretis. <verse eid="GEN 15:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 15:19"/>Ala ndị Ken, na nke ndị Keniz, na nke ndị Kadmọn, <verse eid="GEN 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 15:20"/>na ala ndị Het, na nke ndị Periz na nke ndị Refaim, <verse eid="GEN 15:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 15:21"/>na ala ndị Amọrait na nke ndị Kenan na nke ndị Gigash na nke ndị Jebus.”<verse eid="GEN 15:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="GEN 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Hega na Ishmel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 16:1"/>Ma Serai nwunye Ebram, amụtaghị nwa. Serai nwere odibo nwanyị onye Ijipt, aha ya bụ Hega. <verse eid="GEN 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 16:2"/>Ya mere ọ gwara Ebram sị, “Lee, ugbu a, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> egbochiela m ịmụta ụmụ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">16:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Amụtaghị nwa bụ ihe ndị mmadụ na-ahụta dị ka ntaramahụhụ si nʼaka Chineke. Ọ bụrụ na nwanyị amụtaghị nwa, nʼebe ụfọdụ, omenaala na-akwado ya ị họtara di ya nwanyị ọzọ, onye ga-amụrụ ya ụmụ. Ụmụ niile nwanyị ahụ ga-amụta na-abụ nke nwanyị ahụ na-amụtaghị nwa. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 20:18">Jen 20:18</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 30:3">30:3</ref></char></char></note> Ugbu a, bakwuru nwanyị na-ejere m ozi. Ma eleghị anya, aga m esi na ya wulite ezinaụlọ m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 16:2">Ebram kweere ihe Serai kwuru. <verse eid="GEN 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 16:3"/>Ya mere Serai nwunye Ebram, duuru Hega, odibo nwanyị ya, onye Ijipt, dunye Ebram ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya. Ihe a mere na ngwụcha afọ iri site na mgbe Ebram bịara biri nʼala Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 16:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 16:4"/>Ebram na Hega dinara. Hega tụụrụ ime.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 16:4">Ma mgbe Hega matara na ọ dịrịla ime, ọ malitere ileda nne ya ukwu bụ Serai anya. <verse eid="GEN 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 16:5"/>Mgbe ahụ, Serai gwara Ebram sị, “Ọ bụ gị butere ahụhụ a m nọ nʼime ya. Ọ bụ m were nwaodibo nwanyị m kunye gị nʼaka, ma ugbu a ọ hụrụ na ọ dị ime, abụrụla m onye ọ na-eleda anya. Ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kpee ikpe a nʼetiti mụ na gị.”<verse eid="GEN 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 16:6"/>Ebram zara Serai sị, “Lee, ohu gị nwanyị dị gị nʼaka. Jiri ya mee ihe ọbụla dị gị mma nʼanya.” Nʼihi nke a, Serai mesiri ya ihe ike, nke mere ka o si nʼebe Serai nọ gbapụ.<verse eid="GEN 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 16:7"/>Ma mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> hụrụ ya nʼakụkụ isi iyi mmiri dị nʼọzara, nʼakụkụ ụzọ Shua, <verse eid="GEN 16:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 16:8"/>jụọ ya sị, “Hega, ohu nwanyị Serai, olee ebe i si bịa, olee ebe ka ị na-ejekwa?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 16:8">Hega zara sị, “Ọ bụ site nʼihu nne m ukwu Serai ka m na-agba ọsọ.”<verse eid="GEN 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 16:9"/>Mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara ya sị, “Laghachikwuru nne gị ukwu. Doo onwe gị nʼokpuru ya.” <verse eid="GEN 16:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 16:10"/>Mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sịkwa ya, “Aga m amụba ụmụ gị, ka a hapụ inwe ike ịgụta ole ha dị.”<verse eid="GEN 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 16:11"/>Mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwakwara ya sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 16:11">“Ị dị ime ugbu a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 16:11">ị ga-amụ nwa nwoke.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 16:11">Aha ị ga-agụ ya bụ Ishmel</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 16:11">nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> anụla maka nhụju anya gị.<verse eid="GEN 16:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 16:12"/>Nwoke dịka ịnyịnya ibu a na-azụghị azụ ka ọ ga-abụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 16:12">Ọ ga-emegide onye ọbụla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 16:12">onye ọbụla ga-emegidekwa ya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 16:12">Ọ ga-ebi nʼime ibu iro,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 16:12">megide ụmụnna ya niile.”<verse eid="GEN 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 16:13"/>Hega kpọkuru aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, onye gwara ya okwu sị, “Ị bụ Chineke m na-ahụ m.” Nʼihi na Hega kwuru sị, “Ahụla m, ugbu a, onye ahụ na-ahụ m.” <verse eid="GEN 16:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 16:14"/>Ọ bụ ya mere e ji na-akpọ olulu mmiri ahụ, Bịa-Lahai-Rọị.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">16:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ma o bụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Olulu Mmiri nke Onye ahụ dị ndụ na-ahụ m.</char></note> Ọ ka dị ebe ahụ, nʼetiti Kadesh na Bered.<verse eid="GEN 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 16:15"/>Emesịa, Hega mụtaara Ebram nwa nwoke. Ebram kpọrọ nwa nwoke ahụ Hega mụtaara ya Ishmel. <verse eid="GEN 16:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 16:16"/>Ebram gbara iri afọ asatọ na isii mgbe Hega mụtaara ya Ishmel.<verse eid="GEN 16:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="GEN 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọgbụgba ndụ nke obibi ugwu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 17:1"/>Mgbe Ebram gbara iri afọ itoolu na itoolu, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gosiri ya onwe ya sị ya, “Abụ m Chineke Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile. Jegharịa ije nʼihu m, bụrụ onye na-enweghị ịta ụta ọbụla. <verse eid="GEN 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 17:2"/>Aga m eme ka ọgbụgba ndụ m dịrị nʼetiti mụ na gị, mekwa ka ị mụbaa nke ukwuu nʼọnụọgụgụ.”<verse eid="GEN 17:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 17:3"/>Ebram dara nʼala, kpudo ihu ya nʼala. Chineke gwara ya sị, <verse eid="GEN 17:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 17:4"/>“Lee, nke a bụ ọgbụgba ndụ dị nʼetiti mụ na gị. Ị ga-abụ nna ọtụtụ mba. <verse eid="GEN 17:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 17:5"/>Aha gị agaghị abụkwa Ebram, kama ọ ga-abụ Ebraham, nʼihi na emeela m gị nna nke ọtụtụ mba. <verse eid="GEN 17:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 17:6"/>Aga m eme gị ka ị mụbaa nke ukwuu. Aga m eme ka ị ghọọ ọtụtụ mba dị iche iche, ndị eze ga-esitekwa na gị pụta. <verse eid="GEN 17:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 17:7"/>Aga m eme ka ọgbụgba ndụ mụ na gị gbara guzosie ike, ka ọ dịkwara ụmụ ụmụ ndị ga-esote gị nʼọgbọ niile na-abịa. Ọ bụ ọgbụgba ndụ na-egosi na m bụ Chineke gị, na Chineke ụmụ ụmụ gị niile ga-eso gị. <verse eid="GEN 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 17:8"/>Ala Kenan niile, ebe ị nọ ugbu a dịka ọbịa ka m ga-enye gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ga-esote gị dịka ihe nketa ebighị ebi. Aga m abụ Chineke ha.”<verse eid="GEN 17:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 17:9"/>Chineke gwara Ebraham okwu sị ya, “Ma nʼebe ị nọ, ị ghaghị irube isi imezu ihe ọgbụgba ndụ m kwuru, gị onwe gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ndị ga-esote gị, ruo ọgbọ niile. <verse eid="GEN 17:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 17:10"/>Nke a bụ ọgbụgba ndụ dị nʼetiti mụ na gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ndị ga-esote gị, ọgbụgba ndụ nke unu na-aghaghị idebe. A ga-ebi nwoke ọbụla nʼetiti unu ugwu. <verse eid="GEN 17:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 17:11"/>A ga-ebi unu ugwu, bipụ elu ahụ nke anụ ahụ unu. Nke a ga-abụ ihe ama nke ọgbụgba ndụ dị nʼetiti mụ na unu. <verse eid="GEN 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 17:12"/>Nʼoge ọ gbara mkpụrụ ụbọchị asatọ, unu ga-ebi nwoke ọbụla nʼagbụrụ unu ugwu: ndị a mụrụ nʼụlọ, maọbụ ndị eji ego zụta site nʼaka ndị mba ọzọ, ndị na-esighị na mkpụrụ nke afọ gị. <verse eid="GEN 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 17:13"/>A ga-ebi ha niile ugwu. Ma a mụrụ ha nʼezinaụlọ gị ma i ji ego zụta ha site nʼaka onye mba ọzọ. Ọgbụgba ndụ m nke ga-apụta ihe nʼanụ ahụ gị bụ ọgbụgba ndụ ebighị ebi. <verse eid="GEN 17:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 17:14"/>Nwoke ọbụla a na-ebighị ugwu nke anụ ahụ ka a ga-ebipụ site nʼetiti ụmụnna ya. Nʼihi na o mehiela megide ọgbụgba ndụ m.”<verse eid="GEN 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 17:15"/>Chineke gwakwara Ebraham sị, “Ma nʼebe Serai nwunye gị nọ, ị gaghị akpọkwa ya Serai ọzọ, kama aha ya ga-abụ Sera. <verse eid="GEN 17:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 17:16"/>Aga m agọzi ya, sitekwa na ya nye gị nwa nwoke. Aga m agọzi ya ruo na ọ ga-abụ nne nke ọtụtụ mba. Ndị eze ga-achị ọtụtụ mmadụ ga-esite na ya pụta.”<verse eid="GEN 17:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 17:17"/>Ebraham dara kpuo ihu nʼala, chịakwa ọchị nʼobi ya sị, “Ọ bụ onye gbara narị afọ ka a ga-amụrụ nwa? Sera, onye gbara iri afọ itoolu ọ ga-amụ nwa?” <verse eid="GEN 17:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 17:18"/>Ebraham gwara Chineke sị, “A sịkwa na ị ga-ekwe mee ka Ishmel bụrụ onye dị ndụ nʼihu gị.”<verse eid="GEN 17:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 17:19"/>Ma Chineke zara sị ya, “Ee, kama Sera nwunye gị ga-amụtara gị nwa nwoke. Ị ga-agụ ya Aịzik. Ọgbụgba ndụ m ga-adịkwara ya na agbụrụ ya ruo mgbe ebighị ebi. <verse eid="GEN 17:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 17:20"/>Ma banyere Ishmel, anụla m ihe i kwuru. Aga m agọzi ya mee ya ka ọ baa ụba ma dịkwa ukwuu nʼọnụọgụgụ. Ọ ga-aghọ nna ndị eze iri na abụọ. Aga m eme ya ka ọ ghọọ mba dị ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 17:21"/>Ma ọgbụgba ndụ m ka m ga-eme ka o guzosie ike nʼebe Aịzik nọ, onye Sera ga-amụtara gị nʼoge dịka ugbu a nʼafọ ọzọ.” <verse eid="GEN 17:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 17:22"/>Mgbe ọ gwasịrị Ebraham okwu, Chineke si nʼebe ọ nọ pụọ.<verse eid="GEN 17:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 17:23"/>Nʼụbọchị ahụ, Ebraham duuru Ishmel nwa ya nwoke, na ndị ikom niile a mụrụ nʼezinaụlọ ya, tinyere ndị e ji ego zụta, ndị ikom niile nọ nʼezinaụlọ ya, bie ha ugwu dịka Chineke gwara ya ka ọ mee. <verse eid="GEN 17:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 17:24"/>Ebraham gbara iri afọ itoolu na itoolu mgbe e biri ya ugwu, <verse eid="GEN 17:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 17:25"/>Ishmel nwa ya gbara afọ iri na atọ. <verse eid="GEN 17:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 17:26"/>E biri Ebraham na nwa ya bụ Ishmel ugwu nʼotu ụbọchị ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 17:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 17:27"/>Ndị ikom niile nọ nʼezinaụlọ Ebraham, ndị a mụrụ nʼụlọ ya na ndị e si nʼaka ndị mba ọzọ zụta ka e biri ugwu nʼoge Ebraham biri ugwu.<verse eid="GEN 17:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="GEN 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Ndị ọbịa atọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 18:1"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gosiri Ebraham onwe ya nʼakụkụ osisi ukwu dị na Mamre, mgbe Ebraham nọdụrụ ala nʼihu ụlọ ikwu ya, nʼetiti ehihie. <verse eid="GEN 18:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 18:2"/>O lelitere anya ya hụ ndị ikom atọ ka ha guzo ebe ọ nọ nso. Mgbe ọ hụrụ ha, o sitere nʼihu ụlọ ikwu ya gbakwuru ha izute ha, kpọọ isiala.<verse eid="GEN 18:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 18:3"/>Ọ sịrị, “Onyenwe m, ọ bụrụ na m natara amara nʼihu gị, agabigala ohu gị. <verse eid="GEN 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 18:4"/>Biko, ka ekutere unu mmiri ntakịrị, ka unu sachaa ụkwụ unu, zurukwa ike nʼokpuru osisi a. <verse eid="GEN 18:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 18:5"/>Ka m wetara unu nri ntakịrị unu ga-eri nke ga-agba unu ume tupu unu agawa nʼihu nʼije unu ugbu a unu bịara na nke ohu unu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:5">Ha zara sị ya, “Ọ dị mma. Mee dịka i kwuru.”<verse eid="GEN 18:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 18:6"/>Ya mere, Ebraham mere ngwangwa banyekwuru Sera nʼụlọ ikwu ya sị ya, “Mee ngwa, mapụta ihe ọtụtụ sịa atọ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ya bụ ihe ruru kilogram iri na isii</char></note> site na ọka a kwọrọ nke ọma jiri meta achịcha.”<verse eid="GEN 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 18:7"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ebraham gbagara nʼigwe ehi ya, họpụta otu nwa ehi na-akaghị aka nke ahụ ya dị mma, nye ya otu ohu ya onye mere ngwangwa gbuo ya, dozie ya maka oriri. <verse eid="GEN 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 18:8"/>Emesịa, Ebraham buuru mmiri ara ehi nke rahụrụ arahụ, na mmiri ara ehi, na anụ ahụ a kwadoro dozie ha nʼihu ndị ọbịa ahụ. O guzokwara nso nso ebe ha nọ nʼokpuru osisi ahụ mgbe ha na-eri nri.<verse eid="GEN 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 18:9"/>Ha jụrụ ya sị, “Ebee ka Sera nwunye gị nọ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:9">Ọ zara sị, “Ọ nọ nʼime ụlọ ikwu.”<verse eid="GEN 18:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 18:10"/>Ọ sịrị ya, “Nʼezie, mụ onwe m ga-alọghachikwute gị nʼoge a nʼafọ ọzọ, Sera nwunye gị ga-amụta nwa nwoke.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:10">Sera guzo nʼime ụlọ ikwu ahụ nke dị nʼazụ Ebraham na-ege ntị nʼihe ha na-ekwu. <verse eid="GEN 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 18:11"/>Nʼoge a, Ebraham na Sera emeela nnọọ agadi, gbaakwa isi awọ. Sera agafeela oge ịmụta nwa. <verse eid="GEN 18:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 18:12"/>Ya mere, mgbe Sera nụrụ ihe Onyenwe anyị kwuru, ọ chịrị ọchị sị, “Agadi nwanyị dịka m o si aṅaa amụta nwa, ugbu a onyenwe m karala nka?”<verse eid="GEN 18:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 18:13"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> jụrụ Ebraham ajụjụ sị, “Gịnị mere Sera ji achị ọchị? Gịnị mere o ji kwuo sị, ‘Olee otu agadi nwanyị dịka m ga-esi mụọ nwa?’ <verse eid="GEN 18:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 18:14"/>Ọ dị ihe nyịrị <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ime? Mụ onwe m ga-alọghachikwute gị nʼoge a kara aka, Sera nwunye gị ga-amụta nwa nwoke.”<verse eid="GEN 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 18:15"/>Ma ụjọ tụrụ Sera. Nʼihi ya, ọ gọrọ agọ sị, “Achịghị m ọchị.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:15">Ma Ọ zara sị, “Ọ bụ ezie, Sera, ị chịrị ọchị.”<verse eid="GEN 18:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ebraham arịọ arịrịọ banyere Sọdọm</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 18:16"/>Mgbe ndị ikom atọ ahụ biliri ibidokwa ije ha, ha chere ihu ịga obodo Sọdọm,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18:16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ọnọdụ obodo Sọdọm agbanwebeghị, ọ bụladị ugbu a, ọ ka dị na ndịda akụkụ osimiri Nwụrụ anwụ nke bụkwa osimiri Nnu.</char></note> Ebraham dupụkwara ha. <verse eid="GEN 18:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 18:17"/>Mgbe ha na-aga nʼụzọ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> tulere sị, “O kwesiri ka m zochiere Ebraham ihe m chọrọ ime? <verse eid="GEN 18:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 18:18"/>Ebraham aghaghị ịbụ mba dị ukwuu dịkwa ike. A ga-agọzikwa agbụrụ niile nọ nʼụwa site na ya. <verse eid="GEN 18:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 18:19"/>Nʼihi na ahọpụtala m ya, ka ọ tụziere ụmụ ya na ụlọ ya ndị ga-esote ya ịgbaso ụzọ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> site nʼime ihe dị mma na ihe ziri ezi, ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mezuoro Ebraham ihe niile o kwere ya na nkwa.”<verse eid="GEN 18:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 18:20"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kwuru sị, “Mkpu akwa m na-anụ site na Sọdọm na Gọmọra dị ukwuu, otu a kwa, mmehie ha jọbigara njọ oke. <verse eid="GEN 18:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 18:21"/>Ugbu a, ana m aga ka m jiri anya m hụ ma ihe ha mere ọ dị njọ dịka mkpu akwa m na-anụ si dị. Ma o sighị otu ahụ dịrị, aga m amata.”<verse eid="GEN 18:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 18:22"/>Mgbe ahụ, ndị ikom abụọ nʼime ha gawara Sọdọm. Ma Ebraham nọ na-eguzo nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. <verse eid="GEN 18:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 18:23"/>Ebraham jeruru Onyenwe anyị nso jụọ ya sị, “Uche gị ọ bụ ikpochapụ ndị ezi omume na ndị ajọ omume? <verse eid="GEN 18:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 18:24"/>Ọ bụrụ na ị chọta iri ndị ezi omume ise nʼime obodo ahụ, ị ga-ekpochapụ obodo ahụ? Ị gaghị agbaghara<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18:24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Ị gaghị echebe ya</char></note> ya nʼihi iri ndị ezi omume ise nọ nʼime ya? <verse eid="GEN 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 18:25"/>Ọ bụghị ezi ihe na ị ga-ala ndị ezi omume na ndị ajọ omume nʼiyi. Nʼihi na ị gaghị emeso ndị ezi omume dịka i si mesoo ndị na-eme ajọ ihe. O kwesighị ka onye ga-ekpe ụwa niile ikpe, kpee ikpe ziri ezi?”<verse eid="GEN 18:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 18:26"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị ya, “Ọ bụrụ na m achọta iri ndị ezi omume ise nʼobodo Sọdọm, aga m agbaghara obodo ahụ niile nʼihi ha.”<verse eid="GEN 18:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 18:27"/>Ebraham kwukwara ọzọ sị, “Ugbu a m nwere ike kwuwapụta okwu nʼihu Onyenwe anyị, mụ onye bụ naanị aja na ntụ. <verse eid="GEN 18:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 18:28"/>Eleghị anya ọ bụrụ na e nweta naanị iri ndị ezi omume anọ na ise, ị ga-emebi obodo ahụ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:28">
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị, “Agaghị m ebibi ya ma ọ bụrụ na m achọta iri mmadụ anọ na ise nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 18:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 18:29"/>Ọzọkwa, ọ sịrị ya, “Ọ bụrụkwanụ na a ga-achọta naanị iri mmadụ anọ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:29">
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị ya, “Nʼihi iri mmadụ anọ, agaghị m ebibi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 18:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 18:30"/>Mgbe ahụ ọ sịrị, “Biko, ka iwe hapụ iwe Onyenwe anyị ma m kwuo okwu. Eleghị anya, achọta naanị iri mmadụ atọ nʼebe ahụ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:30">
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zaghachiri sị ya, “Agaghị m emebi ya, ma ọ bụrụ na m achọta iri mmadụ atọ nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 18:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 18:31"/>O kwuru sị, “Ebe ọ bụ na m amalitela ịgwa gị, Onyenwe anyị okwu, biko kwere ka m gaa nʼihu. Ọ bụrụ na a ga-achọta naanị iri mmadụ abụọ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:31">
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị, “Nʼihi iri mmadụ abụọ ahụ agaghị m emebi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 18:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 18:32"/>Nʼikpeazụ, Ebraham kwuru sị, “Ka iwe hapụ iwe Onyenwe anyị. Ka m kwuo naanị otu ugboro a. Ọ bụrụkwanụ na a chọta naanị mmadụ iri nʼebe ahụ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 18:32">
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara sị, “Nʼihi mmadụ iri ahụ, agaghị m ebibi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 18:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 18:33"/>Mgbe <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwachara Ebraham okwu, ọ hapụrụ ya gawa ebe ọ na-aga. Ebraham laghachiri azụ nʼụlọ ya.<verse eid="GEN 18:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="GEN 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Mbibi Sọdọm na Gọmọra</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 19:1"/>Nʼoge anyasị, ndị mmụọ ozi abụọ ahụ bịarutere Sọdọm. Lọt nọ ala nʼọnụ ụzọ ama obodo ahụ. Mgbe ọ hụrụ ha, o biliri jekwuru ha, hulata ihu ya nʼala. <verse eid="GEN 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 19:2"/>Ọ sịrị, “Ndị nwe m, batanụ nʼụlọ ohu unu. Unu nwere ike saa ụkwụ unu, nọọkwa ọnọdụ abalị. Chi bọọ, unu nwere ike ibilikwa bido ịga nʼihu nʼije unu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 19:2">Ha zara sị, “Ee, anyị ga-edina nʼama.”<verse eid="GEN 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 19:3"/>Ma Lọt rịọsiri ha ike. Nʼikpeazụ ha sooro ya laa nʼụlọ ya. Ọ kwadooro ha ihe oriri, ya bụ achịcha na-ekoghị eko ka o ghere. Ha rikwara ya. <verse eid="GEN 19:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 19:4"/>Tupu ha abanye ịrahụ ụra, ndị ikom obodo ahụ, ndị ikom Sọdọm, bịara gbaa ụlọ ahụ gburugburu, ma ụmụ okorobịa ma ndị agadi, ndị niile si nʼakụkụ obodo ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 19:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 19:5"/>Ha kpọrọ Lọt oku sị ya, “Olee ebe ha nọ, bụ ndị ikom ahụ bịara nʼụlọ gị nʼabalị a? Kpọpụtara anyị ha ka anyị na ha dinakọọ.”<verse eid="GEN 19:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 19:6"/>Lọt pụkwuru ha nʼezi, mechie ụzọ ụlọ ya, <verse eid="GEN 19:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 19:7"/>sị ha, “Bikonu, ndị enyi m, unu emela ihe ọjọọ dị otu a. <verse eid="GEN 19:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 19:8"/>Leenụ, enwere m ụmụ nke aka m, ụmụ agbọghọ abụọ na-amaghị nwoke. Ka m kpọpụtara unu ha, ka unu mee ha ihe masịrị unu. Ma hapụnụ ndị ikom ndị a, nʼihi na ha bụ ndị batara izere ndụ nʼụlọ m.”<verse eid="GEN 19:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 19:9"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Pụọra anyị nʼụzọ. Mbịarambịa ka ị bụ! Leenụ mbịarambịa a! Ọ chọrọ ịbụ onye ikpe. Anyị mee gị ihe, ọ ga-ajọrọ gị njọ karịa ihe anyị ga-eme ha.” Ha nuru Lọt aka nughachi ya azụ, malite itiwa ọnụ ụzọ ụlọ ya.<verse eid="GEN 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 19:10"/>Ma ndị ikom ahụ nọ nʼụlọ Lọt, setịpụrụ aka ha dọbata ya nʼụlọ, ma mechie ụzọ ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 19:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 19:11"/>Ha tiri ndị ikom ndị ahụ nọ nʼọnụ ụzọ ihe otiti nke mere ka ha kpụọ ìsì, onye ukwu ha na onye nta ha. Nʼihi ya, ha enweghị ike ịchọta ọnụ ụzọ ụlọ ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 19:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 19:12"/>Ndị ikom abụọ ahụ gwara Lọt sị, “O nwere onye ọbụla ọzọ i nwere nʼebe a? Ndị ọgọ nwoke, maọbụ ụmụ gị ndị ikom, maọbụ ụmụ gị ndị inyom, na ọ bụ onye ọbụla bụ nke gị nʼobodo a. Site nʼebe a kpọpụ ha! <verse eid="GEN 19:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 19:13"/>Nʼihi na anyị na-aga imebi obodo a, mkpu akwa ruru <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ntị megide ndị bi nʼobodo a adịla ukwuu, nke mere o ji zite anyị ibibi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 19:14"/>Ya mere, Lọt pụrụ gaa gwa ndị ọgọ ya nwoke, ndị na-akwado ịlụ ụmụ ya ndị inyom, sị ha, “Ọsọ, sinụ nʼobodo a pụọ. Nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> na-akwado ibibi ya.” Ma ndị ọgọ ya nwoke ndị a chere na ọ na-egwu egwu.<verse eid="GEN 19:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 19:15"/>Nʼụtụtụ, mgbe chi na-abọta, ndị mmụọ ozi a kwagidere Lọt sị ya, “Ọsọ, kpọrọ nwunye gị na ụmụ gị ndị inyom abụọ ndị a site nʼebe a gbapụ, ma ọ bụghị ya, a ga-ekpochapụ unu nʼihi ajọ omume ndị obodo a.”<verse eid="GEN 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 19:16"/>Mgbe Lọt ka nọ na-eche ihe ọ ga-eme, ndị ikom ahụ jidere ya nʼaka, jidekwa nwunye ya, na ụmụ ya ndị inyom abụọ duru ha pụọ nʼobodo ahụ, nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nwere obi ebere nʼebe ha nọ. <verse eid="GEN 19:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 19:17"/>Mgbe ha si nʼime obodo kpọpụta ha, otu onye nʼime ha gwara ha sị, “Gbalaganụ nʼihi ndụ unu. Unu elekwala anya nʼazụ. Unu akwụsịkwala ebe ọbụla na mbara ala. Gbaganụ nʼugwu, nʼihi na ọ bụrụ na unu emeghị otu a, a ga-ekpochapụ unu.”<verse eid="GEN 19:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 19:18"/>Ma Lọt sịrị ha, “Mba, ndị nwe m, bikonu, <verse eid="GEN 19:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 19:19"/>ohu unu achọtala amara nʼihu unu, unu egosila m obi ebere dị ukwuu site nʼichebe ndụ m. Ma agaghị m enwe ike gbalaga nʼugwu ka mbibi a ghara ịdakwasị m, m nwụọ. <verse eid="GEN 19:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 19:20"/>Lee obodo dị nso nke m nwere ike ịgbaga. Ọ bụ obodo dị nta. Kwere ka m gbaga nʼebe ahụ. Obodo nta ka ọ bụ, ọ bụghị ya? Aga m echebekwa ndụ m na ya.”<verse eid="GEN 19:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 19:21"/>Ọ zara sị ya, “Ọ dị mma, aga m emere gị dịka arịrịọ gị si dị. Agaghị m emebi obodo nta ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 19:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 19:22"/>Ma mee ngwangwa, nʼihi na o nweghị ihe ọbụla m ga-eme tutu ruo mgbe i ruru nʼebe ahụ.” (Ọ bụ nke a mere e ji akpọ aha obodo ahụ Zoa.)<verse eid="GEN 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 19:23"/>Mgbe Lọt rutere obodo Zoa, anwụ awalitela nʼala ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 19:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 19:24"/>Mgbe ahụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sitere nʼeluigwe zokwasị obodo Sọdọm na Gọmọra nkume ọkụ nke <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mere ka o si nʼeluigwe zoo. <verse eid="GEN 19:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 19:25"/>Otu a ka o si kwatuo obodo ndị ahụ niile dị na mbara ala ahụ niile, na ndị niile bi nʼobodo ndị ahụ. O kwatukwara ihe niile na-epu nʼala. <verse eid="GEN 19:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 19:26"/>Ma mgbe nwunye Lọt lere anya nʼazụ, otu mgbe ahụ, ọ ghọrọ ogidi nnu.<verse eid="GEN 19:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 19:27"/>Nʼụtụtụ echi ya, Ebraham biliri jeruo ebe ahụ o guzoro nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nʼụbọchị gara aga. <verse eid="GEN 19:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 19:28"/>Ọ lepụrụ anya nʼebe obodo Sọdọm na Gọmọra dị, na nʼebe mbara ala ndị ahụ niile dị. Ọ hụrụ anwụrụ ọkụ dị ukwuu nke si nʼala ahụ na-alali elu. Anwụrụ ọkụ a dị ka anwụrụ ọkụ si nʼebe a kwanyere ọkụ na-enwusi ike.<verse eid="GEN 19:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 19:29"/>Ya mere, mgbe Chineke bibiri obodo ndị ahụ dị na mbara ala, o chetara Ebraham, kpọpụta Lọt site nʼoke mbibi ahụ e bibiri obodo ndị ahụ Lọt bi nʼime ha.<verse eid="GEN 19:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Lọt na ụmụ ya ndị inyom</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 19:30"/>Emesịa, Lọt na ụmụ ya ndị inyom abụọ hapụrụ obodo Zoa, nʼihi na ọ tụrụ egwu ibi nʼime Zoa. Ọ gara biri nʼime ọgba nkume ya na ụmụ ya ndị inyom abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 19:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 19:31"/>Otu ụbọchị, ada ya sịrị nke nta, “Nna anyị emeela agadi, ọ nwekwaghị nwoke ọbụla nọ nʼụwa a, onye ga-enye anyị ụmụ, dịka omenaala si dị nʼụwa niile. <verse eid="GEN 19:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 19:32"/>Ka anyị mee ka nna anyị ṅụọ mmanya, ka anyị na ya dinakọọ, ka anyị chebe agbụrụ anyị site na nna anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 19:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 19:33"/>Nʼabalị ahụ, ha mere ka nna ha ṅụọ mmanya, nke ada banyere soro nna ya dina. Ha abụọ nwere mmekọ. Ma ọ amaghị mgbe ada ya dinara maọbụ mgbe o bilikwara.<verse eid="GEN 19:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 19:34"/>Nʼechi ya, ada gwara nwanne ya nke nta, “Mụ na nna anyị dinara nʼabalị gara aga. Ka anyị mee ka ọ ṅụọkwa mmanya nʼabalị taa, ka ị gaakwa ka gị na ya dina. Ka anyị mee ka agbụrụ anyị dịgide site na nna anyị.” <verse eid="GEN 19:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 19:35"/>Ha mere ka nna ha ṅụọ mmanya nʼabalị ahụ, ada ya nke nta banyere ya na nna ya dinaa. Dịka ọ dịkwa na mbụ, nna ha amataghị mgbe o dinara ala maọbụ mgbe o bilitere.<verse eid="GEN 19:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 19:36"/>Ya mere, ụmụ ndị inyom Lọt abụọ ndị a tụrụ ime site nʼaka nna ha. <verse eid="GEN 19:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 19:37"/>Nke ada mụtara nwa nwoke onye ọ gụrụ Moab. Ọ bụ ya bụ nna nna ndị Moab ruo taa. <verse eid="GEN 19:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 19:38"/>Nwa ya nke nta mụtakwara nwa nwoke onye ọ gụrụ Ben-Ammi. Ọ bụ ya bụ nna nna ndị Amọn ruo taa.<verse eid="GEN 19:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="GEN 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Ebraham na Abimelek</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 20:1"/>Ugbu a, Ebraham sitere nʼebe ahụ bilie gaa na mpaghara Negev biri nʼebe dị nʼagbata Kadesh na Shua. Ọ nọrọ nʼobodo Gera nwa oge nta. <verse eid="GEN 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 20:2"/>Nʼebe ahụ, Ebraham kwuru maka Sera, nwunye ya, sị “Ọ bụ nwanne m nwanyị.” Abimelek, eze Gera, ziri ozi kpọrọ Sera.<verse eid="GEN 20:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 20:3"/>Ma Chineke bịakwutere Abimelek na nrọ nʼanyasị, sị ya, “Onye nwụrụ anwụ ka ị bụ, nʼihi nwanyị nke ị kpọọrọ, nwanyị a bụ onye nwere di.”<verse eid="GEN 20:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 20:4"/>Ma Abimelek abịabeghị Sera nso, ya mere o ji sị, “Onyenwe m, ị ga-ebibi mba aka ya dị ọcha? <verse eid="GEN 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 20:5"/>Ọ bụ na ya onwe ya agwaghị m sị, ‘ọ bụ nwanne m nwanyị,’ nke nwanyị nʼonwe ya, ekwuokwa sị, ‘Nwanne m nwoke ka ọ bụ?’ E ji m uche dị ọcha na aka dị ọcha mee ihe niile m mere.”<verse eid="GEN 20:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 20:6"/>Chineke zara ya sị, “Amaara m na i ji uche dị ọcha mee ihe i mere. Ọ bụ ya mere m ji gbochie gị imehie megide m. Ọ bụkwa ya mere m ji gbochie gị ịmetụ ya aka. <verse eid="GEN 20:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 20:7"/>Ugbu a, nyeghachi nwoke a nwunye ya. Nʼihi na ọ bụ onye amụma. Ọ ga-ekpere gị ekpere, ka ị ghara ịnwụ. Ma ọ bụrụ na i dughachịghị nwanyị a nye di ya, unu ga-anwụ, gị na ndị gị niile.”<verse eid="GEN 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 20:8"/>Ya mere, Abimelek biliri nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, kpọọ nzukọ nke ndịisi ozi ya niile, kọọrọ ha ihe mere. Ha tụrụ ụjọ nke ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 20:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 20:9"/>Emesịa, Abimelek kpọbatara Ebraham sị ya, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere anyị? Gịnị bụ ihe ọjọọ m mere i ji butere mụ na alaeze m ihe oke ikpe ọmụma dị otu a? Ihe a i mere m bụ ihe na-ekwesighị ekwesi.” <verse eid="GEN 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 20:10"/>Abimelek jụrụ Ebraham sị, “Ọ bụ gịnị ka ị hụrụ i jiri mee omume dị otu a?”<verse eid="GEN 20:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 20:11"/>Ebraham zara ya, “Nʼihi na asịrị m nʼobi m, ‘Nʼezie, ịtụ egwu Chineke adịghị nʼebe a. Ha ga-egbu m nʼihi nwunye m.’ <verse eid="GEN 20:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 20:12"/>Ewezugakwa nke a, ọ bụ nwanna m nwanyị, nʼihi na otu nna mụrụ anyị, ma ọ bụghị otu nne, tupu ọ bụrụ nwunye m. <verse eid="GEN 20:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 20:13"/>Mgbe Chineke sitere nʼezinaụlọ nna m zipụ m ije ebe dị anya, agwara m ya sị, ‘Otu a ka ị ga-esi gosi na ị hụrụ m nʼanya, ebe ọbụla anyị gara, kwuo gbasara m, “Onye a bụ nwanne m.” ’ ”<verse eid="GEN 20:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 20:14"/>Mgbe ahụ, Abimelek dupụtara atụrụ, na ehi, na ndị ohu ndị ikom, na ndị ohu ndị inyom, nye Ebraham. Ọ kpọnyekwara ya Sera nwunye ya. <verse eid="GEN 20:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 20:15"/>Abimelek sịrị, “Lee nʼala m niile, birikwa nʼebe ọbụla masịrị gị.”<verse eid="GEN 20:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 20:16"/>Mgbe ahụ, ọ sịrị Sera, “Ana m enye nwanne gị puku shekel ọlaọcha, ka ọ bụrụ ihe m ji kwụọ ụgwọ mmeso ọjọọ m mesoro gị. Ejikwa m ya na-egosi na ị bụ onye aka ya dị ọcha.”<verse eid="GEN 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 20:17"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ebraham kpọkuru Chineke nʼekpere. Chineke gwọrọ Abimelek na nwunye ya, na ndị inyom ndị ohu ya niile, ka ha nwee ike ịmụta ụmụ ọzọ. <verse eid="GEN 20:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 20:18"/>Nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mechiri akpanwa ndị inyom niile nọ nʼezinaụlọ Abimelek nʼihi Sera nwunye Ebraham.<verse eid="GEN 20:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="GEN 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọmụmụ Aịzik</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 21:1"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> jiri amara leta Sera dịka o kwuru na ọ ga-eme. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> meere Sera ihe o kwere na nkwa. <verse eid="GEN 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 21:2"/>Sera tụụrụ ime, mụọra Ebraham nwa nwoke nʼoge o merela agadi. Ọ mụrụ ya nʼoge ahụ a kara aka Chineke kwere ya na nkwa. <verse eid="GEN 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 21:3"/>Ebraham gụrụ nwantakịrị ahụ Sera mụụrụ ya aha, kpọọ ya Aịzik. <verse eid="GEN 21:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 21:4"/>Mgbe Aịzik nọrọ ụbọchị asatọ site nʼụbọchị a mụrụ ya, Ebraham biri ya ugwu dịka Chineke si nye ya nʼiwu. <verse eid="GEN 21:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 21:5"/>Ebraham agbaala narị afọ mgbe a mụrụ Aịzik nwa ya nwoke.<verse eid="GEN 21:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 21:6"/>Nʼoge ahụ, Sera kwuru sị, “Chineke ewetarala m ọchị. Ndị niile nụrụ akụkọ a ga-esoro m chịa ọchị.” <verse eid="GEN 21:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 21:7"/>O kwukwara sị, “Onye gaara agwa Ebraham sị ya na Sera ga-azụlite ụmụntakịrị. Ma otu ọ dị, amụtarala m ya nwa nwoke ugbu a o merela agadi.”<verse eid="GEN 21:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ebraham achụpụ Hega na nwa ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 21:8"/>Nwata ahụ tokwara, ruo mgbe a kwụsịrị ya ara.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼusoro omenaala, ọ bụ mgbe nwantakịrị gbara afọ abụọ, maọbụ atọ ka a na-akwụsị ya ara. Nʼoge ochie, ị kwụsị nwantakịrị ara na-abụ oge mmemme na oke oriri.</char></note> Nʼụbọchị ahụ a kwụsịrị ya ara, Ebraham kpọrọ oriri. <verse eid="GEN 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 21:9"/>Ma mgbe Sera hụrụ na nwa nwoke ahụ Hega onye Ijipt mụtaara Ebraham nọ na-akwa emo, <verse eid="GEN 21:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 21:10"/>ọ gwara Ebraham okwu sị ya, “Chụpụ ohu nwanyị a na nwa ya. Nʼihi na nwa nwoke ohu nwanyị agaghị eso nwa m nwoke Aịzik keta oke nʼihe nketa.”<verse eid="GEN 21:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 21:11"/>Okwu a wutere Ebraham nke ukwuu nʼihi na ihe banyere nwa ya nwoke Ishmel na-emetụ ya nʼobi. <verse eid="GEN 21:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 21:12"/>Ma Chineke gwara Ebraham sị, “Ekwela ka obi jọọ gị njọ nʼihi nwantakịrị a na ohu gị nwanyị. Gee ntị nʼihe ọbụla Sera gwara gị. Nʼihi na ọ bụ site nʼAịzik ka a ga-akpọ mkpụrụ gị aha. <verse eid="GEN 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 21:13"/>Aga m eme ka nwa gị nwoke nke ohu gị mụtara ghọọ mba dị ukwuu, nʼihi na mkpụrụ afọ gị ka ọ bụ.”<verse eid="GEN 21:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 21:14"/>Ebraham biliri nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, kwadoo ihe oriri na mmiri ọṅụṅụ nke dị nʼime karama akpụkpọ, bunye ha Hega. O bukwasịrị ha nʼubu Hega, zipụ ya na nwa ya nwoke. Hega si nʼebe ahụ pụọ wagharịa nʼime ọzara Bịasheba.<verse eid="GEN 21:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 21:15"/>Mgbe mmiri dị na karama akpụkpọ ahụ gwụsịrị, o nibere nwantakịrị ahụ nʼokpuru otu osisi ọhịa. <verse eid="GEN 21:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 21:16"/>Hapụ ya gaa nọdụ ala nʼebe dịtụ anya, ihe dịka narị nzọ ụkwụ, nʼihi na o kwuru nʼobi ya sị, “Achọghị m ịhụ nwantakịrị nwoke a anya mgbe ọ na-anwụ.” Mgbe ọ nọdụrụ ebe ahụ, o bidoro ịkwa akwa.<verse eid="GEN 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 21:17"/>Ma Chineke nụrụ ịkwa akwa nwantakịrị nwoke ahụ. Mmụọ ozi Chineke sikwa na mbara eluigwe kpọọ Hega oku sị ya, “Hega, gịnị na-eme gị? Atụla egwu, nʼihi na Chineke anụla<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21:17 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Chineke anụla </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Chineke na-anụ, bụ ihe Ishmel pụtara.</char></note> olu akwa nwantakịrị ahụ nʼebe ahụ o dina. <verse eid="GEN 21:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 21:18"/>Gaa kulite nwantakịrị ahụ kasịe ya obi, nʼihi na aga m eme ya ka ọ ghọọ mba dị ukwuu.”<verse eid="GEN 21:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 21:19"/>Mgbe ahụ, Chineke meghere anya ya, mee ka ọ hụ olulu mmiri dị nʼebe ahụ. Ọ gara kujuo karama akpụkpọ ahụ mmiri, ma nye nwantakịrị ahụ mmiri ka ọ ṅụọ.<verse eid="GEN 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 21:20"/>Chineke nọnyeere nwantakịrị ahụ mgbe ọ na-eto. O biri nʼọzara ahụ ghọọ onye na-agba àkụ nke ọma. <verse eid="GEN 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 21:21"/>Mgbe o bi nʼọzara Paran, nne ya chọtaara ya nwunye site nʼIjipt.<verse eid="GEN 21:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Nkwekọrịta e nwere na Bịasheba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 21:22"/>Nʼoge a, Abimelek na Fikọl onyeisi ndị agha ya, bịakwutere Ebraham sị ya, “Chineke nọnyeere gị nʼihe niile ị na-eme. <verse eid="GEN 21:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 21:23"/>Ugbu a, ṅụọra m iyi nʼaha Chineke na ị gaghị aghọgbu m maọbụ ghọgbuo ụmụ m, maọbụ ụmụ ụmụ m. Gosi m nʼobodo a i bi nʼime ya dịka onye ọbịa ụdị obiọma m gosiri gị.”<verse eid="GEN 21:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 21:24"/>Ebraham zara sị ya, “Ọ dị mma, aga m aṅụrụ gị iyi.”<verse eid="GEN 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 21:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ebraham kọsaara Abimelek ihe banyere olulu mmiri nke ndị na-ejere ya ozi ji anya ike nara ndị na-ejere Ebraham ozi. <verse eid="GEN 21:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 21:26"/>Abimelek zara sị, “Amaghị m onye mere ihe dị otu a. Ị gwaghị m na ihe dị otu a mere, anụghị m ya ma ọ bụghị naanị taa.”<verse eid="GEN 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 21:27"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ebraham kpụpụtara atụrụ, na ehi, nye Abimelek. Ha abụọ gbara ndụ nkwekọrịta. <verse eid="GEN 21:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 21:28"/>Mgbe Ebraham sitere nʼigwe atụrụ ya wepụta nne atụrụ asaa nupu ha ka ha nọpụ iche, <verse eid="GEN 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 21:29"/>Abimelek jụrụ Ebraham sị ya, “Gịnị ka i ji nne atụrụ asaa ndị a ị họpụtara iche eme?”<verse eid="GEN 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 21:30"/>Ebraham zara sị, “Nabata ụmụ atụrụ asaa ndị a dịka ihe akaebe na-egosi na ọ bụ m gwuru olulu mmiri a.”<verse eid="GEN 21:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 21:31"/>Ya mere, e bidoro ịkpọ ebe ahụ Bịasheba, nʼihi na nʼebe ahụ ka mmadụ abụọ a nọ ṅụrịtaara onwe ha iyi.<verse eid="GEN 21:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 21:32"/>Mgbe ha gbachara ndụ nkwekọrịta na Bịasheba, Abimelek na Fikọl onyeisi agha ya laghachiri azụ nʼala ndị Filistia. <verse eid="GEN 21:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 21:33"/>Ebraham kụrụ osisi tamarisk na Bịasheba. Ebe ahụ ka ọ nọ kpọkuo aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Chineke ebighị ebi. <verse eid="GEN 21:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 21:34"/>Ebraham bigidere nʼala ndị Filistia ogologo oge.<verse eid="GEN 21:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="GEN 22"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụnwa a nwara Ebraham</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 22:1"/>Mgbe ihe ndị a gasịrị, Chineke nwara Ebraham. Ọ sịrị ya, “Ebraham.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 22:1">Ebraham zara sị, “Lekwa m.”<verse eid="GEN 22:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 22:2"/>Chineke sịrị, “Duru nwa gị nwoke, naanị otu nwa gị nwoke, Aịzik onye ị hụrụ nʼanya, gaa nʼala Mọrịa. Jiri ya chụọrọ m aja nsure ọkụ nʼelu otu nʼime ugwu dị nʼebe m ga-egosi gị.”<verse eid="GEN 22:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 22:3"/>Nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, Ebraham biliri kwadoo ịnyịnya ibu ya. O duuru ndị ikom abụọ na-ejere ya ozi, na nwa ya nwoke Aịzik. O gbutere nkụ ga-ezuru ya ịchụ aja nsure ọkụ, bilie gawa ebe ahụ Chineke gwara ya maka ya. <verse eid="GEN 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 22:4"/>Nʼụbọchị nke atọ, Ebraham lepụrụ anya hụ ebe ahụ nʼebe dị anya. <verse eid="GEN 22:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 22:5"/>Ọ gwara ndị na-ejere ya ozi sị, “Nọdụnụ nʼebe a, unu na ịnyịnya ibu anyị, ka mụ na nwokorobịa a gaa nʼebe ahụ. Anyị feecha ofufe, anyị ga-alọghachikwute unu ọzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 22:6"/>Ebraham boro nwa ya nwoke Aịzik ukwu nkụ ahụ e ji achụ aja nsure ọkụ nʼisi, ma ya onwe ya jidere ọkụ na mma. <verse eid="GEN 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 22:7"/>Aịzik gwara nna ya Ebraham sị, “Nna m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 22:7">Ebraham zara, “Ehee, nwa m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 22:7">Aịzik sịrị, “Ọkụ na nkụ dị nʼebe a, olee nwa atụrụ e ji achụ aja nsure ọkụ?”<verse eid="GEN 22:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 22:8"/>Ebraham zara, “Nwa m, Chineke nʼonwe ya ga-eweta nwa atụrụ e ji achụ aja nsure ọkụ.” Ha abụọ gakwara nʼihu nʼije ha.<verse eid="GEN 22:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 22:9"/>Mgbe ha ruru ebe ahụ Chineke gwara ya maka ya, Ebraham wuru ebe ịchụ aja nʼebe ahụ, doo nkụ ndị ahụ niile nʼusoro nʼelu ya. O kere nwa ya Aịzik agbụ, tụkwasị ya nʼelu ebe ịchụ aja ahụ, na nʼelu nkụ ndị ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 22:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 22:10"/>Mgbe ahụ Ebraham setịpụrụ aka ya, welite mma ka o gbuo nwa ya nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 22:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 22:11"/>Ma mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> si nʼeluigwe kpọọ ya oku sị ya, “Ebraham! Ebraham!”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 22:11">Ebraham zara, “Lekwa m nʼebe a.”<verse eid="GEN 22:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 22:12"/>Ọ sịrị ya, “Emetụkwala nwokorobịa ahụ aka. Emekwala ya ihe ọbụla. Nʼihi na amatala m ugbu a na ị na-atụ egwu Chineke, ebe ọ bụ na i kwenyere iji nwa gị nwoke, naanị otu nwa nwoke i nwere chụọrọ m aja.”<verse eid="GEN 22:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 22:13"/>Ebraham leliri anya hụ otu ebule nke eriri ọhịa jidere na mpi ya. Ebraham gara jide ebule ahụ, were ya chụọ aja nsure ọkụ nʼọnọdụ nwa ya nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 22:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 22:14"/>Ya mere, Ebraham kpọrọ ebe ahụ, “<char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ga-arọpụta.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Onyenwe anyị Jaire</char></note>” Ya mere ruo taa a na-asị, “Nʼugwu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, a ga-arọpụta.”<verse eid="GEN 22:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 22:15"/>Mmụọ ozi <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sitere nʼeluigwe kpọọ Ebraham oku nke ugboro abụọ, <verse eid="GEN 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 22:16"/>sị, “Mụ onwe m, bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, ji onwe m na-aṅụ iyi na-ekwupụta sị, ebe ọ bụ na i mere ihe dị otu a, na i kwenyere iji nwa gị nwoke, naanị otu nwoke i nwere chụọrọ m aja, <verse eid="GEN 22:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 22:17"/>aga m agọzi gị nʼezie, mekwa ka ụmụ ụmụ gị mụbaa nʼọnụọgụgụ dịka kpakpando nke mbara eluigwe na dịka aja dị nʼọnụ mmiri osimiri. Ụmụ ụmụ gị ga-enwetara onwe ha ọnụ ụzọ ama ndị iro ha. <verse eid="GEN 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 22:18"/>Sitekwa na mkpụrụ gị ka a ga-agọzikwa agbụrụ niile nọ nʼụwa, nʼihi na i rubeere m isi.”<verse eid="GEN 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 22:19"/>Emesịa, Ebraham laghachikwuru ndị na-ejere ya ozi. Ha niile laghachikwara Bịasheba. Ebraham birikwara na Bịasheba.<verse eid="GEN 22:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụ ụmụ Nahọ</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 22:20"/>Mgbe ihe ndị a gasịrị, e ziri Ebraham ozi si ya, “Lee, Milka ya onwe ya amụkwaarala nwanne gị nwoke bụ Nahọ, ụmụ ndị ikom.<verse eid="GEN 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 22:21"/>Aha ha bụ Uz, onye bụ ọkpara, na Buz nwanne ya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 22:21">Kemuel bụ (nna Aram),<verse eid="GEN 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 22:22"/>Kesed, Hazọ, Pildash, Jidlaf na Betuel.”<verse eid="GEN 22:22"/></para>
  <para style="li3">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 22:23"/>Betuel mụrụ Ribeka.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 22:23">Milka mụtaara Nahọ, nwanne Ebraham ụmụ ndị ikom asatọ ndị a.<verse eid="GEN 22:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 22:24"/>Iko ya nwanyị, onye aha ya bụ Reuma, mụkwaara ya ụmụ ndị ikom.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 22:24">Ha bụ Teba, Gaham, Tahash na Maaka.<verse eid="GEN 22:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="GEN 23"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụ Sera</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 23:1"/>Sera dị ndụ ruo narị afọ na iri afọ abụọ na asaa. <verse eid="GEN 23:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 23:2"/>Ọ nwụrụ na Kiriat Arba (nke bụ Hebrọn), nʼala Kenan. Ebraham ruru ụjụ nʼihi Sera, kwaa akwa nke ukwuu nʼihi ọnwụ ya.<verse eid="GEN 23:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 23:3"/>Ebraham sitere nʼebe ozu nwunye ya dị pụọ, jekwuru ụmụ Het gwa ha sị, <verse eid="GEN 23:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 23:4"/>“Abụ m ọbịa na onye obodo ọzọ nʼetiti unu. Resinụ m ala m ji eme ebe olili nʼebe a, ka m nwee ike lie onye m nwụrụ anwụ.”<verse eid="GEN 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 23:5"/>Ụmụ Het zara Ebraham sị, <verse eid="GEN 23:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 23:6"/>“Nna anyị ukwu, gee anyị ntị. Nwa eze dị ukwu ka ị bụ nʼetiti anyị, lie onye gị nwụrụ anwụ nʼili ahụ nke kachasị mma nʼime ili anyị nwere. O nweghị onye ọbụla nʼime anyị ga-ajụ inye gị ala olili ya maka ili onye gị nwụrụ anwụ.”<verse eid="GEN 23:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 23:7"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ebraham biliri kpọọ isiala nʼihu ndị nwe ala, bụ ndị Het, <verse eid="GEN 23:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 23:8"/>sị ha, “Ọ bụrụ ọchịchọ unu ka m lie onye m nwụrụ anwụ, geenụ m ntị ma rịọrọ m Efrọn nwa Zoha, <verse eid="GEN 23:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 23:9"/>ka o resi m ọgba Makipela, nke bụ nke ya, nke dị na ngwụsị ọhịa ya. Gwa ya ka o resi m ya nʼọnụ ahịa o ruru ka ọ bụrụ ebe olili m nwere nʼetiti unu.”<verse eid="GEN 23:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 23:10"/>Efrọn onye Het nʼonwe ya so nọdụ nʼebe ahụ nʼetiti ndị ya. Ọ zara Ebraham nʼihu ndị Het niile bịara nʼọnụ ụzọ ama obodo <verse eid="GEN 23:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 23:11"/>sị ya, “Mba! Nna m ukwu, gee m ntị. Ana m enye gị ala ahụ na ọgba dị nʼime ya nʼihu ndị a niile bụ ndị m. Gaa lie onye gị nwụrụ anwụ nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 23:12"/>Ọzọ Ebraham kpọrọ isiala nye ndị nwe ala, <verse eid="GEN 23:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 23:13"/>ọ sịrị Efrọn, nʼihu ha niile, “Biko gee m ntị, aga m akwụ gị ọnụahịa iji zụọ ala ahụ. Nara m ya ka m nwee ike lie onye m nwụrụ anwụ nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 23:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 23:14"/>Efrọn zara Ebraham, <verse eid="GEN 23:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 23:15"/>“Gee m ntị, nna m ukwu, ọ bụ ezie na ala ahụ ruru narị shekel ọlaọcha anọ, ma gịnị ka nke a bụ nʼetiti mụ na gị? Gaa lie onye gị nwụrụ anwụ nʼime ya.”<verse eid="GEN 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 23:16"/>Ebraham kwenyere nʼego ole Efrọn chọrọ ka ọ kwụọ. O ji ihe ọtụtụ tụpụtara Efrọn ego ruru ọnụahịa ọ kpọrọ aha nʼihu ndị Het niile, narị shekel ọlaọcha anọ, dịka ihe ọtụtụ nke dị nʼoge ahụ nʼetiti ndị na-azụ ahịa.<verse eid="GEN 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 23:17"/>Site nʼoge ahụ, ala ahụ Efrọn nwere na Makipela, nke dị nso na Mamre, ala ahụ na ọgba dị nʼime ya, na osisi niile dị nʼime ala ahụ niile gburugburu, <verse eid="GEN 23:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 23:18"/>ghọrọ nke Ebraham dịka ihe nzụta ya nʼihu ụmụ Het, nʼihu ndị niile ndị bịara nʼọnụ ụzọ e si abata obodo ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 23:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 23:19"/>Emesịa, Ebraham liri Sera nwunye ya nʼime ọgba ahụ dị nʼala dị na Makipela na nso Mamre (nke dị na Hebrọn) nʼala ndị Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 23:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 23:20"/>Ya mere, ala ahụ na ọgba dị nʼime ya ka ndị Het resiri Ebraham ka ọ bụrụ nke ya, ebe a na-eli ozu.<verse eid="GEN 23:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="GEN 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Aịzik na Ribeka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 24:1"/>Ugbu a, Ebraham aghọọla agadi nʼahụ ya ma nʼọnụọgụgụ afọ ya. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> agọziela ya nʼụzọ niile <verse eid="GEN 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 24:2"/>Ọ gwara onyeisi ndị ozi nʼụlọ ya, onye nke na-elekọta ihe niile o nwere sị ya, “Tinye aka gị nʼokpuru apata m.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">24:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼusoro ịṅụ iyi a, ọ pụtara na ọgbụgba ndụ a maọbụ nkwa ahụ, ga-adịgide nʼagbụrụ Ebraham niile. Jenesis 47:29.</char></note> <verse eid="GEN 24:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 24:3"/>Achọrọ m ka i jiri aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nke eluigwe na ụwa, ṅụọra m iyi, na ị gaghị achọtara nwa m nwoke nwunye site nʼetiti ndị Kenan, ndị m bi nʼetiti ha. <verse eid="GEN 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 24:4"/>Kama na ị ga-aga nʼala nke m na ụmụnna m lụtara nwa m, bụ Aịzik, nwunye nʼetiti ụmụnna m.”<verse eid="GEN 24:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 24:5"/>Ohu ahụ jụrụ ya, “Ọ bụrụkwanụ na nwaagbọghọ ahụ achọghị isoro m lọghachi nʼebe a, m ga-akpọrọ nwa gị nwoke laghachi nʼobodo i si bịa?”<verse eid="GEN 24:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 24:6"/>Ebraham sịrị ya, “Lezie anya hụ na ị kpọghachighị nwa m nwoke nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 24:7"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Chineke nke eluigwe, bụ onye kpọpụtara m site nʼụlọ nna m nakwa obodo nke aka m, onye ahụ gwara m okwu ma kwem nkwa site nʼịṅụ iyi nye sị, ‘Aga m enye ụmụ ụmụ gị ala a.’ Ọ ga-ezipụ mmụọ ozi ya ka ọ gaa nʼihu gị ka i nwee ike inwetara nwa m nwoke nwunye site nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 24:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 24:8"/>Ma ọ bụrụ na nwanyị ahụ achọghị isoro gị lọghachi, mgbe ahụ, ị ga-abụ onye nwere onwe ya pụọ nʼiyi a ị ṅụrụ. Naanị na ị gaghị eme ka nwa m nwoke laghachi nʼebe ahụ.” <verse eid="GEN 24:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 24:9"/>Ya mere, ohu ahụ tinyere aka ya nʼokpuru apata nna ya ukwu Ebraham, ṅụọ iyi banyere okwu ndị a.<verse eid="GEN 24:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 24:10"/>Emesịa, ohu a duuru ịnyịnya kamel iri nʼime ndị nna ya ukwu nwere pụọ. O sitekwara nʼaka nna ya ukwu were ihe ọma dị iche iche maka njem a, gawa Aram Naharaim, rute nʼobodo Nahọ. <verse eid="GEN 24:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 24:11"/>O mere ka ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ makpuru ala nʼakụkụ olulu mmiri dị nʼazụ obodo ahụ. Ọ bụ nʼoge anyasị, oge ụmụ nwanyị ji apụta iseta mmiri nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 24:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 24:12"/>Mgbe ahụ, o kpere ekpere sị, “<char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Chineke nke nna m ukwu Ebraham, mee ka ihe gaara m nke ọma taa. Gosi nna m ukwu Ebraham obi ebere gị. <verse eid="GEN 24:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 24:13"/>Lee, ana m eguzo nʼakụkụ isi iyi mmiri a, ụmụ nwanyị ndị obodo a na-abịa iseta mmiri. <verse eid="GEN 24:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 24:14"/>Kwere ka o si otu a dịrị na nwaagbọghọ nke m ga-asị, ‘Biko, zie ite gị ka m ṅụrụ mmiri.’ Ọ bụrụ na onye ahụ asị m, ‘Ṅụọ, aga m ekutekwa mmiri nke ịnyịnya kamel gị ga-aṅụ,’ ka onye ahụ bụrụ onye ị họpụtara ohu gị Aịzik. Nʼụzọ dị otu a ka m ga-esi mata na i gosila nna m ukwu obi ebere.”<verse eid="GEN 24:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 24:15"/>Tupu o kpechaa ekpere a, lekwa Ribeka ada Betuel, nwa nwoke Milka, onye bụ nwunye Nahọ, nwanne Ebraham. Ọ na-apụta bukwasị ite nʼubu ya. <verse eid="GEN 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 24:16"/>Ọ bụ nwaagbọghọ mara mma nke ukwuu, onye na-amatabeghị nwoke, nke nwoke ọbụla na-edinabeghị. Ọ gara nʼolulu mmiri kujuo ite ya si nʼebe ahụ na-arịgopụta.<verse eid="GEN 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 24:17"/>Ohu ahụ mere ngwangwa jekwuru ya sị ya, “Biko nyetụ m mmiri si nʼite mmiri gị.”<verse eid="GEN 24:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 24:18"/>Ọ mere ngwangwa budata ite ahụ nʼaka ya, hulata ya si ya, “Ṅụọ, onyenwe m.”<verse eid="GEN 24:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 24:19"/>Mgbe o nyechara ya mmiri, ọ sịrị, “Aga m ekutekwa mmiri nye ịnyịnya kamel gị ndị a ruo mgbe ha ṅụjuru afọ.” <verse eid="GEN 24:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 24:20"/>Ngwangwa, ọ wụpụrụ mmiri dị nʼite ya nʼime ihe anụ ụlọ ji aṅụ mmiri, gbara ọsọ gaa kute mmiri ọzọ na-agbanye nʼime ihe ahụ. O kugidere mmiri tutu ruo mgbe ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ ṅụjuchara afọ. <verse eid="GEN 24:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 24:21"/>Mgbe ihe ndị a na-eme, ohu ahụ gbara nkịtị na-ele ya anya ịchọpụta ma <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> emeela ka ije ya bụrụ ihe gara nke ọma.<verse eid="GEN 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 24:22"/>Mgbe ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ ṅụsịrị mmiri, nwoke ahụ wepụtara mgbanimi ọlaedo nke ọtụtụ ya bụ otu beka,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">24:22 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ọkara shekel</char></note> na mgbaaka ọlaedo abụọ nke ọtụtụ ha bụ shekel iri. <verse eid="GEN 24:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 24:23"/>Ọ jụrụ ya sị, “Nwa onye ka ị bụ? Ohere ọ dị nʼụlọ nna gị ebe mụ na ịnyịnya kamel ndị a ga-anọ nʼabalị a?”<verse eid="GEN 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 24:24"/>Ọ zara sị ya, “Abụ m nwa Betuel, nwa Milka nwunye Nahọ.” <verse eid="GEN 24:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 24:25"/>Ọ sịkwara, “Anyị nwere nri anụ ụlọ, nweekwa ebe ị ga-edina nʼabalị a.”<verse eid="GEN 24:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 24:26"/>Nwoke ahụ hulatara ala kpọọ isiala nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. <verse eid="GEN 24:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 24:27"/>Kwuo sị, “Ngọzị dịrị <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, bụ Chineke nna m ukwu Ebraham, onye na-esitebeghị nʼebe nna m ukwu nọ wezuga ebere ya na ikwesi ntụkwasị obi ya. Ma banyere mụ onwe m, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> e duola m nʼije a, kpọrọ m rute nʼụlọ ndị ikwu nna m ukwu.”<verse eid="GEN 24:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 24:28"/>Nwaagbọghọ ahụ gbalara gaa kọọrọ ndị ezinaụlọ nne ya ihe ndị a. <verse eid="GEN 24:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 24:29"/>Ribeka nwere otu nwanne nwoke aha ya bụ Leban. Leban gbara ọsọ gbakwuje nwoke ahụ nʼisi iyi mmiri ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 24:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 24:30"/>Mgbe ọ hụrụ mgbanimi, na mgbaaka ndị ahụ nwanne ya nwanyị yi nʼaka ya, ma nụkwa ihe Ribeka kwuru banyere ihe nwoke ahụ gwara ya, o jekwuru nwoke ahụ, hụ ya ka ya na ịnyịnya kamel ya guzo nʼakụkụ olulu mmiri. <verse eid="GEN 24:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 24:31"/>Ọ sịrị ya, “Bịa, gị onye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gọziri. Gịnị mere i ji guzo nʼebe a. Edozielara m gị ụlọ ebe ị ga-edina na ebe ịnyịnya kamel ndị a ga-anọ.”<verse eid="GEN 24:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 24:32"/>Ya mere, nwoke ahụ gara nʼụlọ, ebe Leban nyere aka butukwaara ya ibu nke ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ bu. E wetara nri nye ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ, wetara ya mmiri nke ya na ndị ikom so ya ji saa ụkwụ ha. <verse eid="GEN 24:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 24:33"/>E doziri ya ihe oriri, ma ọ zara sị, “Agaghị m eri ihe ọbụla tutu ruo mgbe m kwuru ihe m ji bịa.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:33">Leban sịrị, “Ngwa, kwuonụ.”<verse eid="GEN 24:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 24:34"/>Ya mere, ọ sịrị, “Abụ m ohu Ebraham. <verse eid="GEN 24:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 24:35"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> agọziela nna m ukwu, mee ya ka ọ bụrụ ọgaranya. O nyela ya igwe atụrụ, na igwe ehi, na ọlaọcha na ọlaedo, na ọtụtụ ndị ohu nwoke na nwanyị, na ịnyịnya kamel, na ịnyịnya ibu. <verse eid="GEN 24:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 24:36"/>Sera nwunye nna m ukwu mụtaara ya otu nwa nwoke mgbe o merela agadi. Ihe niile nna m ukwu nwere ka o nyefere nwa ahụ nʼaka. <verse eid="GEN 24:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 24:37"/>Nna m ukwu mere ka m ṅụọra ya iyi sị, ‘Ị gaghị esite nʼetiti ụmụ ndị inyom Kenan ndị anyị bi nʼala ha lụtara nwa m nwoke nwunye. <verse eid="GEN 24:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 24:38"/>Kama ị ga-aga nʼezinaụlọ nna m, na nke ndị ikwu m chọtara nwa m nwoke nwunye.’<verse eid="GEN 24:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 24:39"/>“Mgbe ahụ, ajụrụ m nna m ukwu, ‘Ọ bụrụkwanụ na nwanyị ahụ ekweghị iso m lọghachi?’<verse eid="GEN 24:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 24:40"/>“Ọ sịrị, ‘<char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, onye m na-ejegharị nʼihu ya, ga-eziga mmụọ ozi ya ka o soro gị gaa ime ka ije gị nwee isi, ka i nwee ike chọtara nwa m nwoke nwanyị site nʼetiti ndị ikwu m na ezinaụlọ nna m. <verse eid="GEN 24:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 24:41"/>Ị ga-abụ onye nwere onwe gị site nʼiyi ị ṅụrụ ma ọ bụrụ na mgbe i gakwuru ndị ikwu m, ha jụrụ ịkpọnye gị nwanyị ahụ. Ị ga-abụ onye nwere onwe gị site nʼiyi ị ṅụrụ m.’<verse eid="GEN 24:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 24:42"/>“Mgbe m rutere nʼisi iyi mmiri taa, ekwuru m sị, ‘<char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke nna m ukwu Ebraham, ọ bụrụ na ọ masị gị, biko mee ka ije a m bịara bụrụ nke ga-aga nke ọma. <verse eid="GEN 24:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 24:43"/>Lee, ka m na-eguzo nʼakụkụ isi iyi mmiri a, ka nwaagbọghọ ahụ bịara ikuru mmiri nke m ga-asị, “Biko kwere ka m si nʼite gị ṅụrụtụ ntakịrị mmiri,” <verse eid="GEN 24:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="GEN 24:44"/>ma ọ bụrụ na ọ sị m, “Ṅụọ, aga m ekutekwa mmiri nye ịnyịnya kamel gị ndị a,” ka onye dị otu a bụrụ nwanyị ahụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> chọtaara Aịzik nwa nna m ukwu.’<verse eid="GEN 24:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="GEN 24:45"/>“Tupu m kpesịa ekpere a nʼobi m, lekwa Ribeka ka o bụ ite mmiri ya nʼubu ya na-abịa. Ọ gbadara nʼisi iyi mmiri ahụ kute mmiri. Asịrị m ya, ‘Biko nye m mmiri ka m ṅụọ.’<verse eid="GEN 24:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="GEN 24:46"/>“Ngwangwa, o sitere nʼubu ya budata ite, sị m, ‘Ṅụọ, aga m ekutekwa mmiri nke ịnyịnya kamel ndị a ga-aṅụ.’ Ya mere, aṅụrụ m, o nyekwara ịnyịnya kamel m ndị ahụ mmiri ha ṅụrụ.<verse eid="GEN 24:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="GEN 24:47"/>“Mgbe ahụ, ajụrụ m ya, ‘Nwa onye ka ị bụ?’</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:47">“Ọ sịrị m, ‘Abụ m nwa Betuel onye bụ nwa Nahọ nke Milka mụtaara ya.’</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:47">“Mgbe ahụ etinyere m ya mgbanimi ahụ nʼimi ya, tinyekwa ọlaaka ahụ nʼaka ya abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 24:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="GEN 24:48"/>Ehulatara m ala kpọọ isiala nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Etoro m <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Chineke nke nna m ukwu Ebraham, onye duru m nʼezi ụzọ inweta nwa nwanne nna m ukwu dịka nwunye nwa ya nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 24:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="GEN 24:49"/>Ugbu a, ọ bụrụ na unu ga-egosi nna m ukwu obiọma na ikwesi ntụkwasị obi gwanụ m. Ọ bụrụkwanụ na ọ gaghị esi otu a dịrị, gwanụ m ka m mata ụzọ m ga-agbaso.”<verse eid="GEN 24:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="GEN 24:50"/>Leban na Betuel zara sị ya, “Ihe niile si nʼaka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Anyị enweghị ike ịgwa gị okwu ọjọọ maọbụ nke ọma. <verse eid="GEN 24:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="GEN 24:51"/>Lee Ribeka, kpọrọ ya laa, ka ọ bụrụ nwunye nwa nna gị ukwu, dịka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> kwuru.”<verse eid="GEN 24:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="GEN 24:52"/>Mgbe ohu Ebraham nụrụ ihe ha kwuru, ọ dara nʼala kpọọ isiala nye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. <verse eid="GEN 24:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="GEN 24:53"/>Mgbe ahụ kwa, ohu ahụ wepụtara ihe ịchọ mma ọlaedo, na ọlaọcha dị iche iche na uwe nye ha Ribeka. Ọ wepụtakwara onyinye ndị ọzọ dị oke ọnụahịa nye nwanne ya nwoke na nne ya. <verse eid="GEN 24:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="GEN 24:54"/>Emesịa, mgbe ihe ndị a gasịrị, ya na ndị ikom so ya riri, ṅụọ, dinaakwa nʼabalị ahụ.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:54">Mgbe ha si nʼụra teta, o kwuru sị, “Zilaga m ka m lakwuru nna m ukwu.”<verse eid="GEN 24:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="GEN 24:55"/>Ma Leban na nne ya zara sị ya, “Ka nwantakịrị nwanyị a nọnyere anyị ihe dịka ụbọchị iri tupu o soro gị laa.”<verse eid="GEN 24:55"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="56" style="v" sid="GEN 24:56"/>Ma ọ zara ha sị, “Unu egbochila anyị. Ebe ọ bụ na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> emeela ka ije m bụrụ ihe gara nke ọma, zilaga m ka m laghachikwuru nna m ukwu.”<verse eid="GEN 24:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="GEN 24:57"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Ka anyị kpọọ nwantakịrị nwanyị ahụ jụọ ya ihe bụ uche ya.” <verse eid="GEN 24:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="GEN 24:58"/>Ya mere ha kpọrọ Ribeka jụọ ya sị, “Ị ga-eso nwoke a gaa?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:58">Ọ zara sị, “E, aga m aga.”<verse eid="GEN 24:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="GEN 24:59"/>Ya mere, ha zipụrụ nwanne ha nwanyị Ribeka, tinyere nwanyị lekọtara ya anya mgbe ọ dị na nwantakịrị, na ohu Ebraham na ndị ikom so ya. <verse eid="GEN 24:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="GEN 24:60"/>Ha gọziri Ribeka sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 24:60">“Nwanne anyị nwanyị mụọ ọmụmụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 24:60">mụruo puku kwụrụ puku,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 24:60">ka mkpụrụ afọ gị nwetara onwe ha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 24:60">ọnụ ụzọ ama ndị iro ha.”<verse eid="GEN 24:60"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="GEN 24:61"/>Ribeka biliri, ya na ndị inyom na-ejere ya ozi, ha rigoro nʼelu ịnyịnya kamel ndị ahụ, soro nwoke ahụ. Ya mere, ohu ahụ duuru Ribeka laa.<verse eid="GEN 24:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="GEN 24:62"/>Nʼoge a, Aịzik bịara nʼebe mbata obodo Bịa-Lahai-Rọị nʼihi na o bi na Negev. <verse eid="GEN 24:62"/><verse number="63" style="v" sid="GEN 24:63"/>Aịzik pụtara ịtụgharị uche nʼọhịa nʼoge uhuruchi. Ọ lepụrụ anya hụ ọtụtụ ịnyịnya kamel na-abịanụ. <verse eid="GEN 24:63"/><verse number="64" style="v" sid="GEN 24:64"/>Ribeka nʼonwe ya lepụkwara anya hụ Aịzik. O sitere nʼelu ịnyịnya kamel rịdata, <verse eid="GEN 24:64"/><verse number="65" style="v" sid="GEN 24:65"/>jụọ ohu ahụ sị, “Onye bụ nwoke a si nʼọhịa na-abịa izute anyị?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 24:65">Ohu ahụ zara sị ya, “Ọ bụ nna m ukwu” Nʼihi nke a, Ribeka weere akwa mkpudo ya kpuchie ihu ya.<verse eid="GEN 24:65"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="66" style="v" sid="GEN 24:66"/>Ohu ahụ kọọrọ Aịzik akụkọ otu ije ya niile si gaa. <verse eid="GEN 24:66"/><verse number="67" style="v" sid="GEN 24:67"/>Aịzik kpọbatara Ribeka nʼụlọ ikwu Sera,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">24:67 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Cheta nʼoge a, Sera a nwụọlarị afọ atọ gara aga. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 17:17">Jen 17:17</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 23:1">23:1</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 25:20">25:20</ref></char></char></note> nne ya. Ọ lụrụ Ribeka, onye ghọrọ nwunye ya. Aịzik hụrụ ya nʼanya, ma nweta nkasiobi nʼihi ọnwụ nne ya.<verse eid="GEN 24:67"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="GEN 25"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụ Ebraham</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 25:1"/>Ebraham lụrụ nwunye ọzọ, onye aha ya bụ Ketura. <verse eid="GEN 25:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 25:2"/>Ọ mụụrụ ya Zimran, Jokshan, Medan, Midian, Ishbak na Shua. <verse eid="GEN 25:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 25:3"/>Jokshan bụ nna Sheba na Dedan. Ụmụ ndị ikom Dedan bụ Ashurim, Letushim, na Leumim. <verse eid="GEN 25:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 25:4"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Midian bụ Efaa, Efe, Hanok, Abida, na Eldaa. Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ Ketura.<verse eid="GEN 25:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 25:5"/>Ebraham nyere Aịzik ihe niile o nwere. <verse eid="GEN 25:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 25:6"/>Ebraham nyere ụmụ ndị ikom ndị iko ya nwanyị mụtara onyinye dị iche iche, zipụ ha nʼala dị nʼebe ọwụwa anyanwụ, mgbe ọ ka nọ ndụ, ka ha ghara ịnọ nwa ya nwoke Aịzik nso.<verse eid="GEN 25:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 25:7"/>Ebraham dị ndụ ruo narị afọ na iri afọ asaa na ise. <verse eid="GEN 25:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 25:8"/>Ebraham kubiri ume ndụ nwụọ mgbe o mere nnọọ ezigbo agadi, agadi nwoke nke ndụ juru afọ, e mere ka ọ lakwuru ndị ya. <verse eid="GEN 25:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 25:9"/>Ụmụ ya, Aịzik na Ishmel, liri ya nʼọgba Makipela nʼakụkụ Mamre, nʼala ubi Efrọn nwa Zoha onye Het, <verse eid="GEN 25:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 25:10"/>ala ahụ Ebraham zụrụ site nʼaka ndị Het. Ebe ahụ ka e liri Ebraham ya na Sera nwunye ya. <verse eid="GEN 25:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 25:11"/>Mgbe Ebraham nwụrụ, Chineke gọziri nwa ya nwoke Aịzik onye bi nʼoge ahụ na nso nso Bịa-Lahai-Rọị.<verse eid="GEN 25:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụ ụmụ Ishmel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 25:12"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro ezinaụlọ Ishmel nwa Ebraham onye Hega, nwanyị Ijipt ahụ na-ejere Sera ozi mụụrụ ya.<verse eid="GEN 25:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 25:13"/>Ndị a bụ aha ụmụ ndị ikom Ishmel nʼusoro ọmụmụ ha.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 25:13"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 25:13">Nebaiot bụ nwa mbụ ya.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 25:13">Ndị ọzọ bụ Keda, Adbel, Mibsam,<verse eid="GEN 25:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 25:14"/>Mishma, Duma, Masa,<verse eid="GEN 25:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 25:15"/>Hadad, Tema, Jetua,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 25:15">Nafish na Kedema.<verse eid="GEN 25:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 25:16"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ Ishmel, ndị a bụkwa aha ndịisi ikwu iri na abụọ ha, dịka ebe obibi ha si dị, na dịka ọmụma ụlọ ikwu ha si dị.<verse eid="GEN 25:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 25:17"/>Ishmel biri ndụ ruo narị afọ na iri afọ na asaa. Ọ nwụrụ, e mere ka ọ lakwuru ndị ya. <verse eid="GEN 25:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 25:18"/>Ụmụ ụmụ ya bi nʼala dị site na Havila ruo Shua nso nso oke ala ndị Ijipt, nʼụzọ e si aga Ashọ. Ha na ụmụnna ha ndị ọzọ ebighị nʼudo.<verse eid="GEN 25:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb na Ịsọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 25:19"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro agbụrụ Aịzik nwa Ebraham.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 25:19"/>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 25:19">Ebraham bụ nna Aịzik. <verse eid="GEN 25:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 25:20"/>Aịzik gbara iri afọ anọ mgbe ọ lụrụ Ribeka, nwa Betuel, onye Aram si nʼobodo Padan Aram, nwanne Leban, onye Aram.<verse eid="GEN 25:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 25:21"/>Aịzik kpere ekpere rịọọ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ka o nye nwunye ya nwa nʼihi na ọ bụ nwanyị aga. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> zara ekpere ya. Nwunye ya, Ribeka dịịrị ime. <verse eid="GEN 25:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 25:22"/>Ụmụ o bu nʼafọ bidoro na-alụ ọgụ nʼime afọ ya. Nʼihi nke a, o kwuru sị, “Gịnị mere ihe dị otu a ji eme m?” Ya mere, ọ gara jụta ase nʼaka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.<verse eid="GEN 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 25:23"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gwara ya sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 25:23">“Mba abụọ dị gị nʼafọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 25:23">ụzọ mba abụọ dị nʼime gị ka a ga-ekewa.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 25:23">Otu ụzọ ga-adị ike karịa nke ọzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 25:23">nke okenye ga-ejere nke nta ozi.”<verse eid="GEN 25:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 25:24"/>Mgbe oge ime ya zuru, ụmụ abụọ dị nʼakpanwa ya. <verse eid="GEN 25:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 25:25"/>Ahụ nwa nke mbụ buru ụzọ pụta na-acha uhie uhie, ahụ ya niile dịka uwe ajị. Nʼihi ya, ha kpọrọ aha ya Ịsọ. <verse eid="GEN 25:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 25:26"/>Emesịa, nwanne ya pụtara, ma aka ya jidere ikiri ụkwụ Ịsọ. Nʼihi ya, a kpọrọ aha ya Jekọb. Aịzik gbara iri afọ isii mgbe Ribeka mụrụ ha.<verse eid="GEN 25:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 25:27"/>Ha abụọ toro, Ịsọ ghọrọ onye ọka nʼịchụ nta, onye na-epiogharị nʼọhịa, ebe Jekọb bụ nwoke dị nwayọọ, onye na-anọ nʼetiti ụlọ ikwu. <verse eid="GEN 25:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 25:28"/>Aịzik hụrụ Ịsọ nʼanya nʼihi na ụtọ anụ Ịsọ na-egbute nʼọhịa na-adị ya mma, ma Ribeka hụrụ Jekọb nʼanya.<verse eid="GEN 25:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ịsọ eree ọnọdụ ọkpara ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 25:29"/>Otu ụbọchị, Jekọb nọ na-esi ofe mgbe Ịsọ si nʼọhịa bata. Agụụ na-agụkwa ya nke ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 25:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 25:30"/>Ịsọ rịọrọ Jekọb sị, “Nyetụ m ụfọdụ nʼime nri a na-acha uhie uhie ị na-esi ka m rie, nʼihi na agụụ na-agụ m hie nne.” (Ọ bụ ihe a mere e ji na-akpọ ya Edọm.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">25:30 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Edọm pụtara uhie.</char></note>)<verse eid="GEN 25:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 25:31"/>Ma Jekọb zara ya, “Buru ụzọ resi m ọnọdụ ịbụ ọkpara gị.”<verse eid="GEN 25:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 25:32"/>Ịsọ sịrị, “Gịnị bụ uru ọnọdụ ịbụ ọkpara bara mgbe m na-anwụ nʼagụụ?”<verse eid="GEN 25:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 25:33"/>Jekọb sịrị ya, “Buru ụzọ ṅụọrọ m iyi.” Ya mere, ọ ṅụụrụ ya iyi, sị otu a resi Jekọb ọnọdụ ọkpara ya.<verse eid="GEN 25:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 25:34"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb nyere Ịsọ achịcha na ofe lentil o siri. O riri, ṅụọkwa, bilie ọtọ pụọ.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 25:34">Ya mere Ịsọ ledara ọnọdụ ịbụ ọkpara nna ya anya.<verse eid="GEN 25:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="GEN 26"/>
  <para style="s1">Abimelek na Aịzik</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 26:1"/>Nʼoge a, ụnwụ dara nʼala ahụ. Ụnwụ a dị iche nʼụnwụ mbụ nke dara nʼoge Ebraham dị ndụ. Aịzik jekwuru Abimelek<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">26:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Abimelek, bụ aha ndịisi na-achị obodo a na-aza. Abimelek nke anyị nụrụ ihe banyere ya nʼakwụkwọ Jenesis isi 20, a nwụọlarị. Ọ nwụrụ ihe dịka iri afọ asatọ gara aga. Onye nke a bụ eze ọzọ.</char></note> eze ndị Filistia nʼobodo Gera. <verse eid="GEN 26:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 26:2"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gosiri Aịzik onwe ya, sị, “Agakwala Ijipt; biri nʼala ahụ m sị gị biri nʼime ya. <verse eid="GEN 26:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 26:3"/>Nọrọ nʼala a nwa oge nta, aga m anọnyere gị ma gọziekwa gị, nʼihi na gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ka m ga-enye ala ndị a niile. Aga m emezukwa iyi ahụ m ṅụrụ nye Ebraham nna gị. <verse eid="GEN 26:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 26:4"/>Aga m eme ka ụmụ ụmụ gị mụbaa, mee ka ha hie nne nʼọnụọgụgụ dịka kpakpando dị na mbara eluigwe. Ha ka m ga-enye ala ndị a niile. Aga m esite na mkpụrụ gị gọzie mba niile nke ụwa. <verse eid="GEN 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 26:5"/>Ihe ndị a niile ka m ga-eme nʼihi na Ebraham rubere isi ime ihe m gwara ya, na idebe iwu m na ụkpụrụ m, na ịdọ aka na ntị m.” <verse eid="GEN 26:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 26:6"/>Ya mere, Aịzik nọgidere nʼobodo Gera.<verse eid="GEN 26:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 26:7"/>Mgbe ndị obodo ahụ jụrụ ya banyere nwunye ya, ọ gwara ha sị, “Ọ bụ nwanne m nwanyị.” Ọ tụrụ ụjọ ị sị ha, “Nwunye m ka ọ bụ,” O chere nʼobi ya sị, “Ndị ikom obodo a nwere ike gbuo m nʼihi Ribeka. Nʼihi na Ribeka nʼonwe ya mara mma ile anya.”<verse eid="GEN 26:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 26:8"/>Mgbe Aịzik nọrọ ebe ahụ ogologo oge, Abimelek eze ndị Filistia, sitere na oghereikuku ya lepụ anya hụ Aịzik ka ọ nọ na-egwusa Ribeka nwunye ya egwu. <verse eid="GEN 26:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 26:9"/>Ya mere, Abimelek kpọrọ Aịzik sị, “Nwunye gị ka ọ bụ nʼezie. Gịnị mere i ji gwa anyị na ọ bụ nwanne gị nwanyị?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 26:9">Aịzik zara ya, “Ọ bụ nʼihi na m chere na-enwere ike igbu m nʼihi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 26:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 26:10"/>Abimelek sịrị, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere anyị? Otu nwoke nʼetiti anyị gaara akpọrọ nwunye gị dinaa ya. Ị gaara esi otu a wetara anyị ikpe ọmụma.”<verse eid="GEN 26:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 26:11"/>Ya mere, Abimelek nyere ndị niile ya iwu, sị ha, “Onye ọbụla metụrụ nwoke a maọbụ nwunye ya aka, aghaghị ime ka ọ nwụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 26:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 26:12"/>Aịzik kụrụ mkpụrụ ubi nʼala ahụ. Nʼotu afọ ahụ kwa, o si nʼala ahụ webata ihe ubi narị okpukpu karịa nke ọ kụrụ, nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gọziri ya. <verse eid="GEN 26:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 26:13"/>Nwoke a bara ụba, ghọọ ọgaranya. Akụnụba ya gara nʼihu na-amụba, tutu ruo mgbe ọ ghọrọ nnọọ onye ọgaranya a ma ama. <verse eid="GEN 26:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 26:14"/>O nwere ọtụtụ igwe anụ ụlọ, na igwe ehi, na ndị ikom na-ejere ya ozi. Nʼihi ihe ndị a, ndị Filistia bidoro inwe anya ukwu megide ya. <verse eid="GEN 26:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 26:15"/>Ndị Filistia wụjuru aja nʼolulu mmiri ndị ahụ niile ndị na-ejere nna ya ozi gwuru nʼoge nna ya Ebraham dị ndụ.<verse eid="GEN 26:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 26:16"/>Abimelek kpọrọ Aịzik sị ya, “Si nʼala a kwapụ gaa nʼebe ọzọ, nʼihi na ịba ụba gị na ịdị ike gị adịla ukwuu karịa nke anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 26:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 26:17"/>Ya mere Aịzik si nʼebe ahụ kwapụ, gaa maa ụlọ ikwu ya na Ndagwurugwu Gera, biri nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 26:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 26:18"/>O gwugharịkwara olulu mmiri ndị ahụ e gwuru nʼoge nna ya Ebraham, nke ndị Filistia kpojuru aja mgbe Ebraham nwụrụ, kpọọ olulu mmiri ndị a otu aha ahụ nna ya kpọrọ ha na mbụ.<verse eid="GEN 26:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 26:19"/>Ọzọ, ndị na-ejere Aịzik ozi gwuru olulu mmiri ọhụrụ na ndagwurugwu Gera ahụ, gwute mmiri nke si nʼala na-asọpụta. <verse eid="GEN 26:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 26:20"/>Ma ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ obodo Gera sesịrị ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ Aịzik okwu. Ha kwuru sị, “Mmiri a bụ nke anyị!” Nke a mere Aịzik ji kpọọ olulu mmiri ahụ Esek, nʼihi ise okwu nke ha sesịrị ya. <verse eid="GEN 26:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 26:21"/>Ha gwuru olulu mmiri ọzọ, ma ndị ahụ bịakwara ọzọ bido ịzọ ya. Nʼihi ya Aịzik kpọrọ olulu mmiri ahụ Sitna. <verse eid="GEN 26:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 26:22"/>O si nʼebe ahụ pụọ gaa nʼebe ọzọ gwuo olulu mmiri ọzọ. Ma o nweghị ndị bịara zọọ ya. Nʼihi ya ọ kpọrọ olulu mmiri ahụ Rehobọt. O kwuru sị, “Ugbu a, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> enyela anyị ebe sara mbara, ebe ihe ga-anọ gaara anyị nke ọma.”<verse eid="GEN 26:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 26:23"/>O sitere nʼebe ahụ kwapụ gaa Bịasheba. <verse eid="GEN 26:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 26:24"/>Nʼabalị ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> mere ka ọ hụ ya anya, sị ya, “Abụ m Chineke nna gị Ebraham. Atụla egwu, nʼihi na anọnyere m gị, aga m agọzi gị, mụbaa ọnụọgụgụ ụmụ ụmụ gị nʼihi ohu m Ebraham.”<verse eid="GEN 26:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 26:25"/>Ya mere, o wuru ebe ịchụ aja nʼebe ahụ kpọkuo aha <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Ọ makwara ụlọ ikwu ya nʼebe ahụ. Ndị na-ejere ya ozi gwukwara olulu mmiri.<verse eid="GEN 26:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọgbụgba ndụ Aịzik na Abimelek</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 26:26"/>Abimelek na Ahuzat, onye ndụmọdụ ya, na Fikọl onyeisi ndị agha ya sitere Gera jekwuru Aịzik. <verse eid="GEN 26:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 26:27"/>Aịzik jụrụ ha sị, “Gịnị mere unu ji bịakwute m, ebe ọ bụ na unu kpọrọ m asị, chụpụkwa m site nʼetiti unu?”<verse eid="GEN 26:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 26:28"/>Ha sị, “Anyị hụrụ nke ọma na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọnyeere gị, ya mere anyị ji sị, ‘O kwesiri ka ịṅụ iyi dị nʼetiti anyị na gị,’ ka anyị na gị gbaakwa ndụ <verse eid="GEN 26:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 26:29"/>na ị gaghị eme anyị ihe ọjọọ dịka anyị na-esighị mee gị ihe ọjọọ. I lezie anya nke ọma, ị ga-ahụ na anyị meere gị ihe ọma mgbe anyị hapụrụ gị ka ị laa nʼudo. Ugbu a, anyị maara na ị bụ onye <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gọziri agọzi.”<verse eid="GEN 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 26:30"/>Aịzik meere ha mmemme nri dị ukwuu; ha riri, ṅụọkwa. <verse eid="GEN 26:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 26:31"/>Nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, ndị ikom ahụ niile ṅụrịtaara onwe ha iyi ịgba ndụ. Aịzik zilagara ha, ha hapụrụ ya laa nʼudo.<verse eid="GEN 26:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 26:32"/>Nʼotu ụbọchị ahụ kwa, ndị ohu Aịzik bịakwutere ya gwa ya banyere olulu mmiri ha na-egwu, sị ya, “Anyị achọtala mmiri nʼolulu ahụ anyị na-egwu.” <verse eid="GEN 26:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 26:33"/>Ọ kpọrọ ya Shiba. Ọ bụkwa nke a mere e ji akpọ obodo ahụ Bịasheba<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">26:33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nke a pụtara </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Olulu mmiri ịṅụ iyi</char></note> ruo taa.<verse eid="GEN 26:33"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ndị inyom Ịsọ lụrụ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 26:34"/>Mgbe Ịsọ gbara iri afọ anọ, ọ lụrụ Judit nwa Beiri, onye Het. Ọ lụkwara Basemat nwa Elọn, onye Het. <verse eid="GEN 26:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 26:35"/>Ha ghọrọ Aịzik na Ribeka ihe ọnọdụ obi ilu.<verse eid="GEN 26:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="GEN 27"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 27:1"/>Mgbe Aịzik ghọrọ agadi, nʼoge anya ya na-adịghị ahụzi ụzọ nke ọma, ọ kpọrọ Ịsọ ọkpara ya, sị ya, “Nwa m nwoke.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:1">Ọ zara sị, “Lee m nʼebe a.”<verse eid="GEN 27:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 27:2"/>Aịzik gwara ya sị, “Ugbu a, emeela m agadi, amakwaghị m ụbọchị ọnwụ m. <verse eid="GEN 27:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 27:3"/>Ya mere, were ihe ịchụ nta gị, ụta gị na àkụ gị, gaa nʼọhịa, gbutere m anụ. <verse eid="GEN 27:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 27:4"/>Siere m nri ụtọ otu ahụ o si amasị m, butere m ya ka m rie, ka mụ onwe m gọzie gị tupu m nwụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 27:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 27:5"/>Ma Ribeka nọ na-ege ntị mgbe Aịzik na-agwa nwa ya Ịsọ okwu. Nke mere na mgbe Ịsọ gawara nʼọhịa ịchụ nta, <verse eid="GEN 27:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 27:6"/>Ribeka gwara Jekọb nwa ya okwu sị ya, “Lee, anụrụ m ka nna gị na-agwa nwanne gị Ịsọ okwu sị ya, <verse eid="GEN 27:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 27:7"/>‘Gaa nʼọhịa gbute anụ, siere m nri ụtọ, ka m nọdụ nʼihu <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nye gị ngọzị ikpeazụ tupu m nwụọ.’ <verse eid="GEN 27:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 27:8"/>Ugbu a, nwa m nwoke, gee ntị nke ọma, mee ihe niile m gwara gị. <verse eid="GEN 27:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 27:9"/>Gaa ugbu a nʼigwe anụ ụlọ wetara m ụmụ nwa ewu abụọ dị mma ka m jiri ha siere nna gị nri dị ụtọ, ụdị ahụ na-amasị ya. <verse eid="GEN 27:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 27:10"/>Ị ga-eburu ya bujere nna gị ka o rie, ka ya onwe ya gọzie gị tupu ọ nwụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 27:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 27:11"/>Ma Jekọb gwara Ribeka nne ya okwu sị ya, “Nwanne m nwoke Ịsọ bụ onye gbara ajị. Ahụ nke m na-akwọ mụrụmụrụ. <verse eid="GEN 27:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 27:12"/>Gịnị ga-eme ma nna m metụ m aka nʼahụ? Nʼihi ya, aga m abụ onye na-aghọ ya aghụghọ, aga m esi otu a wetara onwe m ịbụ ọnụ kama ngọzị.”<verse eid="GEN 27:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 27:13"/>Nne ya gwara ya sị, “Nwa m nwoke ka ọbụbụ ọnụ gị dakwasị m. Naanị mee ihe m kwuru. Gaa wetara m ha.”<verse eid="GEN 27:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 27:14"/>Ya mere, ọ gara weta ha nye nne ya. O ji ha sie nri dị ụtọ, ụdị nke na-amasị nna ya. <verse eid="GEN 27:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 27:15"/>Emesịa, Ribeka chịpụtara uwe Ịsọ ọkpara ya, ndị dị mma, ndị ọ debere nʼụlọ ya, nye ya nwa ya nta bụ Jekọb. <verse eid="GEN 27:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 27:16"/>O jikwa akpụkpọ anụ ụmụ ewu nwere ajị ajị kee Jekọb nʼaka na nʼakụkụ olu ya na-akwọ mụrụmụrụ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27:16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ya bụ ebe ajị nʼadịghị</char></note> <verse eid="GEN 27:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 27:17"/>O bunyere nwa ya nwoke Jekọb nri ahụ na-atọ ụtọ, na achịcha o mere.<verse eid="GEN 27:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 27:18"/>O jekwuuru nna ya sị ya, “Nna m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:18">Ọ zara sị, “Ahaa, nwa m, onye ka ị bụ?”<verse eid="GEN 27:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 27:19"/>Jekọb zara nna ya sị ya, “Abụ m Ịsọ, ọkpara gị. Emeela m ihe ị sị m mee. Biko bilie ka i rie anụ m gbutere nʼọhịa, ka gị onwe gị gọzie m.”<verse eid="GEN 27:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 27:20"/>Ma Aịzik jụrụ nwa ya nwoke sị, “Olee otu i si chọta ya ngwangwa, nwa m?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:20">Jekọb zara ya sị, “Ọ bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> Chineke gị mere ka ihe gaara m nke ọma.”<verse eid="GEN 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 27:21"/>Mgbe ahụ Aịzik gwara Jekọb sị, “Bịa nso ka m metụ gị aka nwa m nwoke, ka m mata ma ị bụ Ịsọ nʼeziokwu.”<verse eid="GEN 27:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 27:22"/>Jekọb jere nna ya Aịzik nso, onye metụrụ ya aka kwuo sị, “Olu bụ olu Jekọb ma aka gị bụ aka Ịsọ.” <verse eid="GEN 27:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 27:23"/>Ọ chọpụtaghị na ọ bụ Jekọb, nʼihi na aka ya dị ajị ajị dịka nke Ịsọ. Ya mere, ọ gọziri ya. <verse eid="GEN 27:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 27:24"/>Ma ọ jụkwara ya ajụjụ ọzọ sị ya, “Ị bụ nwa m nwoke Ịsọ nʼeziokwu?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:24">Jekọb zara sị ya, “E, abụ m ya.”<verse eid="GEN 27:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 27:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, Aịzik zara sị ya, “Butere m ụfọdụ nʼime anụ ahụ i gbutere ka m rie, nye gị ngọzị m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:25">Jekọb butere ya bunye ya. O riri ya. <verse eid="GEN 27:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 27:26"/>Mgbe ahụ, nna ya Aịzik sịrị ya, “Bịa nʼebe a nwa m nwoke, sutu m ọnụ.”<verse eid="GEN 27:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 27:27"/>Ya mere, o jekwuuru ya sutu ya ọnụ. Mgbe Aịzik nụrụ isisi uwe ya, ọ gọziri ya, sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 27:27">“Nʼezie, isisi nwa m nwoke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:27">dịka isisi ala ubi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:27">nke <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gọziri.<verse eid="GEN 27:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 27:28"/>Ka Chineke nye gị site nʼigirigi nke eluigwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:28">na mmanụ nke ala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:28">ụba nke mkpụrụ ubi na mmanya ọhụrụ<verse eid="GEN 27:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 27:29"/>Ka ọtụtụ mba jeere gị ozi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:29">ka ndị mmadụ kpọọ isiala nye gị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 27:29">Bụrụ onye ọchịchị nʼebe ụmụnna gị nọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:29">ka ụmụ nne gị mụrụ kpọọ isiala nye gị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 27:29">Ka ndị niile na-abụ gị ọnụ bụrụ ndị a bụrụ ọnụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:29">ka ndị na-agọzi gị bụrụ ndị a gọziri agọzi.”<verse eid="GEN 27:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ịsọ arịọọ ka a gọzie ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 27:30"/>Mgbe Aịzik gọzichara Jekọb, ka Jekọb si nʼihu ya na-apụ, lee Ịsọ ka o si ịchụ nta na-alọbata. <verse eid="GEN 27:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 27:31"/>Ya onwe ya sikwara nri na-atọ ụtọ butere nna ya. Mgbe ahụ, ọ gwara ya sị, “Ka nna m, bilie, rie anụ nwa ya si nʼọhịa gbute, ka gị onwe gị nye m ngọzị gị.”<verse eid="GEN 27:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 27:32"/>Aịzik zara sị ya, “Ị bụ onye?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 27:32">Ọ zara sị, “Abụ m nwa gị nwoke Ịsọ, ọkpara gị Ịsọ.”<verse eid="GEN 27:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 27:33"/>Oke ahụ ọma jijiji mara Aịzik, ọ sị, “Onye kwanụ bụ onye ahụ gara gbute anụ butere m ya? Eriri m ya tupu ị bata. Agọziri m ya. Nʼezie, onye a gọziri agọzi ka ọ ga-abụ.”<verse eid="GEN 27:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 27:34"/>Mgbe Ịsọ nụrụ okwu ndị a si nʼọnụ nna ya, o jiri oke olu kwaa akwa nke obi ilu gwa nna ya sị ya, “Gọzie m, mụ onwe m, nna m.”<verse eid="GEN 27:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 27:35"/>Ma ọ zara sị ya, “Nwanne gị ejirila ụzọ aghụghọ bịa nara ngọzị gị.”<verse eid="GEN 27:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 27:36"/>Ịsọ kwuru sị, “E meziri kpọọ ya Jekọb,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27:36 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Jekọb </char><char style="ft" closed="false">pụtara </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">onye aghụghọ maọbụ onye na-ewere ọnọdụ onye ọzọ nʼike.</char></note> onye aghụghọ. Lee, ọ ghọgbuola m ugboro abụọ. Nke mbụ, ọ naara m ọnọdụ ịbụ ọkpara m, ugbu a ọ narakwala m ngọzị m.” Ọ jụrụ ajụjụ sị, “Ọ bụ na i nweghị ngọzị ọ bụla fọdụrụ nke ị ga-agọzi m?”<verse eid="GEN 27:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 27:37"/>Aịzik zara sị ya, “Emeela m ya ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi nʼebe ị nọ, mee ụmụnna ya niile ndị na-ejere ya ozi. Enyela m ya mkpụrụ ubi niile na mmanya ọhụrụ. Gịnị ọzọ ka m nwere ike imere gị, nwa m nwoke?”<verse eid="GEN 27:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 27:38"/>Ịsọ jụrụ nna ya sị, “Nna m, ọ bụ naanị otu ngọzị ka i nwere? Gọziekwa m nna m!” Ịsọ kwara akwa nʼoke olu.<verse eid="GEN 27:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 27:39"/>Nna ya Aịzik zara sị ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 27:39">“Ebe obibi<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27:39 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ala Edọm ebe ndị agbụrụ Ịsọ biri, bụ ala akọrọ, ala nkume nkume, nke na-adịghị emepụta nri nke ọma dị ka ala Kenan. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 36:8">Jen 36:8</ref>; <ref loc="2KI 8:20">2Ez 8:20</ref></char></char></note> gị ga-adịpụ adịpụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:39">site nʼebe akụnụba nke ala dị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:39">site nʼebe igirigi nke eluigwe dị.<verse eid="GEN 27:39"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 27:40"/>Nriju afọ gị ga-abụ site na mma agha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:40">ị ga-ejekwara nwanne gị ozi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 27:40">Ma mgbe i mesịrị nwere onwe gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:40">ị ga-atọpụ agbụ ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 27:40">site nʼolu gị.”<verse eid="GEN 27:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb agbakwuru Leban</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 27:41"/>Ịsọ buru iro nʼobi megide Jekọb nʼihi ngọzị ahụ nna ya nyere ya. O kwuru nʼime onwe ya sị, “Oge a ga-eru ụjụ nʼihi nna m na-abịa nso, nʼoge ahụ aga m egbu nwanne m Jekọb.”<verse eid="GEN 27:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 27:42"/>Mgbe a gwara Ribeka ihe nwa ya nwoke nke okenye bụ Ịsọ kwuru, o ziri kpọọ nwa ya nwoke nke nta bụ Jekọb sị ya, “Lee, Ịsọ nwanne gị na-akasị onwe ya obi site nʼechiche ọ na-eche igbu gị. <verse eid="GEN 27:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 27:43"/>Nʼihi nke a, nwa m nwoke, mee ihe m gwara gị, gbapụ ọsọ ngwangwa, gbakwuru nwanne m Leban na Haran, <verse eid="GEN 27:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="GEN 27:44"/>Nọdụ nʼebe ahụ ruo mgbe iwe nwanne gị ga-adajụ. <verse eid="GEN 27:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="GEN 27:45"/>Mgbe nwanne gị kwụsịrị iwe iwe megide gị, mgbe o chefuru ihe i mere ya, aga m ezitere gị ozi ka ị lọta. Nʼihi gịnị ka m ga-eji gbara aka unu abụọ nʼotu ụbọchị.”<verse eid="GEN 27:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="GEN 27:46"/>Mgbe ahụ Ribeka gara gwa Aịzik sị, “Ike ịdị ndụ agwụla m nʼihi ndị inyom Het ndị a. Ọ bụrụ na Jekọb esite nʼetiti ndị inyom ala a, site nʼetiti ndị inyom Het ndị a lụọ nwunye, mara na ọnwụ ga-akara m ịdị ndụ mma.”<verse eid="GEN 27:46"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="GEN 28"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 28:1"/>Aịzik kpọrọ Jekọb gọzie ya, nye ya iwu sị ya, “Alụla nwunye site nʼala Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 28:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 28:2"/>Kama bilie gaa Padan Aram nʼụlọ nna nne gị, Betuel, lụrụ nwunye site nʼụmụ ndị inyom Leban. <verse eid="GEN 28:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 28:3"/>Ka Chineke Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile, gọzie gị, mee ka ị mịa mkpụrụ, mụbaa, ghọọ ọtụtụ mba. <verse eid="GEN 28:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 28:4"/>Ka Chineke nye gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ngọzị ahụ o kwere nkwa inye Ebraham. Ka i nweta ala a, nke i bi nʼime ya ugbu a dịka ọbịa, bụ ala ahụ Chineke kwere Ebraham na nkwa inye ya.” <verse eid="GEN 28:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 28:5"/>Mgbe ahụ Aịzik zipụrụ Jekọb nʼije ya, ọ gara Padan Aram, nʼụlọ Leban nwa Betuel onye Aram, nwanne Ribeka onye bụ nne Jekọb na Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 28:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 28:6"/>Ịsọ hụrụ ka Aịzik siri gọzie Jekọb, ziga ya Padan Aram ka ọ gaa lụọ nwunye nʼebe ahụ, nyekwa ya iwu mgbe ọ na-agọzi ya sị, “Alụla nwanyị na Kenan,” <verse eid="GEN 28:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 28:7"/>Jekọb rubekwara nna ya na nne ya isi gawa Padan Aram. <verse eid="GEN 28:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 28:8"/>O dokwara Ịsọ anya na ndị inyom Kenan dị njọ nʼanya nna ya Aịzik. <verse eid="GEN 28:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 28:9"/>Nʼihi ya, Ịsọ gakwuru Ishmel lụrụ Mahalat, ada Ishmel, nwa Ebraham, onye bụ nwanyị Nebaiot, tinyekwara ndị nwunye ọ lụrụ na mbụ.<verse eid="GEN 28:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Nrọ Jekọb rọrọ na Betel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 28:10"/>Jekọb hapụrụ Bịasheba gawa Haran. <verse eid="GEN 28:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 28:11"/>Mgbe chi na-eji, ọ kwụsịrị ebe ọ ga-anọ zuo ike abalị. Mgbe ọ chọrọ idina ala, o weere otu nʼime nkume ndị dị nʼebe ahụ hinye nʼisi ya, dinara ala ịrahụ ụra. <verse eid="GEN 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 28:12"/>Nʼabalị ahụ, ọ rọrọ nrọ, hụ mbube e ji arị elu. E mere ka o guzo site nʼụwa ruo nʼeluigwe. Ọ hụkwara ndị mmụọ ozi Chineke ka ha si na ya na-arịgo na-arịdakwa. <verse eid="GEN 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 28:13"/>Nʼelu ya, ọ hụrụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ka o guzo, nụkwa ka ọ na-agwa ya okwu sị, “Mụ onwe m bụ <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, Chineke nna gị Ebraham, na Chineke Aịzik. Aga m enye gị na ụmụ ụmụ gị ala ahụ nke i dina nʼelu ya. <verse eid="GEN 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 28:14"/>Ụmụ gị ga-adị ukwuu, dị ka aja dị nʼala. Ha ga-ejupụta ala a, site nʼọwụwa anyanwụ ruo nʼọdịda anyanwụ, sitekwa nʼugwu ruo na ndịda. A ga-esitekwa na gị na mkpụrụ gị, gọzie mba niile nke ụwa a. <verse eid="GEN 28:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 28:15"/>Anọnyeere m gị. Aga m echebe gị ebe ọbụla ị na-aga. Aga m akpọghachite gị nʼala a. Agaghị m ahapụ gị tutu ruo mgbe m mezuoro gị ihe niile m kwere gị na nkwa.”<verse eid="GEN 28:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 28:16"/>Jekọb tetara nʼụra sị, “Nʼezie <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọ nʼebe a. Ma amaghị m ya.” <verse eid="GEN 28:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 28:17"/>Ọ tụrụ egwu sị, “Lee ka ebe a si dị oke egwu, o nweghị ihe ebe a bụ karịa ụlọ Chineke, nʼezie ọ bụ ọnụ ụzọ ama eluigwe.”<verse eid="GEN 28:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 28:18"/>Nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, Jekọb weere nkume ahụ o hinyere nʼisi ya guzo ya dịka ogidi, wụsa mmanụ nʼelu ya. <verse eid="GEN 28:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 28:19"/>Ọ kpọrọ ebe ahụ Betel, ọ bụ ezie na Luz bụ aha obodo ahụ na mbụ.<verse eid="GEN 28:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 28:20"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb kwere nkwa sị, “Ọ bụrụ na Chineke ga-anọnyere m, chebe m nʼije m na-eje, ọ bụrụ na ọ ga-enye m ihe oriri m ga-eri na uwe m ga-eyi, <verse eid="GEN 28:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 28:21"/>m lọghachi nʼụlọ nna m nʼudo, mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ga-abụ Chineke m. <verse eid="GEN 28:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 28:22"/>Nkume a m doziri elu dịka ogidi ga-abụ ụlọ Chineke. Aga m eke ihe niile i nyere m ụzọ iri, nyeghachi gị otu ụzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 28:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 28"/>
  <chapter number="29" style="c" sid="GEN 29"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb erute nʼụlọ Leban</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 29:1"/>Jekọb gara nʼihu nʼije ya rute nʼala dị nʼọwụwa anyanwụ. <verse eid="GEN 29:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 29:2"/>NʼEbe Nsọ a, ọ hụrụ otu olulu mmiri, hụkwa ụzọ igwe atụrụ atọ ndị nọ nʼakụkụ olulu mmiri nʼihi na ndị na-elekọta ha na-enye ha mmiri site nʼolulu mmiri ahụ. Nkume e ji mechie ọnụ olulu mmiri ahụ buru ibu. <verse eid="GEN 29:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 29:3"/>Nʼihi na mgbe igwe atụrụ niile bịazukọtara nʼolulu mmiri ahụ, ndị ọzụzụ atụrụ na-emeghepụ nkume ahụ nye ha mmiri. Emesịa, ha na-ejikwa nkume ahụ mechie ọnụ olulu mmiri ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 29:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 29:4"/>Jekọb jekwuru ndị na-elekọta atụrụ ahụ jụọ ha sị, “Ụmụnna m, ebee ka unu si?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 29:4">Ha zara sị ya, “Anyị si Haran.”<verse eid="GEN 29:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 29:5"/>Ọ jụrụ ha sị, “Unu maara Leban, nwa Nahọ?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 29:5">Ha zara sị, “Anyị ma ya.”<verse eid="GEN 29:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 29:6"/>Ọzọ Jekọb jụrụ ha sị, “Ahụ ọ dịkwa ya mma?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 29:6">Ha zara sị ya, “E, ahụ dị ya. Lee nwa ya nwanyị Rechel ka ọ chị atụrụ ya na-abịa.”<verse eid="GEN 29:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 29:7"/>Jekọb kwuru sị, “Lee, anyanwụ ka na-acha. O rubeghị oge e ji achịbata igwe ụmụ anụ ụlọ. Nyenụ ha mmiri ka ha ṅụọ, ka ha laghachi gaa taa ahịhịa.”<verse eid="GEN 29:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 29:8"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Anyị agaghị enye ha mmiri tutu ruo mgbe igwe atụrụ niile bịakọtara, mgbe e wepụrụ nkume e ji mechie ọnụ olulu mmiri, mgbe ahụ ka anyị ga-enye ha mmiri.”<verse eid="GEN 29:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 29:9"/>Mgbe Jekọb na ndị ọzụzụ atụrụ ndị a kpụ okwu nʼọnụ, Rechel chịịrị atụrụ nna ya bịakwute ha, nʼihi na onye ọzụzụ atụrụ nwanyị ka ọ bụ. <verse eid="GEN 29:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 29:10"/>Mgbe Jekọb hụrụ Rechel nwa Leban nwanne nne ya, hụkwa igwe atụrụ Leban, ọ meghepụrụ nkume ahụ e ji mechie ọnụ olulu mmiri ahụ nye igwe atụrụ Leban, nwanne nne ya mmiri ka ha ṅụọ. <verse eid="GEN 29:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 29:11"/>Emesịa, Jekọb suturu Rechel ọnụ, kwaa akwa nʼoke olu. <verse eid="GEN 29:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 29:12"/>Jekọb kọwaara Rechel na ọ bụ onye ikwu nna ya, bụrụkwa nwa Ribeka. Nʼihi ya Rechel ji ọsọ gbalaa nʼụlọ ha kọọrọ nna ya.<verse eid="GEN 29:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 29:13"/>Mgbe Leban nụrụ maka Jekọb nwa nwanne ya nwanyị, o mere ngwangwa pụọ izute ya. Ọ makụrụ ya, sutu ya ọnụ, kpọrọ ya laa nʼụlọ. Nʼebe ahụ, Jekọb kọọrọ ya ihe ndị a niile. <verse eid="GEN 29:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 29:14"/>Leban sịrị ya, “Nʼezie, ị bụ ọkpụkpụ m na anụ ahụ m.”</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="GEN 29:14">Ije ozi Jekọb nʼihi Rechel na Lịa</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 29:14">Ọ nọnyeere ya otu ọnwa. <verse eid="GEN 29:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 29:15"/>Leban sịrị Jekọb, “Ọ bụ nʼihi na ị bụ onye ikwu m ka ị na-agbara m odibo nʼefu? Gwa m ego ole m ga-akwụ gị nʼihi ọrụ ị na-arụrụ m?”<verse eid="GEN 29:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 29:16"/>Leban mụrụ ụmụ ndị inyom abụọ. Aha nke okenye bụ Lịa. Aha nke nta bụ Rechel. <verse eid="GEN 29:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 29:17"/>Ịma mma Lịa dị ya nʼanya, ma Rechel mara mma nʼahụ, maakwa mma ile anya. <verse eid="GEN 29:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 29:18"/>Ọ bụ Rechel ka Jekọb hụrụ nʼanya. Nʼihi ya Jekọb gwara Leban sị, “Aga m arụrụ gị ọrụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">29:18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Onye ọbụla chọrọ ịlụ nwanyị na-akwụ nna nwaagbọghọ ahụ ego akụ, nʼisi ya. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 34:12">Jen 34:12</ref></char> Ma ọ bụrụ na o nweghị ego ịkwụ ego akụ, ọ ga-arụrụ nna nwanyị ahụ ọrụ rụzuo ego ole, maọbụ afọ ole rụrụ ihe o kwesiri ịkwụ dịka ego akụ, nʼisi onye ahụ.</char></note> afọ asaa ma ọ bụrụ na ị ga-ekwe ka m lụọ Rechel.”<verse eid="GEN 29:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 29:19"/>Leban zara Jekọb sị ya, “Ọ dị mma na ị lụrụ Rechel karịa na onye ọzọ ga-alụ ya. Soro m nọdụ nʼebe a.” <verse eid="GEN 29:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 29:20"/>Ya mere Jekọb gbara odibo afọ asaa maka Rechel. Ma afọ asaa ndị a dịka abalị ole na ole nʼanya Jekọb nʼihi ịhụnanya o nwere nʼebe Rechel nọ.<verse eid="GEN 29:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 29:21"/>Jekọb gwara Leban, okwu sị ya, “Kpọnye m nwunye m nʼihi nʼụbọchị m ezuola. Achọrọ m ịbakwuru ya.”<verse eid="GEN 29:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 29:22"/>Leban kpọkọtara ndị niile bi nʼebe ahụ mere ha nʼoke oriri. <verse eid="GEN 29:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 29:23"/><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">29:23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ụmụ nwanyị a lụrụ alụ na-eji akwa mkpudo kpuchie ihu ha. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 24:65">Jen 24:65</ref></char></char></note>Nʼanyasị ụbọchị ahụ, Leban kpọọrọ nwa ya nwanyị bụ Lịa kpọbara Jekọb, ọ bakwuuru ya. <verse eid="GEN 29:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 29:24"/>Leban nyekwara Lịa odibo ya, Zilpa, ka ọ bụrụ odibo nwanyị ya.<verse eid="GEN 29:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 29:25"/>Mgbe chi bọrọ, Jekọb hụrụ na ọ bụ Lịa ka Leban kpọnyere ya. Jekọb sịrị Leban, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere m? Ọ bụghị nʼihi Rechel ka m ji gbaara gị odibo? Gịnị mere i ji ghọgbuo m?”<verse eid="GEN 29:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 29:26"/>Leban zara sị ya, “Ọ bụghị omenaala anyị ibu ụzọ kee nwantakịrị nwanyị nke nta di tupu nke ada. <verse eid="GEN 29:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 29:27"/>Otu ọ dị, chere ka mmemme izu ụka nke onye nke a gafee. Mgbe ahụ, aga m akpọnyekwa gị onye nke ọzọ a maka odibo ị ga-agbara m afọ asaa ọzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 29:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 29:28"/>Jekọb mere ka o si kwuo. O debezuru mmemme otu izu ụka onye nke a, Leban kpọnyere ya nwa ya Rechel ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya. <verse eid="GEN 29:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 29:29"/>Leban nyere nwa ya nwanyị, Rechel, odibo ya nwanyị bụ Bilha, ka ọ bụrụ odibo ya. <verse eid="GEN 29:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 29:30"/>Jekọb bakwukwara Rechel. Ọ hụrụ Rechel nʼanya nke ukwuu karịa Lịa. Ọ gbakwaara Leban odibo afọ asaa ọzọ.<verse eid="GEN 29:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụ Jekọb</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 29:31"/>Mgbe <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> hụrụ na Lịa bụ nwanyị a kpọrọ asị, o meghere akpanwa ya, ma Rechel bụ nwanyị aga. <verse eid="GEN 29:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 29:32"/>Lịa tụrụ ime mụọ nwa nwoke, kpọọ ya Ruben. Nʼihi na o kwuru sị, “Ọ bụ nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> ahụla nsogbu m, ugbu a di m ga-ahụ m nʼanya.”<verse eid="GEN 29:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 29:33"/>Ọ tụụrụ ime ọzọ mụọkwa nwa nwoke. O kwuru sị, “<char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> anụla na m bụ nwanyị a kpọrọ asị, ọ bụ ya mere o ji nye m nwa nwoke ọzọ.” Ya mere ọ kpọrọ aha ya Simiọn.<verse eid="GEN 29:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 29:34"/>Lịa tụrụ ime ọzọ, mgbe ọ mụrụ nwa nwoke, o kwuru sị, “Nʼezie, ugbu a ka di m ga-arapara m nʼahụ, nʼihi na amụọrala m ya ụmụ ndị ikom atọ.” Ya mere ọ kpọrọ aha ya Livayị.<verse eid="GEN 29:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 29:35"/>Ọ tụụrụ ime ọzọ mụọ nwa nwoke. O kwuru sị, “Ugbu a aga m eto <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>.” Ya mere, ọ kpọrọ aha ya Juda. Lịa mụsịrị nwa a kwụsị ịmụ ụmụ.<verse eid="GEN 29:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 29"/>
  <chapter number="30" style="c" sid="GEN 30"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 30:1"/>Rechel hụrụ na ya amụghị nwa ọbụla nye Jekọb, o kworo ekworo megide nwanne ya nwanyị. Ya mere, ọ sịrị Jekọb, “Nye m ụmụ. Ọ bụrụ na i meghị otu a, aga m anwụ.”<verse eid="GEN 30:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 30:2"/>Jekọb were iwe megide Rechel, sị ya, “Abụ m Chineke onye gbochiri gị mkpụrụ nke afọ?”<verse eid="GEN 30:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 30:3"/>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">30:3 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">Anyị hụrụ na omenaala a bụ nke sitere nʼala ndị si nʼakụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ, nʼụlọ Ebraham. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 16:2">Jen 16:2</ref></char> Ugbu a, Jekọb na-eme otu ihe ahụ.</char>
    </note>Mgbe ahụ Rechel gwara Jekọb sị ya, “Lee odibo m nwanyị Bilha, bakwuru ya ka ọ mụọ nwa nʼikpere m abụọ, ka mụ onwe m site na ya bụrụkwa onye mụtara ụmụ.”<verse eid="GEN 30:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 30:4"/>Rechel nyere Jekọb Bilha, odibo nwanyị ya, Jekọb bakwuuru ya. <verse eid="GEN 30:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 30:5"/>Bilha tụụrụ ime mụọra Jekọb nwa nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 30:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 30:6"/>Nke a mere ka Rechel kwuo sị, “Chineke ekpepụtala m. Ọ nụla arịrịọ m nye m nwa nwoke.” Nʼihi nke a, Rechel gụrụ nwa ahụ Dan.<verse eid="GEN 30:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 30:7"/>Bilha, odibo nwanyị Rechel, tụụrụ ime ọzọ mụtara Jekọb nwa nwoke nke abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 30:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 30:8"/>Rechel kwuru sị, “Mgba dị ukwuu ka mụ na nwanne m nwanyị gbara, m merie.” Ọ kpọọ ya Naftalị.<verse eid="GEN 30:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 30:9"/>Lịa hụrụ na ya akwụsịla ịmụ nwa, ọ kpọọrọ Zilpa, odibo ya nwanyị kpọnye Jekọb ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya. <verse eid="GEN 30:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 30:10"/>Zilpa, odibo nwanyị Lịa, mụtara Jekọb nwa nwoke. <verse eid="GEN 30:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 30:11"/>Mgbe nke a mere, Lịa kwuru sị, “Nke a bụ ihuọma.” Ọ kpọrọ nwa ahụ Gad.<verse eid="GEN 30:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 30:12"/>Zilpa, odibo nwanyị Lịa mụtaara Jekọb nwa nwoke nke abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 30:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 30:13"/>Mgbe ahụ Lịa kwuru sị, “Ọṅụ ejula m obi, nʼihi na ụmụ nwanyị ibe m ga-akpọ m onye ihe na-agara nke ọma.” Lịa kpọrọ nwantakịrị nwoke ahụ Asha.<verse eid="GEN 30:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 30:14"/>Otu ụbọchị, nʼoge a na-aghọ ọka wiiti, Ruben nwa Lịa, gara nʼọhịa hụ ahịhịa a na-akpọ mandreki.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">30:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mandreki, bụ ahịhịa nke ụmụ mmadụ na-asị, na o nwere ọgwụ na-eweta mkpali ọchịchọ mmekọrịta nʼahụ mmadụ, na-emekwa ka nwanyị ọbụla tara ya tụrụ ime. <char style="xt"><ref loc="SNG 7:13">Abk 7:13</ref></char></char></note> Ọ kụtaara nne ya ụfọdụ nʼime ahịhịa a. Mgbe Rechel hụrụ ahịhịa a, ọ rịọrọ Lịa sị ya, “Biko nyetụ m ụfọdụ nʼime mandreki ndị a nwa gị nwoke kụtara.”<verse eid="GEN 30:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 30:15"/>Ma Lịa zara sị ya, “O zubeere gị na ị napụrụ m di m? Ị chọkwara ịnapụ m mandreki ndị a nwa m nwoke wetaara m?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 30:15">Rechel zara Lịa sị, “Ọ dị mma, ka gị na ya dinaa nʼabalị a ka ọ bụrụ ihe mgbanwo maka mandreki nwa gị nwoke.”<verse eid="GEN 30:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 30:16"/>Ya mere, mgbe Jekọb si nʼọhịa na-alọbata nʼuhuruchi ụbọchị ahụ, Lịa pụrụ izute ya, sị ya, “Ị ga-abakwute m nʼihi na m ejirila m ahịhịa mandreki nwa m nwoke m zụta gị.” Ha dinara nʼabalị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 30:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 30:17"/>Chineke nụrụ olu Lịa, ọ tụụrụ ime mụtara Jekọb nwa nwoke nke ise. <verse eid="GEN 30:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 30:18"/>Lịa sịrị, “Chineke akwụọla m ụgwọ maka odibo m nwanyị m nyere di m.” Ya mere ọ kpọrọ aha ya Isaka.<verse eid="GEN 30:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 30:19"/>Lịa tụkwaara ime ọzọ mụtara Jekọb nwa nwoke nke isii. <verse eid="GEN 30:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 30:20"/>Ugbu a Lịa kwuru sị, “Chineke enyela m ezi onyinye dị oke ọnụ. Ugbu a, di m ga-eji nkwanye ugwu leta m nʼihi na amụọrala m ya ụmụ ndị ikom isii.” Ọ kpọrọ aha ya Zebụlọn.<verse eid="GEN 30:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 30:21"/>Emesịa, Lịa mụrụ nwa nwanyị, kpọọ ya Daịna.<verse eid="GEN 30:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 30:22"/>Chineke chetara Rechel. Ọ nụrụ olu ya, meghee akpanwa ya. <verse eid="GEN 30:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 30:23"/>Nʼihi ya, Rechel tụụrụ ime mụta nwa nwoke. Ọ sịrị, “Chineke ewepụla nkọcha dịịrị m.” <verse eid="GEN 30:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 30:24"/>Rechel kpọrọ aha ya Josef, dị ka ọ sịrị, “Ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nyekwa m nwa nwoke ọzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 30:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Nkwekọrịta Jekọb na Leban</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 30:25"/>Mgbe Rechel mụsịrị Josef, Jekọb jekwuru Leban sị ya, “Zilaga m ka m laghachi nʼebe m na ala nke m. <verse eid="GEN 30:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 30:26"/>Kpọnye m ndị nwunye m, ndị m ji nʼihi ha gbara gị odibo, ha na ụmụ m, ka m lakwaa. Ị maara otu m siri gbaara gị odibo. Kpọnye m ha ka m duru ha laghachi ebe m si bịa.”<verse eid="GEN 30:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 30:27"/>Leban sịrị Jekọb, “Ọ bụrụ na m achọtala amara nʼihu gị biko nọdụ, nʼihi na esi m nʼịgba afa chọpụta na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> agọziela m nʼihi gị.” <verse eid="GEN 30:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 30:28"/>Leban sịrị, “Kwuo ego ole ị chọrọ ka m kwụọ gị, aga m akwụ ya.”<verse eid="GEN 30:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 30:29"/>Jekọb zara sị Leban, “Gị onwe gị maara otu m si gbara gị odibo na ihe mere igwe anụ ụlọ gị ndị m lekọtara. <verse eid="GEN 30:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 30:30"/>Nʼihi na ole na ole ka i nwere mgbe m bịara, ma ugbu a, ha abaala ụba nke ukwuu. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> esitela nʼụkwụ m gọzie gị. Ugbu a, kedụ mgbe m ga-arụkwanụ ọrụ nke mụ onwe m maka ezinaụlọ m?”<verse eid="GEN 30:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 30:31"/>Leban jụrụ Jekọb sị, “Kedụ ihe m ga-enye gị?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 30:31">Jekọb gwara ya sị, “Enyela m ihe ọbụla, kama o nwere otu ihe m chọrọ ka i mee. Ọ bụrụ na i mee ya, aga m alaghachi ilekọta igwe anụ ụlọ gị. <verse eid="GEN 30:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 30:32"/>Kwere ka m jegharịa nʼetiti igwe anụ ụlọ gị, ka m họpụta site nʼetiti igwe atụrụ gị ndị niile tụrụ agwa agwa, na ụmụ atụrụ niile dị oji, na ewu niile tụrụ agwa agwa. Atụrụ na ewu ndị a niile m ga-ahọpụta ga-abụ ụgwọ ọrụ m. <verse eid="GEN 30:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 30:33"/>Ezi omume m ga-azara nʼọdịnihu, mgbe ọbụla ị bịara nyochaa ụgwọ ọrụ ị kwụrụ m. Ewu ọbụla na-atụghị agwa agwa, maọbụ atụrụ ọbụla na-ejighị oji ị chọpụtara nʼetiti igwe ewu na atụrụ nke m ka a ga-agụ dị ka ihe e zuru nʼohi.”<verse eid="GEN 30:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 30:34"/>Leban zara sị ya, “Ọ dị mma. Ya dịrị dịka i kwuru.” <verse eid="GEN 30:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 30:35"/>Nʼotu ụbọchị ahụ, ọ họpụtachara mkpi niile tụrụ agwa maọbụ ntụpọ na nne ewu niile ndị nwere tụrụ agwa maọbụ ntụpọ na nke ọbụla nwere ajị ọcha nʼahụ ya. Ọ họpụtakwara atụrụ ojii niile, nyefee ha nʼaka ụmụ ya ka ha lekọtaa ha. <verse eid="GEN 30:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 30:36"/>Leban jere ije abalị atọ nke kewapụrụ ha site nʼebe Jekọb nọ. Ma Jekọb nọgidere na-elekọta igwe anụ ụlọ Leban ndị ọzọ.<verse eid="GEN 30:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 30:37"/>Mgbe ahụ Jekọb gara gbute ngalaba osisi pọpla, na osisi alụmọnd, na osisi plenụ, kpechapụ ahụ agbụgbọ osisi ndị a, si otu a mee ka ime ime ngalaba osisi ndị a dị ọcha pụta ìhè. <verse eid="GEN 30:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 30:38"/>Ọ tọgbọrọ osisi ndị a o kpechapụtara nʼebe ewu na atụrụ ndị a na-aṅụ mmiri, ka ha cherịta ịhụ ebe igwe anụ ụlọ ndị a nọ mgbe ọbụla ha na-aṅụ mmiri. Nke a mere mgbe igwe anụ ụlọ ndị a na-enwe ekpomọkụ nke ịgba ibe ha, nʼoge ha bịara ịṅụ mmiri, <verse eid="GEN 30:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 30:39"/>ọ bụ nʼihu ngalaba osisi ndị a ka ha na-anọ na-agba onwe ha. Mgbe anụ ụlọ ndị a mụrụ ụmụ, ahụ ụmụ ha na-atụ agwa agwa maọbụ nwe ntụpọ. <verse eid="GEN 30:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 30:40"/>Jekọb na-edo ụmụ igwe ewu na atụrụ ndị a nʼotu akụkụ, ma ọ na-eme ka anụ ụlọ ndị ọzọ chee ihu ha nʼanụ ụlọ Leban ndị tụrụ agwa agwa, maọbụ na-eji oji. Nʼụzọ dị otu a, ọ kewapụtaara onwe ya anụ ụlọ nke ya. O tinyekọtaghị ha nʼanụ ụlọ Leban. <verse eid="GEN 30:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 30:41"/>Mgbe ọbụla nne anụ ụlọ ndị ahụ siri ike nọ nʼọnọdụ ịtụrụ ime, Jekọb na-edobe ngalaba osisi ndị ahụ nʼakụkụ ebe ha na-aṅụ mmiri nʼihu ha, ka ha nọrọ nʼebe ahụ gbaa onwe ha. <verse eid="GEN 30:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 30:42"/>Ma ọ bụrụ na anụ ụlọ ndị ahụ adịghị ike, Jekọb anaghị edebe osisi ndị a nʼihu ha. Ya mere, igwe ewu na atụrụ ndị na-esighị ike gaara Leban. Ma ndị siri ike gaara Jekọb. <verse eid="GEN 30:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 30:43"/>Site nʼụzọ dị otu a, Jekọb ghọrọ onye nwere akụ hie nne. O nwekwara ọtụtụ igwe anụ ụlọ na ọtụtụ ndị na-ejere ya ozi nwoke na nwanyị, na ọtụtụ ịnyịnya kamel, na ọtụtụ ịnyịnya ibu ndị ọzọ.<verse eid="GEN 30:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 30"/>
  <chapter number="31" style="c" sid="GEN 31"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb ahapụ Padan Aram</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 31:1"/>Jekọb nụrụ na ụmụ ndị ikom Leban na-asị, “Jekọb ewerechaala ihe niile nna anyị nwere. O sitere nʼihe nna anyị nwere kpata akụnụba ya niile.” <verse eid="GEN 31:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 31:2"/>Jekọb hụkwara na omume Leban nʼebe ọ nọ adịghịkwa otu ọ dị na mbụ.<verse eid="GEN 31:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 31:3"/>Mgbe ahụ, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> sịrị Jekọb, “Laghachi nʼala nna gị ha, lakwuru ụmụnna gị, aga m anọnyere gị.”<verse eid="GEN 31:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 31:4"/>Ya mere, Jekọb ziri Rechel na Lịa ozi ka ha bịakwute ya nʼọhịa ebe ọ nọ na-elekọta igwe anụ ụlọ ya. <verse eid="GEN 31:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 31:5"/>Ọ sịrị ha, “Ahụla m na omume nna unu nʼebe m nọ adịghịkwa otu ọ dị na mbụ. Ma Chineke nna m ha nọnyeere m. <verse eid="GEN 31:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 31:6"/>Unu maara na eji m ike m niile rụọra nna unu ọrụ. <verse eid="GEN 31:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 31:7"/>Ma nna unu ghọgburu m, gbanwee ụgwọ ọrụ m ugboro iri. Otu ọ dị, Chineke ekweghị ka nna unu merụọ m ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 31:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 31:8"/>Ọ bụrụ na ọ sị, ‘Ndị tụrụ agwa agwa ga-abụ ụgwọ ọrụ gị,’ mgbe ahụ, igwe anụ ụlọ niile na-amụ ụmụ na-abụ ndị tụrụ agwa. Ma ọ bụrụ na ọ sị, ‘Ndị niile nwere ntụpọ ga-abụ ụgwọ ọrụ gị,’ mgbe ahụ, igwe anụ ụlọ niile na-amụ ụmụ na-enwe ntụpọ ọcha nʼahụ ha. <verse eid="GEN 31:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 31:9"/>Chineke napụrụ nna unu anụ ụlọ ya ma nye m ha.<verse eid="GEN 31:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 31:10"/>“Nʼoge ụmụ anụ ụlọ ji atụ ime, eweliri m anya hụ na nrọ na ụmụ mkpi niile na-agba igwe nne ewu bụ ụmụ mkpi ndị tụrụ agwa agwa, ndị nwere akara maọbụ ndị nwere ntụpọ ọcha nʼahụ ha. <verse eid="GEN 31:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 31:11"/>Mgbe ahụ, mmụọ ozi Chineke sịrị m na nrọ, ‘Jekọb.’ Azara m sị, ‘Lee m nʼebe a.’ <verse eid="GEN 31:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 31:12"/>Ọ sịrị m, ‘Lelie anya gị elu, lee ka ị hụ na mkpi niile na-agba igwe nne ewu ndị a bụ mkpi ndị ahụ tụrụ agwa agwa, ndị nwere akara maọbụ ndị nwere ntụpọ ọcha. Nʼihi na ahụla m ihe niile Leban na-eme gị. <verse eid="GEN 31:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 31:13"/>Mụ onwe m bụ Chineke nke Betel, ebe ị wụkwasịrị mmanụ nʼogidi nkume ahụ, ebe ị kwekwara m nkwa. Ugbu a, kulie, hapụ obodo a, laghachi nʼala a nọ mụọ gị.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 31:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 31:14"/>Rechel na Lịa zara sị ya, “Anyị ka nwere oke nʼihe nketa nʼụlọ nna anyị? <verse eid="GEN 31:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 31:15"/>Ọ bụghị dịka ndị ọbịa ka ọ gụnyeziri anyị? Nʼihi na o reela anyị, ripịakwa ụgwọ isi anyị. <verse eid="GEN 31:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 31:16"/>Nʼezie, akụ ndị ahụ Chineke napụrụ nna anyị bụ nke anyị na nke ụmụ anyị. Ya mere, mee ihe ọbụla Chineke sị gị mee.”<verse eid="GEN 31:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 31:17"/>Jekọb biliri, kukwasị ụmụ ya na ndị nwunye ya nʼelu ịnyịnya kamel, <verse eid="GEN 31:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 31:18"/>duru igwe anụ ụlọ ya niile, na ihe ọ kpatara na Padan Aram, lakwuru nna ya Aịzik nʼala Kenan.<verse eid="GEN 31:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 31:19"/>Ka Leban gara ịkpachapụ ajị ụmụ atụrụ ya, Rechel zuuru arụsị ezinaụlọ nna ya. <verse eid="GEN 31:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 31:20"/>Jekọb ghọkwara Leban onye Aram aghụghọ nʼihi na ọ gwaghị ya na ọ na-agbapụ ọsọ. <verse eid="GEN 31:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 31:21"/>Ya mere, o buru ihe niile o nwere gbapụ ọsọ, gbafee iyi ukwu Yufretis, chee ihu nʼala ugwu ugwu Gilead.<verse eid="GEN 31:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Leban achụso Jekọb ọsọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 31:22"/>Abalị atọ agafeelarị tupu a gwa Leban na Jekọb agbalaala. <verse eid="GEN 31:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 31:23"/>O duuru ndị ikwu ya chụọ Jekọb ọsọ abalị asaa tupu ọ chụkwute ya nʼala ugwu ugwu Gilead. <verse eid="GEN 31:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 31:24"/>Ma Chineke bịakwutere Leban onye Aram na nrọ nʼabalị sị ya, “Kpachapụ anya gị, hụ na o nweghị ihe ị gwara Jekọb, maọbụ okwu dị mma, maọbụ nke dị njọ.”<verse eid="GEN 31:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 31:25"/>Jekọb amaala ụlọ ikwu ya nʼala ugwu Gilead mgbe Leban chụkwutere ya. Leban na ndị ikwu ya makwara ụlọ ikwu nke ha nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 31:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 31:26"/>Leban sịrị Jekọb, “Gịnị bụ ihe a i mere? Ị ghọgbuola m. I burula ụmụ m ndị inyom dịka ndị a dọtara nʼagha? <verse eid="GEN 31:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 31:27"/>Gịnị mere i ji ghọgbuo m, zoro ezo gbapụ? Gịnị mere ị gwaghị m ka m jiri ọṅụ na ịbụ abụ nke ya na ịkpọ ụbọ akwara na iti ịgba so, zilaga gị? <verse eid="GEN 31:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 31:28"/>Gịnị mere i nyeghị m ohere ka m sutu ụmụ ụmụ m na ụmụ m ndị inyom ọnụ sị ha laa nke ọma? Omume a i mere bụ omume nzuzu. <verse eid="GEN 31:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 31:29"/>Enwere m ike merụọ gị ahụ ugbu a, ma Chineke nke nna gị mere ka m hụ ya anya na nrọ nʼabalị gara aga. Ọ dọrọ m aka na ntị sị m, ‘Kpachapụ anya gị hụ na o nweghị ihe ị gwara Jekọb, maọbụ okwu dị mma, maọbụ nke dị njọ.’ <verse eid="GEN 31:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 31:30"/>Ugbu a, ị na-ala nʼihi na ọ gụrụ gị agụụ ịlaghachi nʼụlọ nna gị, ma gịnị mere i ji zuru chi m?”<verse eid="GEN 31:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 31:31"/>Jekọb zara sị Leban, “Nʼihi na m tụrụ egwu, nʼihi na m chere sị na ị ga-eji ike napụ m ụmụ gị ndị inyom a. <verse eid="GEN 31:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 31:32"/>Ma ọ bụrụ na ị chọta onye ọbụla ji chi gị ndị a, onye ahụ ga-anwụ. Nʼihu ndị ikwu gị ndị a, chọgharịa nʼonwe gị, lee ma ị ga-achọta ihe ọbụla bụ nke gị dị m nʼaka. Ọ bụrụ na ị chọta ya, were ya.” Ma Jekọb amaghị na Rechel zuuru chi ndị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 31:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 31:33"/>Ya mere, Leban bara nʼụlọ ikwu Jekọb, na nʼime ụlọ ikwu Lịa, na nʼime ụlọ ikwu ndị odibo nwanyị abụọ ya, ma o nweghị ihe ọ chọtara. O sitere nʼụlọ ikwu Lịa pụta baa nʼụlọ ikwu Rechel. <verse eid="GEN 31:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 31:34"/>Nʼoge a, Rechel ewerela arụsị ezinaụlọ ndị ahụ tinye ha nʼime akwa e ji anọkwasị nʼelu ịnyịnya kamel nọdụ ọdụ nʼelu ya. Leban chọgharịrị ebe niile nʼime ụlọ ikwu ahụ ma ọ chọtaghị arụsị ezinaụlọ ndị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 31:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 31:35"/>Mgbe ahụ, Rechel gwara nna ya Leban sị, “Biko, ewela iwe nna m ukwu, nʼihi na enweghị m ike ibili ọtọ nʼihu gị. Anọ m nʼọnọdụ ndị inyom na-anọ kwa ọnwa.” Leban chọgharịrị ebe niile, ma ọ hụghị arụsị ezinaụlọ ndị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 31:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 31:36"/>Iwe were Jekọb megide Leban. O ji iwe jụọ Leban sị, “Gịnị bụ njehie m? Gịnị bụ mmehie m mere i ji si otu a na-achụsi m ike? <verse eid="GEN 31:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 31:37"/>Ugbu a, ị chọgharịala nʼibu m niile, gịnị ka ị chọtara bụ nke gị? Wepụta ya nʼihu ndị ikwu gị na nʼihu ndị nke m, ka ha kpeere mụ na gị ikpe.<verse eid="GEN 31:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 31:38"/>“Iri afọ abụọ ka mụ na gị nọrọ. O nweghị mgbe ime pụrụ ụmụ ewu na atụrụ gị; o nwekwaghị mgbe m riri ebule si nʼigwe anụ ụlọ gị. <verse eid="GEN 31:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 31:39"/><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">31:39 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ọ bụrụ na anụ ọhịa adọgbuo atụrụ e nyere onye ọzụzụ atụrụ ka o lekọta, onye ọzụzụ atụrụ ahụ ga-eweta ụfọdụ nʼime anụ ahụ a dọgburu adọgbu, iji gosi ihe mere. Mgbe ahụ, o nweghị onye ọbụla ga-asị ya kwụọ ụgwọ ọbụla, nʼihi anụ ụlọ ahụ nwụrụ anwụ. <char style="xt"><ref loc="EXO 22:13">Ọpụ 22:13</ref></char></char></note>O nweghị mgbe m welataara gị anụ ụlọ nke anụ ọhịa dọgburu, kama akwụrụ m ụgwọ ha. I mekwara ka m kwụghachi gị anụ ụlọ ọbụla e zuru nʼohi, maọbụ nʼehihie, maọbụ nʼabalị. <verse eid="GEN 31:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 31:40"/>Nʼime oke anwụ nke ehihie ka m rụụrụ gị ọrụ. Rụọkwara gị ọrụ nʼoge oyi na-atụ, nʼabalị ụra sikwa nʼanya m pụọ. <verse eid="GEN 31:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 31:41"/>Otu a ka ọ dịrị m iri afọ abụọ m jeere gị ozi. Arụrụ m gị ọrụ afọ iri na anọ maka ụmụ gị ndị inyom abụọ ndị a, afọ isii ka m lekọtara igwe ewu na atụrụ gị. Ị nọkwa nʼime ihe ndị a gbanwee ụgwọ ọrụ m ugboro iri. <verse eid="GEN 31:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 31:42"/>A sị na Chineke m, Chineke Ebraham, onye ahụ a na-atụ egwu nke Aịzik, anọnyereghị m, ị gaara ezilaga m nʼaka efu, agaara m agbara aka laa. Ma Chineke ahụla ịrụsị ọrụ ike m, na nhụju anya m niile, ọ bụ ya mere o ji baara gị mba nʼabalị gara aga.”<verse eid="GEN 31:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 31:43"/>Mgbe ahụ Leban zaghachiri sị Jekọb, “Ndị inyom ndị a bụ ụmụ m. Ụmụaka ndị a bụ ụmụ m. Igwe anụ ụlọ ndị a bụ nke m. Ihe ndị a niile ị na-ahụ anya bụ nke m. Olee otu m ga-esi merụọ ụmụ m, na ụmụ ụmụ m ahụ? <verse eid="GEN 31:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="GEN 31:44"/>Ugbu a, bịa ka anyị gbaa ndụ mụ na gị, ka ọ bụrụ ihe ama nʼetiti anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 31:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="GEN 31:45"/>Ya mere, Jekọb weere otu nkume guzo ya ọtọ dịka ogidi. <verse eid="GEN 31:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="GEN 31:46"/>Jekọb gwakwara ndị so ya sị ha, “Tụtụkọta nkume.” Ha tụtụkọtara nkume wụsa ha nʼotu ebe mee ka ọ laa elu. Emesịa, ha nọdụrụ nʼakụkụ nkume ndị ahụ rie nri.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">31:46 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Oge ọbụla mmadụ na ibe ya gbara ndụ, ha na-eri nri a na-akpọ, nri ọgbụgba ndụ iji mesie ọgbụgba ndụ ahụ ike.</char></note> <verse eid="GEN 31:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="GEN 31:47"/>Leban kpọrọ nkume ndị ahụ Jega-Sahaduta, nʼasụsụ nke ya. Jekọb kpọrọ ya Galeed, nʼasụsụ nke ya.<verse eid="GEN 31:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="GEN 31:48"/>Emesịa, Leban sịrị, “Ka nkume ndị a bụrụ ihe ama nʼetiti mụ na gị taa.” Nke a mere e ji kpọọ ya Galeed. <verse eid="GEN 31:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="GEN 31:49"/>A kpọkwara ya Mizpa, nʼihi na Leban sịrị, “Ka <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> bụrụ onye ga-eche mụ na gị nche ịhụ na onye ọbụla nʼime anyị debere ọgbụgba ndụ a, mgbe anyị na-anọghị ibe anyị nso. <verse eid="GEN 31:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="GEN 31:50"/>Ọ bụrụ na i mee ụmụ m ndị inyom ihe ọjọọ, maọbụ lụọ ndị inyom ndị ọzọ tinyere ha, o nweghị onye nʼime anyị ga-amata, ma cheta na Chineke ga-abụ onyeama nʼetiti mụ na gị.”<verse eid="GEN 31:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="GEN 31:51"/>Leban gwakwara Jekọb sị, “Lee nkume ndị a a wụsara nʼebe a na ogidi m mere ka o guzo nʼetiti mụ na gị. <verse eid="GEN 31:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="GEN 31:52"/>Nkume ndị a a wụsara bụ akaebe, ogidi a bụkwa ihe ama. Agaghị m agabiga nkume ndị a a wụsara gafeeta nʼakụkụ nke gị ime gị ihe ọjọọ. Gị onwe gị agaghị agabiga nkume ndị a a wụsara na ogidi a gafeeta nʼakụkụ nke m ime m ihe ọjọọ. <verse eid="GEN 31:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="GEN 31:53"/>Ka Chineke Ebraham na Chineke Nahọ,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">31:53 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nahọ bụ nwanne Ebraham, <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 11:26">Jen 11:26</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 22:20">22:20</ref></char> bụrụkwa nna nna Leban. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 24:24">Jen 24:24</ref>,<ref loc="GEN 24:29">29</ref></char> Leban bụ nwoke na-efe ọtụtụ chi. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 31:19">Jen 31:19</ref></char></char></note> Chineke nna ha, bụrụ onye ikpe nʼetiti mụ na gị.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 31:53">Ya mere Jekọb ji onye ahụ a na-atụ egwu nke nna ya Aịzik ṅụọ iyi. <verse eid="GEN 31:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="GEN 31:54"/>Ọ chụrụ aja nʼala ugwu ugwu ahụ, kpọọ ndị ikwu ya niile oriri. Mgbe ha richara nri, ha rahụrụ ụra nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 31:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="GEN 31:55"/>Nʼisi ụtụtụ echi ya, Leban biliri sutu ụmụ ya ndị inyom na ụmụ ụmụ ya ọnụ. Ọ gọziri ha, hapụ ha laghachi ụlọ ha.<verse eid="GEN 31:55"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 31"/>
  <chapter number="32" style="c" sid="GEN 32"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb akwadobe maka izute Ịsọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 32:1"/>Jekọb nʼonwe ya hapụrụ gawa nʼihu nʼije ya. Ndị mmụọ ozi Chineke zutere ya nʼụzọ. <verse eid="GEN 32:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 32:2"/>Mgbe Jekọb hụrụ ha, o kwuru sị, “Ebe a bụ ụlọ ikwu Chineke!” Ọ kpọrọ ebe ahụ, Mahanaim.<verse eid="GEN 32:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 32:3"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb zipụrụ ndị ozi ka ha jee hụ Ịsọ nwanne ya nwoke nʼala Sia,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">32:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ala Sịa nke dị nso iyi Jabọk, ga-emesịa bụrụ ala dị mkpa nʼoge ọchịchị eze Devid na Solomọn. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 14:6">Jen 14:6</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 33:14">33:14</ref>,<ref loc="GEN 33:16">16</ref></char></char></note> nʼobodo Edọm. <verse eid="GEN 32:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 32:4"/>O ziri ha ozi sị, “Ihe a bụ ihe unu ga-agwa nna m ukwu Ịsọ, ‘Odibo gị Jekọb kwuru sị, Ọ bụ na nke Leban ka m jere kemgbe, ọ bụkwa ebe ahụ ka m nọ ruo ugbu a. <verse eid="GEN 32:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 32:5"/>Enwere m ọtụtụ ehi, na ịnyịnya ibu, na igwe atụrụ na ewu, na ndị odibo ndị nwoke na ndị nwanyị. Ana m ezigara onyenwe m ozi a ka m nata ihuọma nʼebe ọ nọ.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 32:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 32:6"/>Mgbe ndị ozi ahụ lọghachikwutere Jekọb, ha gwara ya sị ya, “Anyị jekwuru nwanne gị nwoke Ịsọ dị ka i ziri anyị. Ugbu a, ọ na-abịa. Ọ chị narị ndị ikom anọ na-abịa izute gị.”<verse eid="GEN 32:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 32:7"/>Ụjọ tụrụ Jekọb nke ukwuu, obi ya jupụtakwara na nsogbu. Nʼihi nke a, o kewara ndị niile so ya ụzọ abụọ, tinyere anụ ụlọ ya, na igwe ehi ya na ịnyịnya kamel ya. <verse eid="GEN 32:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 32:8"/>O chere nʼobi ya sị, “Ọ bụrụ na Ịsọ alụso otu nʼime ụzọ abụọ a ọgụ, otu ụzọ fọdụrụ ga-enwe ike gbalaga.”<verse eid="GEN 32:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 32:9"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb kpere ekpere sị, “Chineke nke nna m Ebraham, Chineke nke nna m Aịzik, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, gị onye gwara m sị, ‘Laghachi nʼala gị na nʼebe ụmụnna gị nọ, aga m eme ka ihe gaara gị nke ọma.’ <verse eid="GEN 32:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 32:10"/>Ekwesighị m obi ebere na ikwesi ntụkwasị obi nke i gosiri ohu gị. Mgbe m gabigara Jọdan a, enweghị m ihe ọbụla karịa mkpanaka m, ma ugbu a, abụ m ọmụma ụlọ ikwu abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 32:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 32:11"/>Zọpụta m, arịọ m gị, site nʼaka nwanne m Ịsọ, nʼihi na egwu na-atụ m na ọ ga-abịa lụso m agha, lụsokwa ndị nne a na ụmụntakịrị ha agha. <verse eid="GEN 32:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 32:12"/>Ọ bụ gị kwuru sị, ‘Aga m eme ka ihe gaara gị nke ọma, meekwa ka ụmụ ụmụ gị dịrị ka aja nke dị nʼọnụ osimiri, nke mmadụ na-apụghị ịgụta ọnụ.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 32:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 32:13"/>Jekọb rahụrụ nʼebe ahụ nʼabalị ahụ. Site nʼihe niile o nwere, ọ họpụtara onyinye ọ ga-enye nwanne ya Ịsọ. <verse eid="GEN 32:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 32:14"/>Ọ kwadoro inye ya: narị nne ewu abụọ (200), iri mkpi abụọ (20), narị nne atụrụ abụọ (200), iri ebule abụọ (20) <verse eid="GEN 32:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 32:15"/>Iri nne ịnyịnya kamel atọ (30) na ụmụ ha, na iri nne ehi anọ (40), oke ehi iri (10), iri nne ịnyịnya ibu abụọ (20), oke ịnyịnya ibu iri (10). <verse eid="GEN 32:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 32:16"/>O weere onyinye ndị a niile nyefee nʼaka ndị ozi ya nʼusoro dịka ụdị ha si dị. Ọ gwara ndị na-ejere ya ozi sị ha, “Burunu ụzọ na-aga, meenụ ka ohere dị nʼetiti igwe anụ na igwe ibe ya.”<verse eid="GEN 32:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 32:17"/>O nyere onye mbụ iwu sị ha, “Mgbe Ịsọ nwanne m zutere unu jụọ unu ajụjụ sị, ‘Onye bụ nna unu ukwu? Ebee ka unu na-aga? Onye nwe anụ ụlọ ndị a niile unu chị na-aga?’ <verse eid="GEN 32:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 32:18"/>Unu ga-aza sị ya, ‘Anụ ụlọ ndị a bụ nke ohu gị Jekọb. Ha bụ onyinye e zitere onyenwe m Ịsọ, lee ka ọ na-abịa nʼazụ anyị.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 32:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 32:19"/>Otu ozi ahụ ka Jekọb ziri onye nke abụọ na onye nke atọ, na ndị ọzọ niile chị igwe anụ ụlọ, sị ha, “Unu ga-agwa Ịsọ otu ihe ahụ mgbe unu zutere ya. <verse eid="GEN 32:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 32:20"/>Hụkwanụ na unu gwara ya sị, ‘Ohu gị Jekọb nọ nʼazụ anyị.’ ” Echiche ya bụ, “Aga m eji onyinye ndị a niile m na-ezipụrụ ya mee ka obi ya dajụọ, nke ọ ga-abụ mgbe mụ na ya zutere, ma eleghị anya, ọ ga-anabata m.” <verse eid="GEN 32:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 32:21"/>Mgbe o zipụchasịrị onyinye ndị ahụ niile, Jekọb rahụrụ ụra nʼụlọ ikwu ya nʼabalị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 32:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Mgba Jekọb na Chineke gbara</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 32:22"/>Nʼabalị ahụ, Jekọb biliri duru ndị nwunye ya abụọ na ndị odibo nwanyị ya abụọ, na ụmụ ya iri na otu, site nʼebe na-adịghị omimi nke iyi Jabọk kpọfee ha. <verse eid="GEN 32:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 32:23"/>Mgbe ọ kpọfechara ha, o bufekwara ihe niile o nwere. <verse eid="GEN 32:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 32:24"/>Emesịa, Jekọb lọghachiri nọdụ naanị ya. Mgbe ahụ, otu nwoke bịara gbaso ya mgba. Ha abụọ gbagidere mgba a tutu chi ebido ịbọ. <verse eid="GEN 32:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 32:25"/>Mgbe nwoke ahụ hụrụ na ọ pụghị imeri Jekọb na mgba ahụ, o tiri Jekọb aka nʼọkpụ, mee ka ọkpụ ya hịkwapụ site nʼọnọdụ ya. <verse eid="GEN 32:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 32:26"/>Mgbe nke a mesịrị, nwoke ahụ gwara Jekọb sị ya: “Hapụ m aka ka m laa, nʼihi na chi ebidola ịbọ.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 32:26">Ma Jekọb zara sị ya, “Ọ bụ naanị mgbe ị gọziri m ka m ga-ahapụ gị ka ị laa.”<verse eid="GEN 32:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 32:27"/>Mgbe ahụ nwoke ahụ jụrụ Jekọb ajụjụ sị ya, “Gịnị bụ aha gị?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 32:27">Ọ zara sị, “Aha m bụ Jekọb.”<verse eid="GEN 32:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 32:28"/>Nwoke ahụ zara sị ya, “Aha gị agaghị abụkwa Jekọb, kama ọ ga-abụ Izrel, nʼihi na gị na Chineke na ndị mmadụ gbara mgba, ị mmeri.”<verse eid="GEN 32:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 32:29"/>Jekọb sịrị, “Biko gwa m aha gị.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 32:29">Ma ọ zaghachiri, “Gịnị mere ị ji ajụ aha m?” Mgbe ahụ, ọ gọziri ya nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 32:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 32:30"/>Jekọb kpọrọ aha ebe ahụ Peniel, nʼihi na ọ sịrị, “Ahụla m Chineke ihu na ihu, ma e chebere ndụ m.”<verse eid="GEN 32:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 32:31"/>Anyanwụ awaala mgbe Jekọb si Peniel gafee. Ma nʼihi ihe mere ya nʼọkpụ, ọ naghị agazikwa ije. <verse eid="GEN 32:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 32:32"/>Ọ bụ ihe a mere ụmụ Izrel adịghị eri akwara anụ jikọtara ukwu anụ na ọkpụ ya ruo taa. Nʼihi na ihe ahụ mere Jekọb metụtara akwara ukwu ya.<verse eid="GEN 32:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 32"/>
  <chapter number="33" style="c" sid="GEN 33"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb ezute Ịsọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 33:1"/>Jekọb lepụrụ anya nʼihu, hụ Ịsọ ka ọ na-abịa, ya na narị ndị ikom anọ ndị so ya. Nʼihi ya, o kesara ụmụntakịrị ndị ahụ, nʼetiti Lịa, na Rechel na ndị odibo nwanyị ya abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 33:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 33:2"/>O mere ka ndị odibo nwanyị ya abụọ ahụ na ụmụ ha buru ụzọ, Lịa na ụmụ ya esoro nʼazụ, ebe Rechel na Josef nọ nʼazụ azụ. <verse eid="GEN 33:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 33:3"/>Ma ya onwe ya buru ụzọ na-aga nʼihu ha niile, na-akpọ isiala nye Ịsọ ugboro asaa, tutu ruo mgbe ọ bịarutere nwanne ya nwoke nso.<verse eid="GEN 33:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 33:4"/>Ma Ịsọ gbaara ọsọ bịakwute ya, makụọ ya, jikụọ ya aka nʼolu, sutu ya ọnụ. Ha abụọ kwara akwa. <verse eid="GEN 33:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 33:5"/>Mgbe Ịsọ lelitere anya hụ ndị inyom ndị a na ụmụntakịrị ndị ahụ. Ọ sịrị, “Ndị ole bụ ndị a gị na ha so?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 33:5">Jekọb sịrị, “Ha bụ ụmụ Chineke sitere nʼamara ya nye ohu gị.”<verse eid="GEN 33:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 33:6"/>Mgbe ahụ, ndị odibo nwanyị abụọ na ụmụ ha rutere nso, kpọọ isiala. <verse eid="GEN 33:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 33:7"/>Lịa na ụmụ ya bịarutekwara kpọọ isiala, nʼikpeazụ Rechel na Josef bịara kpọọkwa isiala.<verse eid="GEN 33:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 33:8"/>Ịsọ sịrị, “Igwe ewu na atụrụ ndị a niile m zutere nʼụzọ, gịnị ka ọ pụtara?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 33:8">Jekọb zara, “Ha bụ maka ịnata ihuọma nʼaka gị, onyenwe m.”<verse eid="GEN 33:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 33:9"/>Ma Ịsọ sịrị, “Nwanne m nwoke, debere onwe gị ihe i nwere, nʼihi na enwere m akụ hie nne.”<verse eid="GEN 33:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 33:10"/>Jekọb sịrị, “E, biko, ọ bụrụ na m achọtala ihuọma nʼanya gị, nara m onyinye ndị a. Nʼihi na ịhụ gị anya dịka ilekwasị Chineke anya nʼihu, nke ka nke, otu a i ji ihu ọcha nabata m. <verse eid="GEN 33:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 33:11"/>Biko nara onyinye ndị ahụ e wetaara gị, nʼihi na Chineke emelara m amara. Enwekwara m ihe ga-ezuru m.” Jekọb kwagidere ya, ọ naara onyinye ndị ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 33:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 33:12"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ịsọ sịrị, “Bilienụ ka anyị malite ije ịlaghachi. Aga m esonyere unu.”<verse eid="GEN 33:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 33:13"/>Ma Jekọb sịrị ya, “Onyenwe m, ị maara na ụmụntakịrị ndị a adịghị ike, aga m ejikwa nwayọọ chịa ụmụ atụrụ ndị a na ehi ndị na-enye ụmụ ha ara. Ọ bụrụ na a chịa ha nʼike nʼime otu ụbọchị, ụmụ anụmanụ ndị a niile ga-anwụ. <verse eid="GEN 33:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 33:14"/>Ya mere, ka onyenwe m buru ohu ya ụzọ na-aga, ma ka m jiri nwayọọ nwayọọ na-abịa, dịka ike igwe anụ ndị a na ụmụaka ndị a si dị. Tutu ruo mgbe m ga-ezute onyenwe m na Sia.”<verse eid="GEN 33:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 33:15"/>Ịsọ sịrị, “Ọ bụrụ otu a, ka m hapụrụ gị ụfọdụ ndị a mụ na ha so.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 33:15">Ma Jekọb sịrị, “Nʼihi gịnị kwanụ? Ka m hụta naanị ihuọma nʼanya onyenwe m.”<verse eid="GEN 33:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 33:16"/>Ịsọ laghachikwara azụ na Sia nʼotu ụbọchị ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 33:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 33:17"/>Ma Jekọb na ezinaụlọ ya jere Sukọt, ebe o wuuru onwe ya ụlọ obibi, wuokwara anụ ụlọ ya ụlọ obibi ha. Ọ bụ nke a mere e ji kpọọ ebe ahụ Sukọt.<verse eid="GEN 33:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 33:18"/>Mgbe Jekọb si Padan Aram lọghachi, o rutere obodo Shekem nke dị nʼala Kenan nʼudo. O mara ụlọ ikwu ya nʼihu obodo ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 33:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 33:19"/>Ọ zụrụ ala ebe o mara ụlọ ikwu ya nʼaka ụmụ Hamọ, nna Shekem, ọ kwụrụ narị mkpụrụ ọlaọcha maka ala ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 33:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 33:20"/>Nʼebe ahụ, o wuru ebe ịchụ aja, kpọọ aha ya El Elohe Izrel.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">33:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nke a pụtara Chineke Izrel dị ike nke ukwuu.</char></note><verse eid="GEN 33:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 33"/>
  <chapter number="34" style="c" sid="GEN 34"/>
  <para style="s1">Daịna na nwa eze Shekem</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 34:1"/>Ugbu a, Daịna nwa nwanyị Lịa mụụrụ Jekọb pụrụ ileta ndị inyom ala ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 34:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 34:2"/>Mgbe Shekem, nwa Hamọ onye Hiv, onye na-achị mpaghara ahụ, hụrụ ya, ọ kpọọrọ ya jiri ike ya na ya dinaa. <verse eid="GEN 34:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 34:3"/>Mkpụrụobi ya gara nʼebe Daịna nwa Jekọb, ọ hụrụ nwantakịrị nwanyị ahụ nʼanya, gwakwa ya okwu dị nro. <verse eid="GEN 34:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 34:4"/>Shekem sịrị nna ya bụ Hamọ “Lụtara m nwaagbọghọ a, ka ọ bụrụ nwunye m.”<verse eid="GEN 34:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 34:5"/>Mgbe Jekọb nụrụ na e merụrụ Daịna nwa ya nwanyị, nʼihi na ụmụ ya ndị ikom nọ nʼọhịa ebe ha na-azụ anụ ụlọ, ọ gbara nkịtị na-emeghị ihe ọbụla ruo mgbe ha lọtara.<verse eid="GEN 34:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 34:6"/>Hamọ bụ nna Shekem, pụkwuuru Jekọb ka ha kparịta ụka. <verse eid="GEN 34:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 34:7"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb si nʼọhịa na-alọta mgbe ha nụrụ ihe merenụ, iwe na ọnụma juputara ha obi nke ukwuu nʼihi na Shekem mere ihe na-eweta ihere nʼIzrel site nʼidinakwuru ada Jekọb, ihe a na-ekwesighị ime eme.<verse eid="GEN 34:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 34:8"/>Ma Hamọ sịrị ha, “Nwa m nwoke Shekem hụrụ nwa unu nwanyị nʼanya. Biko, kwerenụ ka ọ lụọ ya. <verse eid="GEN 34:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 34:9"/>Kwerenụ ka anyị na unu na-alụrịta. Ka anyị na-alụ ụmụ ndị inyom unu, ka unu na-alụkwa ụmụ ndị inyom anyị. <verse eid="GEN 34:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 34:10"/>Unu nwere ike biri nʼetiti anyị. Ala a ghere oghe nye unu. Birinụ nʼime ya, na-azụkwanụ ahịa nʼime ya, nwekwanụ akụ nʼime ya nye onwe unu.”<verse eid="GEN 34:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 34:11"/>Shekem gwara nna na ụmụnne Daịna ndị ikom sị, “Kwerenụ ka m chọta ihuọma nʼebe unu nọ, aga m enyekwa unu ihe ọbụla unu chọrọ ka m nye unu. <verse eid="GEN 34:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 34:12"/>Ihe ọbụla unu sị m kwụọ dịka ego akụ ọlụlụ nwunye, ya na onyinye ọbụla unu si m nye aga m enye unu. Naanị kwerenụ ka nwaagbọghọ a bụrụ nwunye m.”<verse eid="GEN 34:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 34:13"/>Ma ụmụ Jekọb jiri aghụghọ zaa Shekem na Hamọ nna ya mgbe ha na-agwa ha okwu, nʼihi na e merụrụ Daịna nwanne ha nwanyị. <verse eid="GEN 34:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 34:14"/>Ha sịrị ha, “Anyị enweghị ike ime ihe a, ị kpọrọ nwanne anyị nwanyị kpọnye nwoke a na-ebighị ugwu. Nke a ga-abụrụ anyị ihe ihere. <verse eid="GEN 34:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 34:15"/>Anyị nwere ike ikwenye ka ọ lụọ ya ma ọ bụrụ na unu ga-adị ka anyị, ka e bie ndị nwoke unu niile ugwu. <verse eid="GEN 34:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 34:16"/>Mgbe ahụ anyị ga-edunye unu ụmụ ndị inyom anyị, ma kpọrọkwa ụmụ ndị inyom unu dịka ndị nwunye anyị. Anyị ga-ebi nʼetiti unu, soro unu bụrụ otu ndị. <verse eid="GEN 34:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 34:17"/>Ọ bụrụ na unu agaghị ekwe ka e bie unu ugwu, anyị ga-akpọrọ nwanne anyị nwanyị laa.”<verse eid="GEN 34:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 34:18"/>Obi tọrọ Hamọ na Shekem nwa ya nwoke ụtọ nʼihi ihe ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb kwuru. <verse eid="GEN 34:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 34:19"/>Nwokorobịa ahụ bụ onye a na-asọpụrụ karịa onye ọbụla nʼụlọ nna ya egbughị oge ime ihe ha kwuru, nʼihi na ihe banyere nwa nwanyị Jekọb dị ya mma nke ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 34:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 34:20"/>Emesịa, Hamọ na Shekem nwa ya nwoke gara nʼọnụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">34:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ọ bụ nʼọnụ ụzọ ama nke obodo ka ndị okenye na-ezukọ, akparịta ụka. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 19:2">Jen 19:2</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 23:10">23:10</ref>; <ref loc="RUT 4:1">Rut 4:1</ref>,<ref loc="RUT 4:11">11</ref>; <ref loc="2SA 15:2">2Sa 15:2</ref></char></char></note> ụzọ ama nke obodo ha gwa ndị ikom obodo ha okwu, sị. <verse eid="GEN 34:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 34:21"/>“Ndị ikom ndị a nwere mmasị nʼebe anyị nọ. Kwerenụ ka ha biri nʼala anyị, ka ha na-agagharị kwa nʼime ya. Anyị nwere ala buru ibu nke ga-ezuru anyị na ha. Ha ga-alụ ụmụ nwanyị anyị, anyị ga-alụkwa ndị nke ha. <verse eid="GEN 34:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 34:22"/>Ma ọ dị otu ihe ha chọrọ ka anyị mee tupu ha ekwere ibi nʼetiti anyị ka anyị na ha bụrụ otu ndị. Ọ bụ ibi ndị ikom anyị niile ugwu dịka e si bie ha ugwu. <verse eid="GEN 34:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 34:23"/>Ọ bụrụ na unu chọrọ ka anụ ụlọ ha niile na akụ ha niile bụrụ nke anyị, ọ dị mma ka anyị kwenyere ha, ka ha binyere anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 34:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 34:24"/>Ndị ikom niile bịara nʼọnụ ụzọ ama obodo ahụ kwenyere nʼokwu Hamọ na nwa ya nwoke Shekem. E bikwara nwoke ọbụla nọ nʼobodo ahụ ugwu.<verse eid="GEN 34:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 34:25"/>O ruo nʼụbọchị nke atọ, mgbe ọnya ugwu ha na-egbu ha mgbu, ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb abụọ, Simiọn na Livayị, ụmụnne Daịna, jiri mma agha ha pụkwuru ndị bi nʼobodo ahụ na-atụghị anya na ihe dị otu a ga-eme, gbuo ndị ikom niile nọ nʼobodo ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 34:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 34:26"/>Ha gbukwara Hamọ na Shekem nwa ya nwoke, kpọpụta Daịna site nʼụlọ Shekem, laghachi nʼụlọ ha. <verse eid="GEN 34:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 34:27"/>Mgbe ahụ ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb niile bịakwasịrị ndị a e gburu egbu, kwakọọ ihe niile dị nʼobodo ahụ niile, nʼihi mmerụ e merụrụ nwanne ha nwanyị. <verse eid="GEN 34:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 34:28"/>Ha kwakọọrọ ngwongwo niile dị nʼobodo ahụ, kpụrụkwa anụ ụlọ niile, igwe ewu na atụrụ, igwe ehi na igwe ịnyịnya ibu niile, na ihe niile dị nʼime obodo ahụ, na ihe niile dị nʼubi ndị ahụ obodo nwere. <verse eid="GEN 34:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 34:29"/>Akụ ha niile, na ndị inyom ha niile na ụmụntakịrị ha, na ihe niile dị nʼime ụlọ ha, ka ha weere dịka ihe a dọtara nʼagha.<verse eid="GEN 34:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 34:30"/>Mgbe Jekọb hụrụ ihe ụmụ ya mere, ọ kpọrọ Simiọn na Livayị sị ha, “Unu ebuterela m nsogbu mee ka m bụrụ ihe na-esi isi ọjọọ nʼetiti ndị Kenan na ndị Periz nwe ala a. Ebe anyị dị ole na ole, ọ bụrụ na ha ejikọta onwe ha ọnụ lụso m agha, ha ga-ekpochapụ mụ na ezinaụlọ m.”<verse eid="GEN 34:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 34:31"/>Ma ha zara sị ya, “O kwesiri ka o meso nwanne anyị nwanyị mmeso dịka ọ bụ akwụna?”<verse eid="GEN 34:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 34"/>
  <chapter number="35" style="c" sid="GEN 35"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb alọghachi Betel</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 35:1"/>Chineke sịrị Jekọb, “Bilie, gaa Betel, birikwa nʼebe ahụ. Wuo ebe ịchụ aja nye Chineke, onye mere ka ị hụ ya mgbe ị na-agbanarị Ịsọ nwanne gị nwoke.”<verse eid="GEN 35:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 35:2"/>Ya mere, Jekọb gwara ndị ezinaụlọ ya na ndị niile so ya sị, “Wezuganụ chi ndị ala ọzọ dị nʼetiti unu. Doonụ onwe unu ọcha, gbanweekwanụ uwe unu. <verse eid="GEN 35:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 35:3"/>Bilienụ, ka anyị gaa Betel, ebe m ga-ewu ebe ịchụ aja nye Chineke, onye zara m oku nʼụbọchị nsogbu m, ma nọnyekwara m na njem nke m gara.” <verse eid="GEN 35:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 35:4"/>Ya mere, ha nyere Jekọb chi ndị ala ọzọ niile ha ji nʼaka, na ọla<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">35:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼoge ahụ, ndị mmadụ kwenyere na ọlantị ha na-eyi bụ ihe na-echekwa ha.</char></note> niile dị ha na ntị. Jekọb chịịrị ha niile lie ha nʼokpuru osisi ook dị na Shekem. <verse eid="GEN 35:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 35:5"/>Ha biliri ije. Egwu Chineke dakwasịrị obodo niile gbara ha gburugburu. Ọ dịghị ndị chụsoro ha.<verse eid="GEN 35:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 35:6"/>Jekọb na ndị niile so ya rutere Luz, nke a na-akpọkwa Betel nke dị na Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 35:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 35:7"/>Jekọb wuru ebe ịchụ aja nʼebe a, kpọọ aha ebe ahụ El Betel, nʼihi na ọ bụ nʼebe ahụ ka Chineke gosiri ya onwe ya mgbe ọ na-agbanarị Ịsọ nwanne ya nwoke.<verse eid="GEN 35:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 35:8"/>Mgbe nke a gasịrị, Debọra, nwanyị lekọtara Ribeka mgbe ọ bụ nwantakịrị, nwụrụ. E liri ya nʼokpuru osisi ook dị na Betel. A kpọkwara ebe ahụ, “Osisi ook ebe ịkwa akwa.”<verse eid="GEN 35:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 35:9"/>Chineke gosiri Jekọb onwe ya ọzọ, mgbe o sitere na Padan Aram pụta, gọziekwa ya. <verse eid="GEN 35:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 35:10"/>Chineke sịrị ya, “Aha gị bụ Jekọb ma a gaghị akpọkwa gị Jekọb ọzọ, kama aha gị ga-abụ Izrel.” Ya mere ọ kpọrọ ya Izrel.<verse eid="GEN 35:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 35:11"/>Chineke sịrị ya, “Abụ m Chineke onye pụrụ ime ihe niile. Mụọ ọmụmụ, baakwa ụba nʼọnụọgụgụ. Otu mba na igwe mba ga-esi na gị pụta. Ndị eze ga-esitekwa gị nʼahụ pụta. <verse eid="GEN 35:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 35:12"/>Ala ahụ m nyere Ebraham na Aịzik ka m na-enyekwa gị. Aga m enyekwa ya ụmụ ụmụ gị ndị ga-esote gị.” <verse eid="GEN 35:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 35:13"/>Emesịa, Chineke si nʼebe ahụ ha nọ kparịtaa ụka pụọ.<verse eid="GEN 35:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 35:14"/>Jekọb wuru ogidi nkume nʼebe ahụ Chineke nọ gwa ya okwu. Ọ wụsara onyinye ihe ọṅụṅụ wụkwasịkwa mmanụ nʼelu ogidi nkume ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 35:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 35:15"/>Jekọb kpọrọ ebe ahụ ya na Chineke nọ kparịtaa ụka Betel.<verse eid="GEN 35:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụ Rechel na Aịzik</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 35:16"/>Ha biliri ije, site na Betel. Ma mgbe ha ka nọ ebe dị anya site nʼobodo Efrat, Rechel mụrụ nwa, ma o nwere ihe mgbu ka ọ na-amụ nwa. <verse eid="GEN 35:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 35:17"/>Mgbe o sitere nʼoke ihe mgbu na-amụpụta nwa ahụ, nwanyị na-aghọ nwa gwara ya, “Atụla egwu, nʼihi na ọ bụ nwa nwoke ọzọ ka ị mụtara.” <verse eid="GEN 35:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 35:18"/>Ma tupu Rechel ekuo ume ikpeazụ, nʼihi na ọ na-anwụ, ọ kpọrọ aha nwa ọhụrụ ahụ Ben-Oni, ma nna ya kpọrọ ya Benjamin.<verse eid="GEN 35:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 35:19"/>Rechel nwụrụ, e lie ya nʼakụkụ ụzọ gara Efrat, nke a na-akpọkwa Betlehem. <verse eid="GEN 35:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 35:20"/>Jekọb wuru ogidi nʼelu ili ya, nke na-eguzokwa ruo taa, igosi ebe e liri Rechel.<verse eid="GEN 35:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 35:21"/>Izrel malitere ije ya, tutu ruo ebe o wuru ebe izuike ya nʼala dị nʼofe ọzọ nke Migdal Eda. <verse eid="GEN 35:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 35:22"/>Mgbe Izrel bi nʼala ahụ, Ruben gara dinakwuru Bilha, iko nwanyị nna ya. E mekwara ka Izrel nụ ihe a Ruben mere.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 35:22"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="GEN 35:22">Ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb dị iri na abụọ.<verse eid="GEN 35:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 35:23"/>Ụmụ Lịa bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 35:23">Ruben, ọkpara Jekọb.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 35:23">Simiọn, Livayị, Juda, Isaka na Zebụlọn.<verse eid="GEN 35:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 35:24"/>Ụmụ Rechel bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 35:24">Josef na Benjamin.<verse eid="GEN 35:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 35:25"/>Ụmụ Bilha, odibo nwanyị Rechel bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 35:25">Dan na Naftalị.<verse eid="GEN 35:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 35:26"/>Ụmụ Zilpa, odibo nwanyị Lịa bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 35:26">Gad na Asha.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 35:26"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="GEN 35:26">Ụmụ ndị ikom ndị a ka a mụụrụ Jekọb na Padan Aram.<verse eid="GEN 35:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 35:27"/>Nʼikpeazụ, Jekọb bịakwutere nna ya Aịzik na Mamre nke dị nso na Kiriat Arba (ebe a na-akpọ Hebrọn). Ebe ahụ ka Ebraham na Aịzik biri na mbụ. <verse eid="GEN 35:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 35:28"/>Nʼoge ahụ Aịzik gbara narị afọ na iri afọ asatọ. <verse eid="GEN 35:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 35:29"/>Ọ dịkwaghị anya site nʼoge a, Aịzik nwụrụ, mgbe o mere nnọọ agadi. Ụmụ ya ndị ikom abụọ, Ịsọ na Jekọb, liri ya.<verse eid="GEN 35:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 35"/>
  <chapter number="36" style="c" sid="GEN 36"/>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụ ụmụ Ịsọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 36:1"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro agbụrụ Ịsọ, onye a na-akpọ Edọm.<verse eid="GEN 36:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 36:2"/>Ịsọ lụrụ ndị inyom a site nʼala Kenan. Onye nke mbụ bụ Ada nwa Elọn, onye Het. Nke abụọ bụ Oholibama, nwa Ana, nwa nwa Zibiọn, onye Hiv. <verse eid="GEN 36:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 36:3"/>Onye nke atọ bụ Basemat, nwa Ishmel, onye nwanne ya nwanyị bụ Nebaiot.<verse eid="GEN 36:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 36:4"/>Ada mụụrụ Ịsọ Elifaz, ebe Basemat mụrụ Reuel. <verse eid="GEN 36:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 36:5"/>Oholibama mụtaara Jeush na Jalam na Kora. Ndị a bụ ụmụ Ịsọ ndị a mụtara ya nʼala Kenan.<verse eid="GEN 36:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 36:6"/>Emesịa, Ịsọ duuru ndị nwunye ya na ụmụ ya ndị ikom na ndị inyom, na ndị niile nọ nʼezinaụlọ ya. Ọ chịkọọrọ anụ ụlọ ya niile, na akụ niile ọ kpatara nʼala Kenan kwapụ gaa biri nʼala dị anya site nʼebe nwanne ya Jekọb nọ. <verse eid="GEN 36:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 36:7"/>Ebe ọ bụ na akụnụba ha nwere dịkarịrị ukwuu ha ibikọta ọnụ, tinyekwara na ala ebe ha bi enwezighị ike ibuli ha nʼihi anụ ụlọ niile ha nwere. <verse eid="GEN 36:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 36:8"/>Ya mere, Ịsọ gara biri nʼala ugwu ugwu Sia, Ịsọ bụkwa Edọm.<verse eid="GEN 36:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 36:9"/>Nke a bụ akụkọ banyere usoro agbụrụ Ịsọ, nna obodo Edọm, nʼala ugwu ugwu Sia.<verse eid="GEN 36:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 36:10"/>Ndị a bụ aha ụmụ ndị ikom Ịsọ mụtara.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:10">Elifaz bụ ọkpara Ada, nwunye Ịsọ. Nwanne ya bụ Reuel, nwa Basemat, nwunye Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 36:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 36:11"/>Ụmụ Elifaz ndị ikom bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:11">Teman, Ọmaa, Zefo, Gatam na Kenaz. <verse eid="GEN 36:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 36:12"/>Elifaz nwa Ịsọ nwere iko nwanyị aha ya bụ Timna, onye mụtaara ya Amalek. Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Ada, nwunye Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 36:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 36:13"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Reuel bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:13">Nahat, Zera, Shama na Miza. Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ ụmụ Basemat, nwunye Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 36:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 36:14"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ Oholibama, nwunye Ịsọ. Oholibama bụ nwa Ana na nwa nwa Zibiọn. Ọ mụtaara Ịsọ</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:14">Jeush, Jalam na Kora.<verse eid="GEN 36:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 36:15"/>Ndị a bụ ọnụmara si nʼetiti ụmụ ụmụ Ịsọ.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 36:15">Site nʼetiti ụmụ Elifaz, ọkpara Ịsọ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:15">e nwere Ọnụmara Teman, ọnụmara Ọmaa, ọnụmara Zefo, ọnụmara Kenaz. <verse eid="GEN 36:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 36:16"/>Ọnụmara Kora, ọnụmara Gatam na ọnụmara Amalek. Ndị eze ndị a bụ ụmụ Elifaz nʼala Edọm. Ha bụ ụmụ ụmụ Ada.<verse eid="GEN 36:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 36:17"/>Ndị bụ ụmụ Reuel, nwa Ịsọ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:17">e nwere ọnụmara Nahat, ọnụmara Zera, ọnụmara Shama, ọnụmara Miza. Ọnụmara ndị a bụ ụmụ Reuel nʼala Edọm. Ha bụ ụmụ Basemat, nwunye Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 36:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 36:18"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ Oholibama, nwunye Ịsọ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:18">ọnụmara Jeush, ọnụmara Jalam, na ọnụmara Kora. Ndị a bụ ọnụmara ụmụ Oholibama nwa Ana, nwunye Ịsọ.<verse eid="GEN 36:18"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 36:19"/>Ndị a niile bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Ịsọ (ya bụ, Edọm). Ndị a bụkwa ọnụmara ha.<verse eid="GEN 36:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 36:20"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Sia onye Hor, ndị bi nʼakụkụ ala ahụ:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:20">Lotan, Shobal, Zibiọn, Ana, <verse eid="GEN 36:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 36:21"/>Dishọn, Eza na Dishan. Ụmụ ndị ikom Sia nʼala Edọm, ha bụ ndị ọnụmara Hor.<verse eid="GEN 36:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 36:22"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Lotan bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:22">Hori na Homam. Timna bụkwa nwanne nwanyị Lotan.<verse eid="GEN 36:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 36:23"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Shobal bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:23">Alvan, Manahat, Ebal, Shefo na Onam.<verse eid="GEN 36:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 36:24"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Zibiọn mụrụ bụ</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:24">Aịa na Ana. Ana bụ nwoke ahụ chọpụtara isi iyi mmiri ime ala ahụ nke mmiri dị ọkụ si nʼime ya na-asọpụta nʼọzara, mgbe ọ na-elekọta ịnyịnya ibu nna ya Zibiọn.<verse eid="GEN 36:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 36:25"/>Ụmụ Ana bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:25">Dishọn na Oholibama nwa nwanyị Ana.<verse eid="GEN 36:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 36:26"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Dishọn bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:26">Hemdan na Eshban na Itran na Keran.<verse eid="GEN 36:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 36:27"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Eza bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:27">Bilhan na Zaavan na Akan.<verse eid="GEN 36:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 36:28"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Dishan bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:28">Uz na Aran.<verse eid="GEN 36:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 36:29"/>Ndị a bụ ndị ọnụmara Hor,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 36:29">ọnụmara Lotan, ọnụmara Shobal, ọnụmara Zibiọn, ọnụmara Ana, <verse eid="GEN 36:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 36:30"/>ọnụmara Dishọn, ọnụmara Eza na ọnụmara Dishan.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="GEN 36:30">Ndị a niile bụ ndị ọnụmara Hor dịka nkewa ha si dị nʼala Sia.<verse eid="GEN 36:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ndị eze Edọm</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 36:31"/>Ndị a bụ ndị eze chịrị nʼEdọm tupu ndị Izrel enwee eze mbụ ha.<verse eid="GEN 36:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 36:32"/>Bela, nwa Beoa chịrị dịka eze nʼEdọm. Isi obodo ya bụ Dinhaba.<verse eid="GEN 36:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 36:33"/>Mgbe Bela nwụrụ, Jobab nwa Zera onye Bozra nọchiri ya dịka eze.<verse eid="GEN 36:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 36:34"/>Mgbe Jobab nwụrụ, Husham onye si nʼala Teman nọchiri ya dịka eze.<verse eid="GEN 36:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 36:35"/>Mgbe Husham nwụrụ, Hadad nwa Bedad, onye meriri ndị Midia nʼagha nʼala Moab nọchiri dịka eze. Isi obodo ya bụ Avit.<verse eid="GEN 36:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 36:36"/>Mgbe Hadad nwụrụ, Samla onye Masrika nọchiri ya dịka eze.<verse eid="GEN 36:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 36:37"/>Mgbe Samla nwụrụ, Shaul onye sitere na Rehobọt dị nʼakụkụ osimiri nọchiri ya dịka eze.<verse eid="GEN 36:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 36:38"/>Mgbe Shaul nwụrụ, Baal-Hanan nwa Akboa nọchiri ya dịka eze.<verse eid="GEN 36:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 36:39"/>Mgbe Baal-Hanan nwa Akboa nwụrụ, Heda nọchiri ya dịka eze. Aha obodo ya bụ Pau. Aha nwunye ya bụ Mehetabel, nwa Matred nwa nwa Mezahab.<verse eid="GEN 36:39"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 36:40"/>Ndị a bụ ndịisi ọnụmara Ịsọ, dịka aha ha si dị, dịka ikwu ha na akụkụ ebe ha bi si dị:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 36:40">Timna, Alva, Jetet,<verse eid="GEN 36:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 36:41"/>Oholibama, Elaa, Pinon,<verse eid="GEN 36:41"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 36:42"/>Kenaz, Teman, Mibza,<verse eid="GEN 36:42"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 36:43"/>Magdiel na Iram.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="GEN 36:43">Ndị a bụ ndịisi ọnụmara nʼEdọm, dịka ebe obibi ha na ala obi ha si dị.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 36:43"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="GEN 36:43">Nke a bụ ezinaụlọ Ịsọ bụkwa nna ndị Edọm.<verse eid="GEN 36:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 36"/>
  <chapter number="37" style="c" sid="GEN 37"/>
  <para style="s1">Nrọ Josef</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 37:1"/>Jekọb bigidere nʼala Kenan, ala ahụ nna ya buru ụzọ biri nʼime ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 37:2"/>Nke a bụ usoro akụkọ banyere ezinaụlọ Jekọb.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 37:2"/>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 37:2">Josef, onye gbarala afọ iri na asaa, na-esonyere ụmụnne ya ndị ikom na-azụ igwe anụ ụlọ, ya onwe ya bụ naanị nwantakịrị na-enyere ụmụ Bilha na ụmụ Zilpa ndị nwunye nna ya aka. Ma Josef na-ewetara nna ha akụkọ maka ihe ọjọọ ha na-eme.<verse eid="GEN 37:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 37:3"/>Ma Izrel hụrụ Josef nʼanya karịa ụmụ ya ndị ikom ndị ọzọ niile nʼihi na Josef bụ nwa a mụụrụ ya nʼoge agadi ya. Ọ kwaara ya uwe mwụda nwere ọtụtụ agwa. <verse eid="GEN 37:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 37:4"/>Mgbe ụmụnne ya chọpụtara na nna ha hụrụ ya nʼanya karịa onye ọbụla nʼime ha, ha kpọrọ ya asị, ha adịghị agwakwa ya okwu ọma.<verse eid="GEN 37:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 37:5"/>Otu oge, Josef rọrọ nrọ, mgbe ọ kọọrọ ụmụnne ya nrọ a ọ rọrọ, ha kpọrọ ya asị karịa. <verse eid="GEN 37:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 37:6"/>Ọ gwara ha, “Geenụ ntị na nrọ a m rọrọ. <verse eid="GEN 37:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 37:7"/>Anyị niile nọ nʼubi na-achịkọta ọka, ngwangwa ukwu ọka nke m biliri guzoro ọtọ, ebe ukwu ọka nke unu niile gbara ukwu ọka nke m gburugburu, na-akpọ isiala nye ya.”<verse eid="GEN 37:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 37:8"/>Ụmụnne ya jụrụ ya, “Ị na-akọwa na ọ bụ gị ga-abụ eze anyị? Na ọ bụ gị nʼezie ga-achị anyị?” Ha kpọrọ ya asị karịa nʼihi nrọ ya na okwu ya niile.<verse eid="GEN 37:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 37:9"/>Josef rọkwara nrọ ọzọ, kọkwara ụmụnne ya. Ọ sịrị, “Geenụ ntị, arọrọ m nrọ ọzọ. Ma na nrọ nke ugbu a, anyanwụ na ọnwa na kpakpando iri na otu na-akpọ isiala nye m.”<verse eid="GEN 37:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 37:10"/>Ma mgbe ọ kọọrọ nna ya na ụmụnne ya nrọ a. Nna ya baara ya mba, sị, “Nrọ nke a ị rọrọ bụ nrọ gịnị? Ọ bụ ezie na anyị niile, mụ onwe m na nne gị na ụmụnne gị, ga-abịa na-akpọrọ gị isiala?” <verse eid="GEN 37:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 37:11"/>Ụmụnne ya kwosiri ya ekworo nʼihi ya, ma nna ya debere ihe ndị a niile nʼobi ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Orire e rere Josef</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 37:12"/>Ka ọ dị, ụmụnne ya gara ilekọta igwe anụ ụlọ nna ha na Shekem. <verse eid="GEN 37:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 37:13"/>Izrel sịrị Josef, “Dịka ị maara, ụmụnne gị nọ na-eche anụ ụlọ na Shekem. Bịa, aga m eziga gị nʼebe ahụ.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 37:13">Josef zara sị, “Ọ dị mma.”<verse eid="GEN 37:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 37:14"/>Ya mere, ọ gwara ya, “Gaa ka ị chọpụta ma ihe ọ na-agazikwara ụmụnne gị na igwe anụ ụlọ ndị ahụ nke ọma, ma weghachiri m ozi.” O sitere na Ndagwurugwu Hebrọn zipụ ya.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 37:14">Ọ bịaruru Shekem, <verse eid="GEN 37:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 37:15"/>ma otu nwoke hụrụ ya ka ọ na-awagharị gburugburu nʼọhịa dị nʼebe ahụ, ọ jụrụ ya, “Gịnị ka ị na-achọ?”<verse eid="GEN 37:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 37:16"/>Ọ sịrị, “Ana m achọ ụmụnne m. Biko, ị nwere ike ịgwa m ebe ha nọ na-azụ igwe anụ ụlọ ha?”<verse eid="GEN 37:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 37:17"/>Nwoke ahụ zara sị, “Ha esitela nʼebe a pụọ. Anụrụ m ka ha na-asị, ‘Ka anyị gaa Dọtan.’ ”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 37:17">Ya mere, Josef gawara Dọtan ịchọ ụmụnne ya. Ọ hụkwara ha nʼebe dị nso na Dọtan. <verse eid="GEN 37:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 37:18"/>Ma ha lepụrụ anya hụ ya ka ọ na-abịa, gbaa izu otu ha ga-esi gbuo ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 37:19"/>Ha sịrịtara onwe ha, “Lee eze nrọ ahụ ka ọ na-abịa! <verse eid="GEN 37:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 37:20"/>Ugbu a, bịanụ, ka anyị gbuo ya, tụba ya nʼime otu olulu ndị a.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">37:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ebe ala ala olulu mmiri ndị a na-agbasa agbasa karịa ọnụ ha. <char style="xt"><ref loc="JER 38:6">Jer 38:6</ref>,<ref loc="JER 38:13">13</ref></char></char></note> Anyị ga-asịkwa na anụ ọhịa eriela ya. Mgbe ahụ, anyị ga-ahụkwa ihe nrọ ya niile ga-abụ.”<verse eid="GEN 37:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 37:21"/>Ruben nụrụ ihe a, ma napụtakwa ya site nʼaka ha. Ọ sịrị, “Ka anyị hapụ igbu ya.” <verse eid="GEN 37:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 37:22"/>Ruben sịrị ha, “Ka unu hapụ ịkwafu ọbara. Kama tụnyenụ ya nʼime olulu a dị nʼọzara. Ma unu akpatụkwala ya aka.” Ma nzube ya bụ ịnapụta ya site nʼaka ha, dulaara ya nna ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 37:23"/>Ya mere, mgbe Josef bịakwutere ụmụnne ya, ha yipụrụ ya uwe mwụda ya, uwe mwụda nwere ọtụtụ agwa o yi nʼahụ. <verse eid="GEN 37:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 37:24"/>Ha duru ya tụnye ya nʼime olulu. Ọ bụ olulu tọgbọrọ nʼefu, nke mmiri na-adịghị nʼime ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 37:25"/>Mgbe ha nọdụrụ ala bido iri nri, ha leliri anya ha hụ igwe ndị ahịa Ishmel si Gilead. Ịnyịnya kamel ha bu ụda na mgbaa na máá. Ọ bụkwa Ijipt ka ha bu ihe ndị a na-aga.<verse eid="GEN 37:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 37:26"/>Mgbe ahụ, Juda jụrụ ụmụnne ya, “Uru gịnị ka ọ ga-abara anyị igbu nwanne anyị, ma kpuchie ọbara ya? <verse eid="GEN 37:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 37:27"/>Bịanụ, ka anyị resi ya ndị Ishmel ndị a, ka aka anyị ghara nʼimetụ ya, nʼihi na nwanne anyị na otu anụ ahụ anyị ka ọ bụ.” Ụmụnne ya gere ya ntị.<verse eid="GEN 37:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 37:28"/>Mgbe ndị ahịa Midia ahụ rutere, ha sitere nʼolulu dọpụta Josef resi ya ndị Ishmel ahụ, ndị kwụrụ ụmụnne Josef iri mkpụrụ shekel ọlaọcha abụọ. Ha duuru Josef gaa Ijipt.<verse eid="GEN 37:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 37:29"/>Ruben mechara lọghachi gaa nʼolulu ahụ, ma ka ọ na-ahụghị Josef nʼime olulu a, ọ dọwara uwe ya. <verse eid="GEN 37:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 37:30"/>O jekwuru ụmụnne ya sị ha, “Nwata ahụ anọkwaghị ebe ahụ! Mụ onwe m, olee ebe m ga-ala?”<verse eid="GEN 37:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 37:31"/>Ụmụnne ya gburu otu ewu were uwe Josef bịanye nʼime ọbara ya. <verse eid="GEN 37:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 37:32"/>Ha chịịrị uwe mwụda ahụ nwere ọtụtụ agwa jekwuru nna ha sị ya, “Anyị hụrụ uwe a nʼime ọhịa. Leruo ya anya ka ị mara maọbụ uwe mwụda nwa gị.”<verse eid="GEN 37:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 37:33"/>Ọ matara na ọ bụ ya, sị, “E, nke a bụ uwe nwa m nwoke. Ajọ anụ eriela ya. Anụ ọhịa adọkasịala Josef nʼezie.”<verse eid="GEN 37:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 37:34"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb dọwara uwe ya, yiri akwa mkpe, ruo ụjụ ọtụtụ ụbọchị nʼihi nwa ya. <verse eid="GEN 37:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 37:35"/>Ụmụ ya ndị ikom na ụmụ ya ndị inyom niile bịara ịkasị ya obi, ma ọ jụrụ ịnabata nkasiobi ọbụla. Ọ sịrị, “Aga m alakwuru nwa m nʼala mmụọ site nʼiru ụjụ.” Nna ya kwagidere akwa nʼihi ya.<verse eid="GEN 37:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 37:36"/>Ugbu a, ndị Midia ahụ rere<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">37:36 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ire maọbụ ịzụta mmadụ dịka ohu bụ otu nʼime ahịa ndị bi nʼọzara na-azụ. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 17:12">Jen 17:12</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 37:26">37:26</ref></char></char></note> Josef nʼIjipt, resi ya Pọtifa, otu nʼime ndịisi na-ejere Fero ozi, onye bụ onyeisi ndị nche Fero, bụ eze Ijipt.<verse eid="GEN 37:36"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 37"/>
  <chapter number="38" style="c" sid="GEN 38"/>
  <para style="s1">Juda na Tama</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 38:1"/>Nʼoge ahụ, Juda hapụrụ ụmụnne ya gaa binyere otu nwoke onye Adulam a na-akpọ Hira. <verse eid="GEN 38:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 38:2"/>Nʼebe ahụ, Juda hụrụ otu nwaagbọghọ, nwa otu nwoke onye Kenan, aha ya bụ Shua. Ọ lụrụ ya ma bakwuru ya. <verse eid="GEN 38:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 38:3"/>Ọ tụụrụ ime mụọ nwa nwoke, onye Juda gụrụ aha Ịa <verse eid="GEN 38:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 38:4"/>Nwunye ya dịkwara ime ọzọ mụta nwa nwoke nke ya bụ nwunye ya gụrụ Onan. <verse eid="GEN 38:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 38:5"/>Ọ mụkwara nwa nwoke ọzọ, onye ọ kpọrọ Shela. Ọ bụ na Kezib ka ọ mụrụ ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 38:6"/>Juda lụtaara Ịa, ọkpara ya, nwunye onye aha ya bụ Tama. <verse eid="GEN 38:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 38:7"/>Ma nʼihi na Ịa, ọkpara Juda, dị njọ nʼanya <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gburu ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 38:8"/>Mgbe ahụ, Juda sịrị Onan, “Bakwuru nwunye nwanne gị ka ịkuchie ya, ka i si otu a wulite mkpụrụ maka nwanne gị.” <verse eid="GEN 38:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 38:9"/>Onan ma na mkpụrụ a agaghị abụ nke ya. Nʼihi ya, mgbe ọbụla ọ bakwuru nwunye nwanne ya, ọ na-anyụsa mkpụrụ nwa ya nʼala, ime ka ọ ghara inye nwanne ya nwoke nwa. <verse eid="GEN 38:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 38:10"/>Ma ihe a o mere jọrọ njọ nʼanya <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>. Nʼihi ya <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gbukwara ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 38:11"/>Juda sịrị nwunye nwa ya, bụ Tama, “Laa nʼụlọ nna gị nọrọ dịka nwanyị di ya nwụrụ tutu Shela nwa m nwoke etoo.” Ma echiche ya bụ, “ka ọ ghara ịnwụ dịka ụmụnne ya.” Tama lara gaa biri nʼụlọ nna ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 38:12"/>Mgbe ọtụtụ oge gasịrị, nwunye Juda nwa Shua nwụrụ. Mgbe oge nkasiobi ya gasịrị, Juda jere Timna, ya na enyi ya Hira, onye Adulam, ilekọta ndị na-akpụchapụ igwe ewu na atụrụ ya ajị.<verse eid="GEN 38:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 38:13"/>A gwara Tama sị ya, “Nna di gị na-aga Timna ịkpacha atụrụ ya ajị.” <verse eid="GEN 38:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 38:14"/>O yipụrụ uwe mkpe ya, were akwa mkpuchi kpuchie onwe ya gaa nọdụ ala nʼọnụ ụzọ ama Enayim, nke dị nʼụzọ e si aga Timna. O mere otu a nʼihi na ọ matara na Shela etoola, ma enyeghị ya ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 38:15"/>Mgbe Juda hụrụ ya, o chere na ọ bụ otu nwanyị akwụna, ebe ọ bụ na o kpuchiri ihu ya. <verse eid="GEN 38:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 38:16"/>Ma ebe ọ mataghị na ọ bụ nwunye nwa ya, o jekwuru ya ebe ọ nọdụrụ ala nʼakụkụ ụzọ sị ya, “Bịa, kwere ka mụ na gị dinaa.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 38:16">Tama jụrụ, “Gịnị ka ị ga-enye m ma ọ bụrụ na m kwere ka mụ na gị dinaa?”<verse eid="GEN 38:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 38:17"/>Ọ zara, “Aga m ezitere gị otu nwa ewu site nʼigwe ewu na atụrụ m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 38:17">Ọ jụrụ, “Ị ga-enye m ihe akaebe ruo mgbe ị ga-ezite ya?”<verse eid="GEN 38:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 38:18"/>Ọ sịrị, “Kedụ ihe akaebe m ga-enye gị?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 38:18">Ọ zara, “Mgbaaka akara gị na eriri ya, na mkpanaka dị gị nʼaka.” O nyere ya ihe ndị a. Ọ bakwuru ya nke mere na ọ tụụrụ ime. <verse eid="GEN 38:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 38:19"/>Mgbe o si nʼebe ahụ pụọ, o yipụrụ akwa ahụ o ji kpuchie ihu ya, yirikwa uwe mkpe ya.<verse eid="GEN 38:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 38:20"/>Mgbe Juda zigara enyi ya onye Adulam ka ọ gaa wegara ya nwa ewu ahụ, ma nataghachi ihe ibe ahụ, ọ hụghị ya. <verse eid="GEN 38:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 38:21"/>Ọ jụrụ ndị ikom bi nʼebe ahụ sị, “Olee nwanyị akwụna ụlọ arụsị ahụ na-anọdụ nʼọnụ ụzọ ama Enayim?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 38:21">Ha sịrị, “O nweghị nwanyị akwụna ụlọ arụsị nọrọla nʼebe a.”<verse eid="GEN 38:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 38:22"/>Ya mere, ọ laghachiri gaa gwa Juda, “Ahụghị m ya. Ọzọkwa, ndị ikom ndị bi nʼebe ahụ sịrị, ‘O nweghị nwanyị akwụna<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">38:22 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nʼoge ochie, ụmụ nwanyị akwụna bụ ndị na-efe chi ndị ha na-ewe ka chi ọmụmụ. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 38:21">Jen 38:21</ref></char></char></note> ụlọ arụsị nọrọla nʼebe a.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 38:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 38:23"/>Juda zara, “Ka o jide ihe niile o ji, ma ọ bụghị otu a anyị ga-aghọ ihe ọchị. Lee, ezigarala m ya nwa ewu a, ma gị onwe gị achọtaghị ya.”<verse eid="GEN 38:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 38:24"/>Mgbe ọnwa atọ gasịrị, ozi ruru Juda ntị sị, “Tama nwunye nwa gị gbara akwụna, bịa site nʼịgba akwụna dịrị ime.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 38:24">Juda sịrị, “Kpọpụtanụ ya ka akpọọ ya ọkụ.”<verse eid="GEN 38:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 38:25"/>Ma mgbe ha kpọ ya na-apụta, o zigara nna di ya ozi, sị, “Ọ bụ nwoke nwee ihe ndị a tụwara m ime. Ọ sịkwara, Leruo anya ma ị ga-amata onye nwe ihe ndị a: mgbaaka akara a na eriri ya, na mkpanaka a.”<verse eid="GEN 38:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 38:26"/>Juda ghọtara ha, sị, “Ọ bụ onye ezi omume karịa m, ebe ọ bụ na m jụrụ ịkpọrọ ya kpọnye nwa m nwoke Shela ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya.” O dinakwaghị ya ọzọ.<verse eid="GEN 38:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 38:27"/>Mgbe oge ọmụmụ nwa ya ruru, ejima ka ahụrụ nʼakpanwa ya. <verse eid="GEN 38:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 38:28"/>Mgbe ọ na-amụ ha, otu nʼime ha sepụtara aka ya. Nwanyị na-aghọ nwa weere eriri na-acha uhie uhie kee ya na nkwoji aka kwuo sị, “Ọ bụ nke a bụ ụzọ pụta.” <verse eid="GEN 38:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 38:29"/>Ma nwa ahụ mesịrị sekpuo aka ya, nwanne ya nke ọzọ eburu ya ụzọ pụta. Nwanyị ahụ sịrị, “Ọ bụ otu a ka ị si tikapụta?” A kpọrọ ya Perez.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">38:29 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Perez bụ nna ochie Devid. <char style="xt"><ref loc="RUT 4:18-22">Rut 4:18-22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 1:3-6">Mat 1:3-6</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 3:32-33">Luk 3:32-33</ref></char></char></note> <verse eid="GEN 38:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 38:30"/>Emesịa, nwanne ya, nke bu eriri uhie uhie ahụ na nkwoji aka pụtakwara. A kpọrọ ya Zera.<verse eid="GEN 38:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 38"/>
  <chapter number="39" style="c" sid="GEN 39"/>
  <para style="s1">Josef na nwunye Pọtifa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 39:1"/>A kpọọrọ Josef gaa nʼala Ijipt. Pọtifa, bụ nwoke Ijipt, otu nʼime ndịisi na-ejere Fero ozi, na onyeisi ndị agha na-eche nche zụụrụ ya site nʼaka ndị Ishmel, bụ ndị duuru ya gaa nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 39:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 39:2"/>
    <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọnyeere Josef, nke mere na ihe gaara ya nke ọma nʼụlọ nna ya ukwu onye Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 39:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 39:3"/>Nna ya ukwu hụrụ na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọnyeere Josef, hụkwa na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> na-eme ka ihe niile o mere gaara ya nke ọma. <verse eid="GEN 39:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 39:4"/>Josef hụtara amara nʼihu ya, ghọọ onyeozi nke aka ya. Pọtifa mere ya onye na-elekọta ezinaụlọ ya. Nyefee ya ihe niile o nwere ka ọ bụrụ onye na-elekọta ha. <verse eid="GEN 39:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 39:5"/>Site nʼoge a, o mere ka ọ bụrụ onye na-elekọta ezinaụlọ ya na ihe niile o nwere, <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> gọziri ezinaụlọ onye Ijipt ahụ nʼihi Josef. Ngọzị <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> dịkwasịrị nʼihe niile Pọtifa nwere, ma ihe o nwere nʼụlọ ma ndị o nwere nʼubi ya. <verse eid="GEN 39:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 39:6"/>Ya mere, ọ hapụrụ ihe niile o nwere nʼaka Josef. Nke a mere na ọ mazighị ihe ọzọ na-eme, ma ọ bụghị nri nke ọ na-eri.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">39:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Usoro iri nri ndị Ijipt dị iche site na nke ndị Juu, nʼihi ụzọ esi akwado ha tupu e rie ha. <char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 43:32">Jen 43:32</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 39:6">Josef nʼonwe ya mara mma ahụ dịkwa mma ile anya. <verse eid="GEN 39:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 39:7"/>Mgbe oge nta gasịrị, nwunye Pọtifa lere Josef anya sị ya, “Bịa ka anyị abụọ dinaa.”<verse eid="GEN 39:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 39:8"/>Ma Josef jụrụ. Ọ gwara nwunye nna ya ukwu sị, “Lee, nna m ukwu anaghị echegbu onwe ya banyere ihe ọbụla nʼụlọ a. O werela ihe niile o nwere nyefee m nʼaka ka m lekọta ha anya. <verse eid="GEN 39:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 39:9"/>O nweghị onye ọnọdụ ya dị elu karịa nke m nʼụlọ a. O gbochighị m ihe ọbụla ma ọ bụghị gị, nʼihi na ị bụ nwunye ya. Olee otu m ga-esi mee oke ihe ọjọọ dị otu a, mee mmehie megide Chineke.” <verse eid="GEN 39:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 39:10"/>Ọ bụ ezie na nwanyị a nọgidere na-enye Josef nsogbu site nʼụbọchị ruo ụbọchị ma Josef jụrụ iso ya dinaa, jụkwa ịnọnyere ya.<verse eid="GEN 39:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 39:11"/>Otu ụbọchị, Josef batara nʼime ụlọ ịrụ ọrụ ya. O nweghị ndị ọzọ na-eje ozi nọ nʼime ụlọ nʼụbọchị ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 39:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 39:12"/>Nwunye Pọtifa jidere Josef nʼuwe mwụda ya, rịọọ ya sị ya, “Bịa ka anyị dinaa.” Ma Josef si nʼime ụlọ ahụ gbapụ, hapụ uwe mwụda ya nʼaka nwunye Pọtifa.<verse eid="GEN 39:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 39:13"/>Mgbe nwanyị a hụrụ na Josef agbapụla, hapụ uwe ya, <verse eid="GEN 39:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 39:14"/>ọ kpọrọ ndị na-eje ozi nʼezinaụlọ ya sị ha, “Lee, onye Hibru a di m kpọbatara nʼụlọ a chọrọ iji anyị gwurie egwu. Ọ bịakwutere m nʼime ụlọ chọọ ka mụ na ya dinaa. E tiri m mkpu nʼolu ike. <verse eid="GEN 39:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 39:15"/>Mgbe ọ nụrụ ka m welitere olu m tie mkpu enyemaka m tiri, o sitere nʼime ụlọ a gbapụ, ma hapụrụ m uwe ya.”<verse eid="GEN 39:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 39:16"/>Nwanyị a debere uwe ahụ nʼakụkụ ya ruo mgbe nna ya ukwu lọtara nʼụlọ. <verse eid="GEN 39:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 39:17"/>Mgbe ahụ, ọ gwara di ya okwu ndị a sị, “Onye ohu Hibru a ị kpọbataara anyị bakwutere m iji m gwurie egwu. <verse eid="GEN 39:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 39:18"/>Ma mgbe m welitere olu tie mkpu enyemaka o sitere nʼụlọ gbapụ hapụrụ m uwe ya.”<verse eid="GEN 39:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 39:19"/>Mgbe nna ya ukwu nụrụ ihe nwunye ya gwara ya sị, “Otu a ka ohu gị si meso m mmeso,” o were iwe dị ọkụ. <verse eid="GEN 39:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 39:20"/>Nna ukwu Josef weere ya tụnye nʼụlọ mkpọrọ, nʼebe a na-etinye ndị mkpọrọ eze Ijipt.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 39:20">Ma ebe ahụ Josef nọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ, <verse eid="GEN 39:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 39:21"/><char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọnyeere ya. O meere ya ebere, mekwa ka o nweta ihuọma nʼebe onyeisi ndị nche ụlọ mkpọrọ ahụ nọ. <verse eid="GEN 39:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 39:22"/>Onyeisi ndị na-eche ụlọ mkpọrọ mere Josef onyeisi ndị mkpọrọ niile nọ nʼime ụlọ mkpọrọ ahụ. Josef ghọrọ onye a na-ajụ otu ihe si aga nʼime ụlọ mkpọrọ ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 39:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 39:23"/>Onyeisi ndị nche ụlọ mkpọrọ ahụ enyeghịkwa onwe ya nsogbu maka ihe ọbụla. Nʼihi na <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char> nọnyeere Josef, mee ka ihe ọbụla ọ na-eme gaa nke ọma.<verse eid="GEN 39:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 39"/>
  <chapter number="40" style="c" sid="GEN 40"/>
  <para style="s1">Josef akọwaa nrọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 40:1"/>Mgbe ụfọdụ oge gasịrị, onye na-ebu iko ihe ọṅụṅụ eze Ijipt na onye na-esiri ya nri mehiere megide nna ha ukwu, eze Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 40:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 40:2"/>Nʼihi ya, Fero were iwe megide ndị ozi ya abụọ ndị a, onyeisi ndị na-ebu iko ya na onye na-esiri ya nri. <verse eid="GEN 40:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 40:3"/>O tinyere ha na nga, nʼụlọ mkpọrọ dị nʼụlọ onyeisi ndị nche, ebe ahụ a tụbara Josef. <verse eid="GEN 40:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 40:4"/>Onyeisi ndị nche mere Josef onye na-elekọta ha.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 40:4">Ha nọrọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ ọtụtụ ụbọchị. <verse eid="GEN 40:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 40:5"/>Ha abụọ, onye ahụ na-esiri eze nri, na onye na-ebu iko eze Ijipt, rọrọ nrọ nʼotu abalị. Nrọ nke onye ọ bụla nwere nkọwa nke ya.<verse eid="GEN 40:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 40:6"/>Mgbe chi bọrọ, Josef bịakwutere ha hụ na ihu ha gbarụrụ agbarụ. <verse eid="GEN 40:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 40:7"/>Nʼihi ya, ọ jụrụ ndị ozi Fero ndị a ha na ya nọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ dị nʼụlọ nna ya ukwu sị ha, “Gịnị mere ihu unu ji gbarụọ taa?”<verse eid="GEN 40:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 40:8"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Anyị rọrọ nrọ ọjọọ, ma onye nkọwa ya adịghị.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 40:8">Josef sịrị ha, “Ọ bụghị Chineke nwee ike ịkọwa nrọ? Kọọrọnụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">40:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Unu zere m nrọ unu</char></note> m ha.”<verse eid="GEN 40:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 40:9"/>Onyeisi ndị na-ebu iko kọọrọ Josef nrọ ya. Ọ sịrị ya, “Arọrọ m nrọ hụ osisi vaịnị nʼihu m. <verse eid="GEN 40:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 40:10"/>Osisi vaịnị a nwere alaka atọ. Mgbe m nọ na-ele anya, osisi vaịnị ahụ mara ifuru, mịpụta mkpụrụ nʼụyọkọ nʼụyọkọ, ha chakwaa. <verse eid="GEN 40:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 40:11"/>Ebe ọ bụ nʼiko Fero dị m nʼaka, a ghọọrọ m mkpụrụ vaịnị ndị a, pịpụta mmiri ha pịnye nʼime iko mmanya Fero, bunye ya ka ọ ṅụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 40:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 40:12"/>Josef sịrị ya, “Nke a bụ ihe nrọ gị pụtara. Alaka atọ ahụ bụ abalị atọ. <verse eid="GEN 40:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 40:13"/>Nʼime abalị atọ Fero ga-akpọpụta gị, mee ka i nwere onwe gị. Fero ga-enyeghachikwa gị ọrụ gị. Ị ga-etinyekwa Fero iko ya nʼaka dịka i si eme na mbụ mgbe ị bụ onye na-ebu iko ya. <verse eid="GEN 40:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 40:14"/>Mgbe ihe gaara gị nke ọma, chetakwa m, ma gosi m obiọma, gwara m Fero ka o si nʼụlọ mkpọrọ a wepụta m. <verse eid="GEN 40:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 40:15"/>Ọ bụ ntọrọ ka atọọrọ m site nʼala ndị Hibru. Nʼotu aka ahụ, nʼebe a ọ dịkwaghị ihe ọjọọ ọ bụla m mere nke kwesiri ka atụnye m nʼụlọ mkpọrọ a.”<verse eid="GEN 40:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 40:16"/>Mgbe onyeisi ndị na-esiri Fero nri hụrụ na nkọwa nrọ ahụ dị mma, ọ sịrị Josef, “Mụ onwe m, na nrọ m nke m, ebu m nkata achịcha atọ nʼisi. <verse eid="GEN 40:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 40:17"/>Nkata nke dị nʼelu jupụtara na achịcha dị iche iche e gheere eze, bụ Fero. Ma ụmụ nnụnụ bịara na-eri achịcha ndị ahụ dị na nkata m bụ nʼisi.”<verse eid="GEN 40:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 40:18"/>Josef zara sị ya, “Lee ihe nrọ gị pụtara. Nkata atọ ahụ bụ abalị atọ. <verse eid="GEN 40:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 40:19"/>Nʼime abalị atọ ka Fero ga-esi nʼụlọ mkpọrọ kpọpụta gị, nye iwu ka e bepụ gị isi, kwụba gị nʼelu osisi. Ụmụ nnụnụ ga-erichapụ anụ ahụ gị.”<verse eid="GEN 40:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 40:20"/>Nʼabalị nke atọ, site nʼụbọchị ndị a rọrọ nrọ ha, Fero mere mmemme ncheta ọmụmụ ya. Ọ kpọrọ ndị niile na-ejere ya ozi oriri. O ziri ozi ka a gaa nʼụlọ mkpọrọ kpọpụta onyeisi ndị na-ebunye ya iko ihe ọṅụṅụ na onyeisi ndị na-esiri ya nri. <verse eid="GEN 40:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 40:21"/>O nyeghachiri onyeisi ndị na-ebu iko ya ọrụ ya, weghachi ya nʼọnọdụ ya. Nwoke a bunyekwara Fero iko ya dịka o si eme na mbụ. <verse eid="GEN 40:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 40:22"/>Ma ọ kwụgburu onyeisi ndị na-esiri ya nri, dịka Josef si kọwaa nrọ ha.<verse eid="GEN 40:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 40:23"/>Ma onyeisi ndị ahụ na-ebu iko eze echetaghị Josef. O chefuru ya.<verse eid="GEN 40:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 40"/>
  <chapter number="41" style="c" sid="GEN 41"/>
  <para style="s1">Nrọ Fero na nkọwa ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 41:1"/>O ruo mgbe afọ abụọ gasịrị, Fero rọrọ nrọ hụ onwe ya ka o guzo nʼakụkụ mmiri Naịl. <verse eid="GEN 41:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 41:2"/>Nʼebe ahụ, ọ hụrụ ehi asaa ndị si nʼosimiri Naịl na-apụta. Ehi ndị a buru ibu, maa mma. Ahụ ha na-akwọ mụrụmụrụ. Ha pụtara, bido ịta nri nʼetiti ahịhịa riidi. <verse eid="GEN 41:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 41:3"/>Nʼatụfughị oge, ehi asaa ọzọ soro ha nʼazụ sikwa nʼosimiri Naịl na-apụta. Ma ehi ndị a tara ahụ nke ukwuu. Ha bụ nnọọ ọkpụkpụ ọkpụkpụ, jọọ njọ ile anya. Ha bịara guzo nʼakụkụ ehi ndị ahụ buru ibu. <verse eid="GEN 41:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 41:4"/>Mgbe ahụ, ehi ndị a bụ naanị ọkpụkpụ ọkpụkpụ bịara richapụ ehi ndị ahụ buru ibu. Mgbe nke a mere Fero kwolitere.<verse eid="GEN 41:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 41:5"/>Emesịa, Fero rahụkwara ụra ọzọ, rọọ nrọ nke ugboro abụọ, hụ ogbe ọka asaa ndị mịrị nʼotu ukwu ọka. Ogbe ọka ndị a buru ibu maa ezi mma. <verse eid="GEN 41:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 41:6"/>Emesịa, ọ hụkwara ogbe ọka asaa ọzọ ka ha mịkwara nʼotu ukwu ọka ahụ. Ma ndị a ọ hụrụ kpọnwụsịrị akpọnwụ, fịkpọkwa afịkpọ. Ọ bụ ikuku si nʼọwụwa anyanwụ mere ka ha kpọnwụọ. <verse eid="GEN 41:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 41:7"/>Ogbe ọka ndị a fịkpọrọ afịkpọ loro ogbe ọka asaa ndị ahụ buru ibu. Fero kwolitere hụ na ihe ndị a bụ nrọ.<verse eid="GEN 41:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 41:8"/>Mgbe chi bọrọ, o nweghị udo na mmụọ ya. O ziri ozi kpọkọta ndị majiki niile, na ndị ọkachamara niile nke Ijipt. Fero kọọrọ ha ihe ọ rọrọ na nrọ. Ma ọ dịghị onye nwere ike ịkọwara ya ihe nrọ ya pụtara.<verse eid="GEN 41:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 41:9"/>Ma nʼoge ahụ, onyeisi ndị na-ebu iko jekwuuru Fero gwa ya sị, “Taa ka m chetara mmehie m. <verse eid="GEN 41:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 41:10"/>Oge ahụ Fero were iwe megide ndị na-ejere ya ozi, o tinyere mụ na onyeisi ndị na-esi nri nʼụlọ mkpọrọ nke dị nʼebe onyeisi ndị nche eze bi. <verse eid="GEN 41:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 41:11"/>Onye ọbụla nʼime anyị abụọ rọrọ nrọ nʼotu abalị, nrọ ọbụla nwekwara nkọwa nke ya. <verse eid="GEN 41:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 41:12"/>O nwere nwokorobịa onye Hibru anyị na ya nọ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ nʼoge ahụ. Ọ bụ ohu onyeisi ndị nche eze. Anyị kọọrọ ya nrọ anyị rọrọ. Ọ kọwakwaara anyị ihe nrọ anyị pụtara nye onye ọbụla nkọwa nke nrọ ya. <verse eid="GEN 41:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 41:13"/>Ihe niile mere dịka o si kọwara anyị. E nyeghachiri m ọnọdụ m, ma kwụba onye nke ọzọ nʼosisi.”<verse eid="GEN 41:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 41:14"/>Ya mere Fero ziri ozi ka a kpọọ Josef. E mere ngwangwa wepụta ya site nʼụlọ mkpọrọ ahụ. Mgbe ọ kpụchara afụọnụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Otu ihe e ji maara ndị Ijipt bụ ịkpụcha agịrị isi na afụọnụ ha, ma nke a bụghị omenaala ndị Juu.</char></note> ya, gbanwee uwe ya, ọ bịakwara nʼihu Fero.<verse eid="GEN 41:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 41:15"/>Fero gwara Josef sị, “Arọrọ m nrọ ma o nweghị onye ọbụla nwere ike ịkọwara m ihe nrọ m rọrọ pụtara. Ma anụla m na a kọọrọ gị nrọ a rọrọ, i nwere ike ịkọwa ihe nrọ ahụ pụtara.”<verse eid="GEN 41:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 41:16"/>Josef zara sị ya, “Enweghị m ike ịkọwa nrọ nʼike aka m. Ma Chineke ga-enye Fero ọsịsa udo dịka ọ chọrọ.”<verse eid="GEN 41:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 41:17"/>Mgbe ahụ, Fero malitere ịkọwara Josef nrọ ya. O kwuru sị, “Eguzoro m nʼakụkụ osimiri Naịl na nrọ m. <verse eid="GEN 41:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 41:18"/>Mgbe ahụ, ahụrụ m ehi asaa si na mmiri ahụ pụta. Ehi ndị a mara abụba, ma gbaa agba. Ha bidokwara ịta nri nʼetiti ahịhịa riidi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:18 </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Ahịhịa riidi </char><char style="ft" closed="false">bụ ahịhịa na-epu nʼakụkụ osimiri Naịl</char></note> <verse eid="GEN 41:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 41:19"/>Emesịa, a hụrụ m ehi asaa ọzọ ka ha sikwa nʼosimiri ahụ pụta. Ehi ndị a ejighị ahụ. Ha bụ ọkpụkpụ ọkpụkpụ, jọọ njọ ile anya. Nʼezie, ahụtụbeghị m ụdị ehi dị otu a nʼala Ijipt niile. <verse eid="GEN 41:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 41:20"/>Ehi asaa ndị a jọrọ njọ riri ehi ndị ahụ buru ibu, bụ ndị bu ha ụzọ si nʼosimiri ahụ pụta. <verse eid="GEN 41:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 41:21"/>Ma mgbe ha risiri ehi ndị a, nri ahụ emeghị ka ụdịdị ha gbanwee. Ha dịkwa otu ha dị. Mgbe m hụsịrị ihe a, etetara m nʼụra.<verse eid="GEN 41:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 41:22"/>“Mgbe m rọrọ nrọ ọzọ, a hụrụ m ogbe ọka asaa nke mịrị nʼotu ukwu ọka. Ọka asaa ndị a buru ibu, dị mma ile anya. <verse eid="GEN 41:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 41:23"/>Ogbe ọka asaa ọzọ mịkwara nʼelu ukwu ọka ahụ, ma ndị a kpọnwụrụ akpọnwụ, fịkpọkwa afịkpọ nʼihi nʼikuku si nʼọwụwa anyanwụ chakpọrọ ha. <verse eid="GEN 41:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 41:24"/>Ma ọka ndị a fịkpọrọ afịkpọ lodara ọka asaa ndị ahụ mara mma. Akọọlara m ndị majiki ihe ndị a, ma ọ dịghị onye nʼime ha nwere ike ịkọwara m ihe nrọ ndị a pụtara.”<verse eid="GEN 41:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 41:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef sịrị Fero, “Nrọ abụọ Fero rọrọ pụtara otu ihe. Chineke esitela na nrọ ndị a gwa Fero ihe ọ na-aga ime. <verse eid="GEN 41:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 41:26"/>Ehi asaa ndị ahụ buru ibu bụ afọ asaa. Ogbe ọka asaa ndị ahụ buru ibu bụkwa afọ asaa. Ọ bụ otu nrọ ahụ, ọ bụ ezie na ị rọrọ ya ugboro abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 41:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 41:27"/>Ehi asaa ndị ọzọ ahụ dị ọkpụkpụ ọkpụkpụ ndị pụtara mgbe ndị nke mbụ pụtachara bụ afọ asaa. Otu a kwa ogbe ọka ndị ọzọ fịkpọrọ afịkpọ nke ikuku si nʼọwụwa anyanwụ mere ka ha fịkpọọ bụ afọ asaa. Ha na-egosi afọ asaa mgbe oke ụnwụ ga-adị.<verse eid="GEN 41:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 41:28"/>“Dịka m gwara Fero na mbụ, Chineke egosila gị ihe ọ chọrọ ime. <verse eid="GEN 41:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 41:29"/>Afọ asaa na-abịa ga-abụ afọ asaa mgbe nri ga-adị ukwuu nʼala Ijipt niile. <verse eid="GEN 41:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 41:30"/>Emesịa afọ asaa oke ụnwụ ga-eso ha. Mgbe ahụ, a ga-echefu ụba niile nke ala Ijipt. Ụnwụ a ga-ala obodo nʼiyi. <verse eid="GEN 41:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 41:31"/>Agaghị echetakwa na e nwere oge ịba ụba ihe oriri nʼala a, nʼihi oke ụnwụ ahụ nke ga-eso ya ga-adị oke ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 41:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 41:32"/>Ihe mere Fero ji rọọ nrọ a ugboro abụọ bụ nʼihi na Chineke ekpebiela na ihe ndị a ga-emezuriri. Chineke ga-emekwa ya nʼoge na-adịghị anya.<verse eid="GEN 41:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 41:33"/>“Ma ugbu a, ka Fero chọọ onye nwere ezi nghọta na amamihe. Ya mee ya onyeisi ọchịchị nʼala Ijipt niile. <verse eid="GEN 41:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 41:34"/>Ka Fero mee nhọpụta ndị nlekọta ala Ijipt. Ka e debe otu ụzọ nʼime ụzọ ise nke nri niile a ga-enweta nʼoge ahụ nri ga-adị ukwuu nʼala Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 41:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 41:35"/>Ka ha kpokọtaa nri niile ga-adị nʼoge ịba ụba nke ihe oriri, nke ga-adị nʼafọ ndị a na-abịa. Ka ha kpokọta ha nʼụlọ ichebe nri nke ga-adị nʼokpuru ọchịchị Fero. Ka ọ bụrụ nri e debere nʼobodo dị iche iche. <verse eid="GEN 41:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 41:36"/>A ga-echebe nri ndị a nke ọma maka ndị bi nʼala a, ka ọ bụrụ nri a ga-eri nʼime afọ asaa ndị ahụ nke ụnwụ ga-adị nʼala Ijipt, ka ụnwụ ghara ibibi ala a.”<verse eid="GEN 41:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 41:37"/>Ntụpụta ahụ dị mma nʼanya Fero na ndịisi ọchịchị ya. <verse eid="GEN 41:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 41:38"/>Fero jụrụ ndịisi ọchịchị ya, “Anyị ga-achọtali onye ọzọ dịka nwoke a, onye mmụọ nke Chineke dị nʼime ya?”<verse eid="GEN 41:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="GEN 41:39"/>Ya mere Fero tụgharịrị sị Josef, “Ebe Chineke kpugheere gị ihe ndị a, o nweghị onye ọzọ nwere ezi nghọta na amamihe dịka gị. <verse eid="GEN 41:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="GEN 41:40"/>Gị onwe gị ga-abụ onye na-elekọta ụlọeze m. Ndị m niile ga-erube isi nʼiwu ọbụla i nyere. Ọ bụ naanị nʼocheeze ka m ga-eji dị ukwuu karịa gị.”<verse eid="GEN 41:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Josef aghọọ onye na-achị Ijipt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="GEN 41:41"/>Fero gwara Josef, “Lee, emeela m gị onye nlekọta ala Ijipt niile.” <verse eid="GEN 41:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="GEN 41:42"/>Mgbe ahụ, Fero gbapụtara mgbaaka<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:42 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mgbaaka a na-agbanye na mkpịsịaka bụ ihe e ji emesi okwu ike. <char style="xt"><ref loc="EST 3:10">Est 3:10</ref></char></char></note> eze ya gbanye ya Josef nʼaka. O yikwasịkwara Josef uwe e ji ezi akwa ọcha duo, nyanye ya ihe ịnya nʼolu nke e ji ọlaedo kpụọ. <verse eid="GEN 41:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="GEN 41:43"/>O mere ka ọ nyaa ịnyịnya ụgbọ ya nke abụọ. Ndị oti mkpu na-etikwa nʼihu ya, “Gbuonụ ikpere nʼala.” Otu a ka Fero si mee Josef onye na-achị ala Ijipt niile.<verse eid="GEN 41:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="GEN 41:44"/>Fero gwakwara Josef sị, “Ọ bụ mụ onwe m bụ Fero! O nweghị onye ọbụla ga-ewelita aka maọbụ ụkwụ ya nʼala Ijipt niile ma ọ bụghị site nʼike i nyere ya.” <verse eid="GEN 41:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="GEN 41:45"/>Fero gụrụ Josef aha Zafenat-Pania.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:45 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Aha a pụtara, Onye nwere ike dị ka chi nke nwere ike ndụ na ọnwụ.</char></note> Ọ kpọnyekwara ya, Asenat, nwa Pọtifera, onye nchụaja obodo a na-akpọ On,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:45 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Pọtifera bụ onye nchụaja nke obodo On.</char></note> ka ọ bụrụ nwunye ya. Josef bịara gazuo ala Ijipt.<verse eid="GEN 41:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="GEN 41:46"/>Josef gbara iri afọ atọ mgbe o bidoro iguzo nʼihu Fero eze Ijipt. O si nʼihu Fero pụọ, malite ijegharị ebe niile nʼala Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 41:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="GEN 41:47"/>Nʼafọ asaa ahụ nke a na-eriju afọ, ala mepụtara nri nʼebe ọ dị ukwuu. <verse eid="GEN 41:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="GEN 41:48"/>Nʼime afọ asaa ndị a nke nri juru ebe niile nʼIjipt, Josef chịkọtara nri niile nke si nʼubi, ma chekwaa ha nʼụlọ e wuru maka iche nri nʼobodo niile ahụ. Nʼobodo ọbụla, ka ọ na-etinye ihe oriri nke si nʼubi gbara ya gburugburu. <verse eid="GEN 41:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="GEN 41:49"/>Josef chekwara ọka dị ukwuu nʼọnụọgụgụ, dịka aja dị nʼakụkụ osimiri. A kwụsịrị ịgụ ha ọnụ nʼihi na ha hiri nne nke ukwuu nke na ha enweghị ọnụọgụgụ.<verse eid="GEN 41:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="GEN 41:50"/>Tupu oge ụnwụ ahụ ebido, Asenat nwa nwanyị Pọtifera, onye nchụaja nke On, mụtara Josef ụmụ ndị ikom abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 41:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="GEN 41:51"/>Josef gụrụ ọkpara ya Manase,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:51 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Aha a bụ Manase pụtara Nchefu.</char></note> nʼihi na ọ sịrị, “Chineke emeela ka m chefuo ahụhụ m niile, mekwa ka m chefuo ndị ezinaụlọ nna m.” <verse eid="GEN 41:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="GEN 41:52"/>Josef gụrụ nwa ya nke abụọ Ifrem.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">41:52 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ifrem pụtara Ụba.</char></note> Ọ sịrị, “Nʼihi na Chineke emeela ka m mịa mkpụrụ nʼala nke ahụhụ m.”<verse eid="GEN 41:52"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="GEN 41:53"/>Afọ asaa nke ụba nri nke dịrị nʼala Ijipt mechara gabiga. <verse eid="GEN 41:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="GEN 41:54"/>Afọ asaa nke ụnwụ bidoro bịawa dịka Josef kwuru. Ụnwụ nọ nʼobodo niile, ma nʼala Ijipt niile nri dị. <verse eid="GEN 41:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="GEN 41:55"/>Ka agụ jidere ala Ijipt niile, ndị mmadụ tikuru Fero ka o nye ha nri. Ma Fero gwara ndị Ijipt niile, “Jekwurunụ Josef. Ihe ọbụla ọ gwara unu meenụ ya.”<verse eid="GEN 41:55"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="56" style="v" sid="GEN 41:56"/>Mgbe ụnwụ ahụ gbasara ruo nʼakụkụ niile nke ala ahụ, Josef meghepụrụ ụlọ ichebe nri niile bido iresi ndị Ijipt nri, nʼihi na ụnwụ ahụ dị njọ nʼala Ijipt niile. <verse eid="GEN 41:56"/><verse number="57" style="v" sid="GEN 41:57"/>Mba niile bịara Ijipt ịzụ nri site nʼaka Josef nʼihi na ụnwụ ahụ dị njọ nʼụwa niile.<verse eid="GEN 41:57"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 41"/>
  <chapter number="42" style="c" sid="GEN 42"/>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụnne Josef abịaruo Ijipt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 42:1"/>Ugbu a, Jekọb nụrụ na ọka dị nʼIjipt. Ọ sịrị ụmụ ya, “Kedụ ihe anyị jiri nọrọ na-elerịta onwe anyị anya” <verse eid="GEN 42:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 42:2"/>Ọ sịrị, “Lee anụrụ m na ọka dị nʼIjipt. Gbadatanụ nʼebe ahụ zụtara anyị ọka ka anyị dị ndụ ghara ịnwụ.”<verse eid="GEN 42:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 42:3"/>Ụmụnne Josef iri ndị ahụ gbadara Ijipt ịzụta ọka. <verse eid="GEN 42:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 42:4"/>Ma Jekọb ekweghị ka Benjamin nwanne nta Josef soro ha gaa, nʼihi na ọ tụrụ egwu na ihe ndaba ọjọọ nwere ike ịbịakwasị ya. <verse eid="GEN 42:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 42:5"/>Otu a, ụmụ Izrel so nʼọtụtụ ndị ọzọ ndị jekwara ịzụrụ nri nʼIjipt, nʼihi na ụnwụ ahụ dị njọ nʼala Kenan.<verse eid="GEN 42:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 42:6"/>Nʼoge a, Josef na-achị ala Ijipt, bụrụkwa onye iresi ndị obodo ọka dị nʼaka. Ya mere, mgbe ụmụnne Josef rutere, ha bịara hulata kpọọ isiala nye Josef. <verse eid="GEN 42:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 42:7"/>Mgbe Josef hụrụ ụmụnne ya, ọ matara ndị ha bụ. Ma ọ kpara agwa dịka onye na-amaghị ha, gwa ha okwu nʼolu ike, sị ha, “Ebee ka unu si bịa?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 42:7">Ha zara, “Anyị si ala Kenan bịa. Anyị bịara ịzụrụ nri.”<verse eid="GEN 42:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 42:8"/>Josef matara ụmụnne ya, ma ha onwe ha amataghị onye ọ bụ. <verse eid="GEN 42:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 42:9"/>Josef chetakwara nrọ ndị ahụ ọ rọrọ banyere ha. Ọ gwara ha okwu sị ha, “Unu bụ ndị nnyocha. Ịchọpụta adịghị ike ala anyị mere unu ji bịa.”<verse eid="GEN 42:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 42:10"/>Ha zara sị, “Nna anyị ukwu, anyị bụ ndị ohu gị bịara ịzụrụ nri. <verse eid="GEN 42:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 42:11"/>Anyị niile bụ ụmụ otu nna. Ndị ohu gị bụ ndị kwesiri ntụkwasị obi. Anyị abụghị ndị nnyopụta.”<verse eid="GEN 42:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 42:12"/>Ma Josef gwara ha sị, “Mba! Unu bịara ịchọpụta akụkụ obodo anyị nke a na-echezighị nke ọma.”<verse eid="GEN 42:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 42:13"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Ndị ohu gị dị ụmụnne iri na abụọ. Ọ bụkwa otu nna mụrụ anyị niile. Nna anyị na nwanne anyị nta, onye ikpeazụ ọ mụrụ nọ na Kenan ugbu a. Ma otu onye nʼime anyị anwụọla.”<verse eid="GEN 42:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 42:14"/>Josef sịrị, “Ihe unu na-akọ na-egosi na unu bụ ndị nnyopụta, dịka m gwara unu. <verse eid="GEN 42:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 42:15"/>Nke a ka a ga-eji anwale unu. Nʼaha Fero dị ndụ, unu agaghị esi nʼebe a laa tutu nwanne unu nke nta ahụ abịa nʼebe a. <verse eid="GEN 42:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 42:16"/>Zipụnụ otu onye nʼime unu ka ọ gaa kpọta nwanne unu nwoke. Ma aga m etinye ndị fọdụrụ nʼụlọ mkpọrọ, tutu m chọpụta ma ihe unu kwuru ọ bụ eziokwu maọbụ ụgha. Ọ bụrụ ụgha nʼezie, dịka Fero na-adị ndụ, unu bụ ndị nnyopụta.” <verse eid="GEN 42:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 42:17"/>O tinyere ha niile nʼụlọ mkpọrọ, hapụ ha nʼebe ahụ abalị atọ.<verse eid="GEN 42:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 42:18"/>Josef gwara ha, nʼụbọchị nke atọ, “Nke a bụ ihe unu ga-eme ma dị ndụ, nʼihi na abụ m onye na-atụ egwu Chineke. <verse eid="GEN 42:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 42:19"/>Ọ bụrụ na unu bụ ndị ezi mmadụ, ka otu onye nʼime unu nọdụ nʼebe a, nʼụlọ mkpọrọ, ka ndị fọdụrụ buru ọka bulaara ndị ezinaụlọ unu nọ nʼagụụ. <verse eid="GEN 42:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 42:20"/>Ma kpọtaranụ m nwanne unu nke nta nʼebe a, nke a ga-egosi na okwu unu bụ eziokwu, na unu agaghịkwa anwụ.” Ha mere otu a.<verse eid="GEN 42:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 42:21"/>Ha gwarịtara onwe ha okwu sị, “Nʼezie, ọ bụ nʼihi nwanne anyị nwoke ka ahụhụ ndị a ji abịakwasị anyị. Anyị hụrụ obi mgbawa ya, mgbe ọ na-arịọ ka anyị chebe ndụ ya, ma anyị egeghị ya ntị. Ọ bụ nke a mere mmekpa ahụ ndị a ji bịakwasị anyị ugbu a.”<verse eid="GEN 42:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 42:22"/>Ruben zara sị ha, “Ọ bụ na mụ agwaghị unu sị unu hapụ imejọ nwantakịrị ahụ, ma unu egeghị ntị? Ugbu a, anyị na-asa ajụjụ banyere ọbara ya.” <verse eid="GEN 42:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 42:23"/>Ha amataghị na Josef na-anụ ihe ha na-ekwu, nʼihi na onye nsụgharị okwu nọ nʼetiti ha.<verse eid="GEN 42:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 42:24"/>O sitere nʼebe ha nọ tụgharịa gaa kwaa akwa. Ọ lọghachikwutere ha ọzọ gwakwa ha okwu. O si nʼetiti ha kpọpụta Simiọn kee ya agbụ ka ha na-ele ya anya.<verse eid="GEN 42:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 42:25"/>Josef nyere iwu ka e kpojuo ọka nʼakpa ha, tinyekwara onye ọbụla ego ọ kwụrụ nʼakpa ya. Ọ nyere iwu ka e nye ha ihe ha ga-eri nʼụzọ. Mgbe e mesịrị ihe ndị a, <verse eid="GEN 42:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 42:26"/>ha bokwasịrị ịnyịnya ibu akpa ọka ha nʼotu nʼotu. Ha hapụrụ Ijipt lawa.<verse eid="GEN 42:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 42:27"/>Mgbe ha ruru ebe ha nọrọ ọnọdụ abalị, otu nʼime ha meghere akpa ya ka o nye ịnyịnya ibu ya ọka, ọ hụrụ ego ya nʼọnụ akpa ya. <verse eid="GEN 42:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 42:28"/>Ọ gwara ụmụnne ya sị, “Lee, e tighachiri ego m kwụrụ. Lee ya nʼakpa ọka m.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 42:28">Ike gwụrụ onye ọbụla nʼime ha. Site nʼahụ ịma jijiji ha lerịtara onwe ha anya sị, “Gịnị bụ ihe a Chineke mere anyị?”<verse eid="GEN 42:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 42:29"/>Mgbe ha lakwutere nna ha Jekọb nʼala Kenan, ha kọọrọ ya ihe niile dakwasịrị ha. Ha gwara ya sị, <verse eid="GEN 42:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 42:30"/>“Nwoke na-achị ala ahụ gwara anyị okwu nʼolu ike. O mesoro anyị mmeso dịka anyị bụ ndị bịara inyochapụta obodo ha. <verse eid="GEN 42:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 42:31"/>Ma anyị gwara ya sị, ‘Anyị bụ ndị kwesiri ntụkwasị obi, ndị na-abụghị ndị nnyopụta obodo. <verse eid="GEN 42:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 42:32"/>Anyị dị ụmụnne iri na abụọ ndị nwere otu nna. Otu nʼime anyị anọkwaghị, ma nke ntakịrị na nna anyị nọ na nʼala Kenan taa.’<verse eid="GEN 42:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 42:33"/>“Mgbe ahụ, nwoke a, onye na-achị ala ahụ, sịrị anyị, ‘Nke a ka m ga-eji mata ma unu bụ ndị ezi mmadụ. Hapụrụnụ m otu nwanne unu. Burunu ọka, bulaara ndị ezinaụlọ unu agụụ na-agụgbu. <verse eid="GEN 42:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 42:34"/>Ma kpọtara m nwanne unu nke nta. Mgbe ahụ ka m ga-ama ihe unu bụ. Ma unu bụ ndị nnyopụta maọbụ ndị ezi mmadụ. Mgbe ahụ, aga m ahapụrụ unu nwanne unu. Unu ga na-azụkwa ahịa nʼala a.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 42:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="GEN 42:35"/>Mgbe ha bidoro ịwụpụtasị ọka dị nʼakpa ha, lee, nʼime akpa ọka onye ọbụla, a chọtara ego ọ kwụrụ nʼakpa ya. Mgbe ha na nna ha hụrụ ego ndị a, ha tụrụ egwu. <verse eid="GEN 42:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="GEN 42:36"/>Ya mere, nna ha Jekọb gwara ha sị, “Unu agbawala m aka ụmụ. Josef anọghị, Simiọn anọkwaghị. Ma unu na-achọ iwezuga Benjamin. Naanị m ka ihe niile ndị a na-emegide!”<verse eid="GEN 42:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="GEN 42:37"/>Mgbe ahụ, Ruben gwara nna ya sị, “I nwere ike gbuo ụmụ m ndị ikom abụọ ma ọ bụrụ na m akpọghachighị Benjamin. Tifee ya nʼaka m, aga m akpọghachikwara gị ya.”<verse eid="GEN 42:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="GEN 42:38"/>Ma Jekọb sịrị, “Nwa m agaghị eso unu gaa. Nʼihi na nwanne ya anwụọla, ọ bụkwa naanị ya ka ọ fọdụrụ. Ọ bụrụ na nsogbu ezute ya nʼụzọ nʼije a, unu ga-eme ka m jiri isi awọ m laa nʼili nʼọnọdụ mwute.”<verse eid="GEN 42:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 42"/>
  <chapter number="43" style="c" sid="GEN 43"/>
  <para style="s1">Njeru Ijipt nke ugboro abụọ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 43:1"/>Ma ụnwụ a siri oke ike nʼala ahụ nʼoge a. <verse eid="GEN 43:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 43:2"/>O ruo, mgbe ha richara nri ha zụtara nʼIjipt, nna ha gwara ha sị, “Jeghachinụ, zụtara anyị ntakịrị nri.”<verse eid="GEN 43:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 43:3"/>Juda gwara nna ya bụ Jekọb sị, “Nwoke ahụ dọsiri anyị aka na ntị ike sị, ‘Unu agaghị ahụ ihu m ma ọ bụrụ na nwanne unu esoghị unu bịa.’ <verse eid="GEN 43:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 43:4"/>Ọ bụrụ na ị ga-edunyere anyị nwanne anyị, anyị ga-agbada gaa zụtara gị nri. <verse eid="GEN 43:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 43:5"/>Ma ọ bụrụ na ị gaghị edunyere anyị ya, anyị agaghị agbada, nʼihi na nwoke a sịrị anyị, ‘Unu agaghị ahụ ihu m ma ọ bụrụ na nwanna unu esoghị unu.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 43:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 43:6"/>Mgbe ahụ Izrel sịrị, “Gịnị mere unu ji wetara m nsogbu dị otu a, site nʼịgwa nwoke ahụ na unu nwere nwanne ọzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 43:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 43:7"/>Ha zara sị, “Nwoke a jụrụ anyị ajụjụ dị iche iche banyere onwe anyị, na ndị ezinaụlọ anyị. Ọ sị, ‘Nna unu, ọ dị ndụ ugbu a? Unu nwere nwanne ọzọ?’ Ya mere, anyị zara ajụjụ niile. O nweghị otu anyị siri mara na ọ ga-asị anyị kpọta nwanne anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 43:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 43:8"/>Mgbe ahụ, Juda sịrị nna ya Izrel, “Dunye m nwantakịrị a ka anyị bilie gawa, ka anyị dị ndụ ghara ịnwụ, ma anyị onwe anyị, ma gị, ma ụmụntakịrị anyị. <verse eid="GEN 43:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 43:9"/>Aga m eji onwe m gbaa ebe nʼihi ya. I nwere ike itife ya nʼaka m. Ọ bụrụ na m akpọtaghachighị ya, kpọbata ya nʼihu gị, mgbe ahụ, ịta ụta bụrụ nke m nʼihu gị, nʼụbọchị ndụ m niile. <verse eid="GEN 43:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 43:10"/>A sị nnọọ na anyị egbughị oge niile a, anyị gaara aga ma lọtakwarị ugboro abụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 43:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 43:11"/>Mgbe ahụ nna ha Izrel gwara ha sị, “Ọ bụrụ na ọ ga-adịrịrị otu a, gịnị ọzọ ka anyị ga-eme. Kama mgbe unu na-aga, werenụ nʼakpa unu onyinye ịnata ihuọma nke bụ ihe niile kachasị mma nke si nʼala a welaara nwoke a. Werenụ nwantịntị mmanụ otite, na nwantịntị mmanụ aṅụ, ha na ụda dị iche iche, na eso osisi máá, na akụ, na alụmọnd. <verse eid="GEN 43:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 43:12"/>Werekwanụ ego okpukpu abụọ nʼaka unu. Weghachirinụ ya ego ahụ e tinyere nʼọnụ akpa unu, eleghị anya ọ bụ nʼohihie anya ka ha ji tinye ya. <verse eid="GEN 43:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 43:13"/>Ngwa, kpọrọnụ nwanne unu nwoke bilienụ laghachikwurunụ nwoke ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 43:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 43:14"/>Ka Chineke Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile, mee ka nwoke ahụ nwee obi ebere nʼebe unu nọ. Ya meekwa ka o nwee ike ịhapụrụ unu nwanne unu Simiọn na Benjamin ka ha soro unu lọta. Ọ bụrụkwanụ uche Chineke na m ga-agbara aka ụmụ, ya mee dịka o si chọọ.”<verse eid="GEN 43:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 43:15"/>Ya mere, ndị ikom ahụ weere onyinye ndị a, na okpukpu ego abụọ nʼaka, ma kpọrọkwa Benjamin. Ha biliri ije. Garuo Ijipt, ma guzo nʼihu Josef. <verse eid="GEN 43:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 43:16"/>Mgbe Josef lepụrụ anya hụ Benjamin nʼetiti ha, ọ gwara onye na-elekọta ụlọ ya sị, “Duru ndị ikom ndị a gaa nʼụlọ. Gbuo anụ, kwadoo nri, nʼihi na ndị a ga-eso m rie nri ehihie.”<verse eid="GEN 43:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 43:17"/>Odibo a mere dịka Josef ziri ya. O duuru ndị ikom ndị ahụ gaa nʼụlọ Josef. <verse eid="GEN 43:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 43:18"/>Nʼoge a, mgbe a kpọbatara ha nʼụlọ, ndị ikom ndị ahụ tụrụ ụjọ, nʼihi na a kpọbatara ha nʼime ụlọ Josef. Ha sịrị, “Ọ bụ nʼihi ego ahụ e tighachiri nʼakpa anyị nʼoge mbụ ka e ji kpọbata anyị, ka o nwee ike ịchọta ụzọ ọ ga-esi megide anyị, mesie anyị ike, si otu a were anyị na ịnyịnya ibu anyị dịka ndị ohu ya.”<verse eid="GEN 43:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 43:19"/>Ha bịaruru odibo Josef ahụ nso gwa ya okwu nʼọnụ ụzọ ụlọ ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 43:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 43:20"/>Ha sịrị ya, “Nna anyị ukwu, anyị bịara ebe a nʼoge mbụ ịzụ ihe oriri. <verse eid="GEN 43:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 43:21"/>Ma, mgbe anyị rutere ebe anyị nọrọ ọnọdụ abalị, anyị meghere akpa anyị, chọpụta ego anyị kwụrụ nʼihi nri ahụ anyị zụrụ ka ọ dị nʼọnụ akpa anyị nʼotu na otu. E sepụkwaghị ya ihe ọ bụla. Ya mere, anyị weghachiri ya nʼoge a. <verse eid="GEN 43:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 43:22"/>Anyị jikwa ego ọzọ anyị ga-eji zụọ ihe oriri. Ma anyị amaghị onye tinyere ego ahụ nʼime akpa anyị.”<verse eid="GEN 43:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 43:23"/>Odibo ahụ zara sị ha, “Udo dịrị unu, unu atụla egwu, nʼihi na Chineke unu, na Chineke nna unu enyela unu akụ zoro ezo nʼime akpa unu. Ego unu kwụrụ ruru m aka.” Mgbe ahụ, ọ hapụrụ ha gaa kpọpụta Simiọn.<verse eid="GEN 43:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 43:24"/>Nʼoge ahụ, odibo ahụ duuru ndị ikom ndị ahụ bata nʼụlọ Josef, nye ha mmiri ha ji saa ụkwụ ha. O nyekwara ịnyịnya ibu ha nri. <verse eid="GEN 43:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 43:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, ụmụ Jekọb kwadoro onyinye ịnata ihuọma ha ji bịa, nke ha ga-enye Josef ma ọ bata nʼetiti ehihie, nʼihi na ha anụla na ha ga-eri nri nʼebe ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 43:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 43:26"/>Mgbe Josef lọtara ụlọ, ha wetaara ya onyinye dị nʼaka ha, daa nʼala, kpọọ isiala nye ya. <verse eid="GEN 43:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 43:27"/>Josef jụrụ ha ajụjụ banyere ọdịmma ha, jụọkwa ha sị, “Agadi nna unu, nke unu gwara m ihe banyere ya, ahụ ọ dịkwa ya? Ọ ka dịkwa ndụ.”<verse eid="GEN 43:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 43:28"/>Ha zaghachiri sị ya, “Ahụ dị ohu gị bụ nna anyị. Ọ ka nọ ndụ.” Ha hulatara isi ha, kpọọ isiala nye ya.<verse eid="GEN 43:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 43:29"/>Mgbe Josef welitere anya ya elu hụ nwanne ya Benjamin, onye bụ nwanne afọ ya, ọ jụrụ ha ajụjụ sị, “Onye a ọ bụ nwanne unu nke nta ahụ unu gwara m ihe banyere ya?” Tupu ha asaa ya ihe ọbụla, o lere Benjamin anya sị ya, “Ka amara Chineke dịrị gị, nwa m nwoke.” <verse eid="GEN 43:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 43:30"/>Mgbe ahụ kwa Josef mere ọsịịsọ pụọ nʼezi ịchọ ebe ọ ga-akwa akwa nʼihi na ọhụhụ ọ hụrụ nwanne ya anya ọzọ metụrụ ya nnọọ nʼobi. Ọ pụrụ banye nʼime ụlọ ya kwaa akwa.<verse eid="GEN 43:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 43:31"/>Emesịa, ọ sara ihu ya, pụta, jisie onwe ya ike nye odibo ya iwu ka o bute nri ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 43:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 43:32"/>Ha doziiri ya nri nke ya iche, doziekwara ụmụnne ya nri nke ha iche. Otu a kwa, ha dozikwaara ndị Ijipt ya na ha na-erikọ nri, nri nke ha iche. Nʼihi na ọ bụ ihe arụ nʼanya ndị Ijipt na ha na ndị Hibru ga-erikọta nri ọnụ. <verse eid="GEN 43:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 43:33"/>Ma mgbe e nyere ha ọnọdụ nʼihu Josef, e mere ka ha nọdụ dịka ha si tọọ ibe ha. Nke ọkpara buru ụzọ nọdụ, onye na-eso ya anọdụkwa. Otu a ka ha niile siri nọdụ ruo nʼonye ikpeazụ nʼime ha. Ha lerịtara onwe ha anya nʼihi na o juru ha anya. <verse eid="GEN 43:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 43:34"/>O sitekwara na nri e doziri ya nyebinye ha nri. Nri e nyere Benjamin dị ukwuu okpukpu ise karịa nri nke e nyere ha niile. Ha na ya riri, ṅụọkwa nʼuju.<verse eid="GEN 43:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 43"/>
  <chapter number="44" style="c" sid="GEN 44"/>
  <para style="s1">Iko ọlaọcha a chọtara nʼakpa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 44:1"/>Mgbe ahụ Josef nyere odibo nọ nʼụlọ ya iwu sị, “Gbajuo akpa ndị ikom ndị a nri. Tinyere ha nri nke onye ọbụla nʼime ha nwere ike ibu, tinyekwa ego nke onye ọbụla nʼime ha kwụrụ nʼọnụ akpa ya. <verse eid="GEN 44:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 44:2"/>Ma tinye iko ọlaọcha m nʼime ọnụ akpa onye nke nta nʼime ha. Tinyekwa ego ọ kwụrụ nʼihi nri ọ zụrụ nʼime akpa ya.” Odibo a mere dịka Josef gwara ya.<verse eid="GEN 44:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 44:3"/>Mgbe chi bọrọ, ha zipụrụ ndị ikom ndị a, ha na ịnyịnya ibu ha. <verse eid="GEN 44:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 44:4"/>Mgbe ha ji naanị ihe nta gafee obodo ahụ, Josef gwara odibo ya sị, “Bilie, chụso ndị ikom ndị ahụ ọsọ. I zute ha, sị ha, ‘Gịnị mere unu ji were ihe ọjọọ kwụghachi ihe ọma? <verse eid="GEN 44:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 44:5"/>Gịnị mere unu ji zuru iko ọlaọcha nna m ukwu, iko o ji aṅụ ihe ọṅụṅụ na nke o ji ajụ ase? Unu emeela ihe ọjọọ nʼihi ihe a unu mere.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 44:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 44:6"/>Mgbe odibo ahụ zutere ha, ọ gwara ha ihe ndị a. <verse eid="GEN 44:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 44:7"/>Ma ha zara sị ya, “Nna anyị ukwu, gịnị mere i ji ekwu ụdị okwu ndị a? Ihe arụ ka ọ bụ anyị ime ihe dị otu a. <verse eid="GEN 44:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 44:8"/>Lee, ego anyị chọtara nʼọnụ akpa anyị ka anyị sitere nʼala Kenan weghachi. Olee otu anyị ga-esi zuru ọlaedo maọbụ ọlaọcha site nʼụlọ nna gị ukwu? <verse eid="GEN 44:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 44:9"/>Onye ọbụla nʼime anyị a chọtara iko a nʼaka ya ga-anwụ. Anyị onwe anyị ga-aghọrọ nna anyị ukwu ndị ohu.”<verse eid="GEN 44:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 44:10"/>Odibo ahụ zara sị ha, “Ka ọ dịrị dịka unu kwuru. Onye ọbụla a chọtara ya nʼaka ga-abụ ohu m. Ma ndị a na-achọtaghị ya nʼaka ha enweghị ịta ụta ọbụla.”<verse eid="GEN 44:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 44:11"/>Ha mere ngwangwa, onye ọbụla tọdatara akpa ya. Onye ọbụla kwa meghere akpa ya. <verse eid="GEN 44:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 44:12"/>Odibo ahụ malitere nʼonye ukwu nʼetiti ha chọọ rute nʼonye nta. Ọ bụ nʼakpa Benjamin ka a chọtara iko ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 44:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 44:13"/>Mgbe ahụ, ha dọwara uwe ha nʼihi mwute. Onye ọbụla nʼime ha tighachiri ibu ya nʼelu ịnyịnya ibu ya. Ha niile bidokwara ịlaghachi azụ nʼobodo ha si pụta.<verse eid="GEN 44:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 44:14"/>Mgbe Juda na ụmụnne ya lọghachiri nʼụlọ Josef, ha hụrụ Josef ka ọ nọ nʼebe ahụ. Ha dara nʼala nʼihu ya. <verse eid="GEN 44:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 44:15"/>Ma Josef jụrụ ha sị, “Gịnị bụ ihe a unu mere? Ọ bụ na unu amataghị na onye dịka m nwere ike ịmata onye zuru iko m?”<verse eid="GEN 44:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 44:16"/>Ya mere Juda sị ya, “Gịnị ka anyị ga-ekwu? Olee otu anyị ga-esi gosi nʼaka anyị dị ọcha? Chineke ekpugheela ikpe ọmụma ndị ohu gị. Lee, anyị bụkwa ndị ohu onyenwe m. Anyị onwe anyị, tinyekwara onye a chọtara iko ahụ nʼaka ya.”<verse eid="GEN 44:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 44:17"/>Ma Josef sịrị, “Ọ ga-abụrụ m ajọ omume ime ihe dị otu ahụ. Naanị nwoke ahụ a chọpụtara iko ahụ nʼakpa ya bụ onye ga-abụ ohu m. Ma unu onwe unu nwere ike laa nʼudo jekwuru nna unu nʼudo.”<verse eid="GEN 44:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Arịrịọ nʼihi Benjamin</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 44:18"/>Juda jekwuuru ya, sị, “Biko, onyenwe m, kwere ka ohu gị gwa gị okwu. Ewesola mụ bụ ohu gị iwe nʼihi na ị nọ ọnọdụ dị ka Fero. <verse eid="GEN 44:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 44:19"/>Onyenwe m, ọ bụ gị jụrụ ndị ohu gị ajụjụ sị, ‘Unu nwere nna maọbụ nwanne?’ <verse eid="GEN 44:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 44:20"/>Anyị zara sị, ‘Anyị nwere nna onye bụ agadi, na otu nwa nwoke ọ mụtara nʼagadi ya. Nwanne nwantakịrị nwoke a anwụọla, ya mere naanị otu a fọdụrụ nʼime ụmụ nke nne ha mụtara. Nna ya hụkwara ya nʼanya.’<verse eid="GEN 44:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 44:21"/>“Mgbe ahụ, ị sị ndị ohu gị, ‘Kpọta nwantakịrị a ka m hụ ya anya.’ <verse eid="GEN 44:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 44:22"/>Ma anyị gwara onyenwe m sị na ‘Nwata a apụghị ịhapụ nna ya, nʼihi na nna ya ga-anwụ ma ọ bụrụ na ọ hapụ ya.’ <verse eid="GEN 44:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 44:23"/>Ma ị gwara ndị ohu gị sị, ‘Unu agaghị ahụ ihu m anya ọzọ, ma ọ bụrụ na nwanne unu a esoghị unu gbadata.’ <verse eid="GEN 44:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 44:24"/>Mgbe anyị lakwuuru ohu gị bụ nna anyị, anyị gwara ya okwu onyenwe m kwuru.<verse eid="GEN 44:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 44:25"/>“Mgbe nna anyị gwara anyị sị, ‘Laghachi gaa zụta nri,’ <verse eid="GEN 44:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 44:26"/>anyị gwara ya na, ‘Anyị agaghị agbada ma ọ bụrụ na nwanne anyị nta agaghị eso anyị. Nʼihi na anyị enweghị ike ịhụ nwoke ahụ anya, ma ọ bụrụ na nwanne anyị nta esoghị anyị.’<verse eid="GEN 44:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 44:27"/>“Oge ahụ, ohu gị bụ nna anyị sịrị anyị, ‘Unu maara na nwunye m mụụrụ m ụmụ nwoke abụọ. <verse eid="GEN 44:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 44:28"/>Otu nʼime ha funarịrị m, mgbe anụ ọhịa dọkasịrị ya iperipe na iperipe. Ruo ugbu a, ahụbeghị m ya anya. <verse eid="GEN 44:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 44:29"/>Ọ bụrụ na unu anapụkwa m onye nke a, si otu a mee ka ihe ọjọọ zute ya, ọ pụtara na unu ga-eme ka m jiri isi awọ m laa nʼili nʼọnọdụ obi ọjọọ?’<verse eid="GEN 44:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 44:30"/>“Ya mere, ọ bụrụ na m alaghachikwute ohu gị, bụ nna anyị, ma nwantakịrị a esoghị anyị, ebe ọ bụ na e kekọtara ndụ nna anyị na ndụ nwantakịrị a, <verse eid="GEN 44:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 44:31"/>mgbe ọ ga-ahụ na nwantakịrị a esoghị anyị, ọ ga-anwụ. Mgbe ahụ, anyị bụ ndị ohu gị, ga-eme ka nna anyị jiri isi awọ laa nʼili nʼọnọdụ obi ọjọọ. <verse eid="GEN 44:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 44:32"/>Biko, onyenwe m, eji m ndụ m zọọrọ nna m ebe na m ga-elezi nwantakịrị a anya. Asị m ya, ‘Ọ bụrụ na m akpọghachighị nwantakịrị a nye gị, ka ịta ụta bụrụ nke m nʼihu gị bụ nna m nʼụbọchị niile nke ndu m.’<verse eid="GEN 44:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 44:33"/>“Ya mere ugbu a, biko, ka ohu gị nọdụ dịka ohu onyenwe m nʼọnọdụ nwantakịrị a, ka nwantakịrị a soro ụmụnne ya laghachikwuru nna anyị. <verse eid="GEN 44:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 44:34"/>Aga m esi aṅaa laghachikwuru nna m ma ọ bụrụ na mụ na nwantakịrị a esoghị? Enweghị m ike ilekwasị ihe ọjọọ ga-adakwasị nna m anya.”<verse eid="GEN 44:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 44"/>
  <chapter number="45" style="c" sid="GEN 45"/>
  <para style="s1">Ụmụnne Josef amara onye ọ bụ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 45:1"/>Nʼoge a, Josef enwekwaghị ike ijite onwe ya aka nʼihu ndị na-ejere ya ozi. O welitara olu sị, “Zipụnụ onye ọbụla site nʼebe m nọ.” Ya mere, o nweghị onye ya na Josef nọ mgbe ọ kọọrọ ụmụnne ya onye ọ bụ. <verse eid="GEN 45:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 45:2"/>O tiri mkpu akwa nke ndị Ijipt nụrụ, na nke ndị ụlọ Fero nụkwara.<verse eid="GEN 45:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 45:3"/>Josef gwara ụmụnne ya sị, “Mụ onwe m bụ Josef. Nna m ọ ka nọ ndụ ugbu a?” Ma ụmụnne ya enweghị ọnụ ha ji asa ya, nʼihi na oke egwu jidere ha nʼihu ya.<verse eid="GEN 45:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 45:4"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef sịrị ụmụnne ya, “Biko, bịanụ m nso.” Mgbe ha bịara ya nso, ọ sịrị ha, “Abụ m nwanne unu, Josef, onye unu rere ree gaa Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 45:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 45:5"/>Ma otu ọ dị, ka ọ ghara iwute unu, unu atakwala onwe unu ụta nʼihi orure unu rere m. Nʼihi na ọ bụ nʼihi ichebe ndụ unu ka Chineke ji buru ụzọ zite m nʼebe a. <verse eid="GEN 45:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 45:6"/>Oge ụnwụ agwụchabeghị. Ọ bụ ezie na afọ abụọ nke oke ụnwụ agafeela, ma ọ fọdụrụ afọ ise ọzọ nʼihu, oge a na-agaghị akọ ihe ọbụla nʼala, maọbụ iwere ihe ọbụla nʼubi. <verse eid="GEN 45:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 45:7"/>Chineke zitere m ka m buru ụzọ bịa nʼebe a nʼihi ime ka ndụ fọdụrụ unu nʼụwa, na ịzọpụta ndụ unu site nʼụzọ nnapụta dị oke egwu.<verse eid="GEN 45:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 45:8"/>“Ya mere, ọ bụghị unu zitere m nʼebe a, kama ọ bụ Chineke. Ya onwe ya emeela ka m ghọọrọ Fero nna, na onyeisi ezinaụlọ ya niile, na onye na-achị ala Ijipt niile. <verse eid="GEN 45:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 45:9"/>Ugbu a, meenụ ngwa lakwuru nna m, sị ya, ‘Ihe ndị a ka Josef nwa gị nwoke kwuru, Chineke emeela m onye na-achị Ijipt niile. Egbula oge ịbịakwute m. <verse eid="GEN 45:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 45:10"/>Ị ga-ebi nʼala Goshen,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">45:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ala Goshen bụ ala na-emepụta nri nʼebe ọ dị ukwuu. Ọ dị na mpaghara akụkụ ọnụ mmiri osimiri Naịl.</char></note> ka i nwee ike ịnọ m nso, gị na ụmụ gị, na ụmụ ụmụ gị, na igwe ewu na atụrụ gị, na igwe ehi gị, na ihe niile i nwere. <verse eid="GEN 45:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 45:11"/>Nʼebe ahụ ka m ga-enyekwa gị ihe ị chọrọ, nʼihi na ụnwụ afọ ise ka dị nʼihu na-abịa. Ọ bụrụ na i meghị otu a, gị na ezinaụlọ gị na ihe niile bụ nke gị ga-ada ụkpa.’<verse eid="GEN 45:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 45:12"/>“Nʼezie, anya unu na nʼanya nwanne m Benjamin, ahụla na mụ onwe m ji ọnụ m na-agwa unu okwu ndị a. <verse eid="GEN 45:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 45:13"/>Unu ga-akọrọ nna m maka nsọpụrụ niile a na-enye m nʼala Ijipt na ihe niile unu hụrụ. Kpọtakwanụ nna m ọsịịsọ ebe a.”<verse eid="GEN 45:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 45:14"/>Ugbu a, ọ dakwasịrị nʼolu Benjamin, nwanne ya, kwaa akwa. Benjamin jidekwara ya nʼolu kwaa akwa. <verse eid="GEN 45:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 45:15"/>Emesịa, o suturu ụmụnne ya niile ọnụ, bekwasịkwa ha akwa. Nʼikpeazụ, ụmụnne ya kpanyeere ya ụka.<verse eid="GEN 45:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 45:16"/>Mgbe akụkọ a ruru ụlọ Fero na ụmụnne Josef bịara, ọ tọrọ Fero na ndịisi ozi niile ya ụtọ. <verse eid="GEN 45:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 45:17"/>Fero gwara Josef sị ya, “Gwa ụmụnne gị, ka ha mee ihe otu a, ha bokwasị ịnyịnya ibu unu ibu laghachikwa nʼala Kenan. <verse eid="GEN 45:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 45:18"/>Ha ruo, ha kpọta nna gị, na ezinaụlọ ha, ka ha lọghachikwute m nʼala Ijipt. Nʼihi na aga m enye ha ala kachasị mma nʼIjipt. Ha onwe ha ga-erikwa uru ala ahụ.<verse eid="GEN 45:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 45:19"/>“Gwakwa ụmụnne gị okwu sị ha, ‘Sitenụ nʼala Ijipt were ụgbọala, nke unu ga-eji budata ndị nwunye unu na ụmụntakịrị unu. Dutekwanụ nna unu. <verse eid="GEN 45:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 45:20"/>Unu esogbula onwe unu banyere ngwa ụlọ unu, nʼihi na ihe niile dị mma nʼala Ijipt bụ nke unu.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 45:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 45:21"/>Ya mere ụmụ Izrel mere ihe ndị a. Josef nyere ha ụgbọala dịka Fero nyere nʼiwu. O nyekwara ha nri ha ga-eri nʼụzọ. <verse eid="GEN 45:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 45:22"/>O nyere onye ọ bụla nʼime ha uwe mgbanwe ọhụrụ, ma o nyere Benjamin narị shekel ọlaọcha atọ, na uwe mgbanwe ise. <verse eid="GEN 45:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 45:23"/>O zipụụrụ nna ya ihe ndị a: ịnyịnya ibu iri ndị e bokwasịrị ihe mara mma niile si nʼala Ijipt, na nne ịnyịnya ibu iri ndị e bokwasịrị ọka na achịcha, na ihe ndị ọzọ dị iche iche, nʼihi ije ya. <verse eid="GEN 45:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 45:24"/>O zipụrụ ụmụnne ya. Ma oge ha na-achọ ịhapụ ya, ọ gwara ha sị, “Unu esekwala okwu nʼụzọ.”<verse eid="GEN 45:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 45:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, ha hapụrụ ala Ijipt mechaa rute ala Kenan, bịakwute Jekọb nna ha. <verse eid="GEN 45:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 45:26"/>Ha gwara ya sị, “Josef ka nọ ndụ. Nʼezie, ọ bụ ya na-achị ala Ijipt niile.” Ma o siiri Jekọb ike ịnabata akụkọ a. O kwenyeghị na ọ bụ eziokwu. <verse eid="GEN 45:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 45:27"/>Ma mgbe ha gwasịrị ya ihe niile Josef gwara ha, mgbe ọ hụkwara ụgbọala niile Josef zitere ka e jiri bute ya, mmụọ nna ha Jekọb lọghachiri. <verse eid="GEN 45:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 45:28"/>Mgbe ahụ Izrel kwuru sị, “Ekwetala m! Josef nwa m ka dị ndụ. Aga m aga hụ ya anya tupu m nwụọ.”<verse eid="GEN 45:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 45"/>
  <chapter number="46" style="c" sid="GEN 46"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb abịaruo Ijipt</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 46:1"/>Izrel biliri ije, ya na ihe niile o nwere rute Bịasheba. Ebe a, ọ chụrụ aja nye Chineke nke nna ya Aịzik.<verse eid="GEN 46:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 46:2"/>Chineke gwara Izrel okwu nʼọhụ nke abalị. Ọ sịrị, “Jekọb! Jekọb!”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 46:2">Ọ zara sị, “Lee m nʼebe a.”<verse eid="GEN 46:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 46:3"/>Chineke gwara ya sị, “Abụ m Chineke, Chineke nke nna gị. Atụla egwu ịgbada Ijipt nʼihi na aga m eme gị ka ị ghọọ mba dị ukwuu nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 46:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 46:4"/>Mụ onwe m ga-eso gị agbada nʼala Ijipt. Mụ onwe m ga-akpọlatakwa gị ọzọ. Josef nʼonwe ya ga-eji aka ya ekpuchikwa gị anya.”<verse eid="GEN 46:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 46:5"/>Jekọb mechara si na Bịasheba pụta. Ụmụ Izrel kuuru Jekọb nna ha, na ụmụaka ha na ndị nwunye ha, kubanye nʼụgbọala ahụ Fero zitere ka ha ji bute ya. <verse eid="GEN 46:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 46:6"/>Ha buuru anụ ụlọ ha niile, na ihe onwunwe ha niile, nke ha kpatara nʼala Kenan, gaa Ijipt. Jekọb na agbụrụ ya niile so. <verse eid="GEN 46:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 46:7"/>Ụmụ ya ndị ikom niile, na ụmụ ụmụ ya ndị ikom niile, na ụmụ ya ndị inyom niile, na ụmụ ụmụ ya ndị inyom niile, na ndị niile bụ mkpụrụ afọ ya, ka ọ kpọrọ gaa Ijipt.<verse eid="GEN 46:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 46:8"/>Ndị a bụ aha ụmụ ndị ikom Izrel, ya bụ Jekọb na ụmụ ụmụ ya, ndị sooro ya gaa Ijipt.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="GEN 46:8"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="GEN 46:8">Ruben, ọkpara Jekọb<verse eid="GEN 46:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 46:9"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Ruben bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:9">Hanok, na Palu, na Hezrọn na Kami.<verse eid="GEN 46:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 46:10"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Simiọn bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:10">Jemuel, na Jamin, na Ohad, na Jakin, na Zoha, na Shaul. Nne Shaul bụ nwanyị Kenan.<verse eid="GEN 46:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 46:11"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Livayị bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:11">Geshọn, na Kohat, na Merari.<verse eid="GEN 46:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 46:12"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Juda bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:12">Ịa, na Onan, na Shela, na Perez, na Zera. Ma Ịa na Onan nwụrụ nʼala Kenan.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:12">Ụmụ ndị ikom Perez bụ,</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="GEN 46:12">Hezrọn na Hamul.<verse eid="GEN 46:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 46:13"/>Ma ụmụ ndị ikom Isaka bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:13">Tola, na Puva, na Jashub, na Shịmrọn.<verse eid="GEN 46:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 46:14"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Zebụlọn bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:14">Sered, na Elọn, na Jaliil.<verse eid="GEN 46:14"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 46:15"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ ndị ikom Lịa mụụrụ Jekọb nʼala Padan Aram. Ọ mụtakwara otu nwanyị aha ya bụ Daịna. Ụmụ ndị ikom na ndị inyom ndị a dị iri atọ na atọ.<verse eid="GEN 46:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 46:16"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Gad bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:16">Zefọn, na Hagi, na Shuni, na Ezbon, na Eri, na Arodi na Areli.<verse eid="GEN 46:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 46:17"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Asha bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:17">Imna, Ishva, Ishvi na Beriya. Nwanne ha nwanyị bụ Sera.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:17">Ụmụ Beriya bụ,</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="GEN 46:17">Heba na Malkiel.<verse eid="GEN 46:17"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 46:18"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ a mụụrụ Jekọb site na Zilpa, odibo nwanyị ahụ Leban kpọnyere Lịa nwa ya nwanyị. Ha dị iri na isii nʼọnụọgụgụ.<verse eid="GEN 46:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 46:19"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb site na Rechel nwunye ya bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:19">Josef na Benjamin.<verse eid="GEN 46:19"/></para>
  <para style="li3">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 46:20"/>Nʼala Ijipt, a mụụrụ Josef Manase na Ifrem, site na nwunye ya Asenat nwa nwanyị Pọtifera, onye nchụaja nke On.<verse eid="GEN 46:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 46:21"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Benjamin bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:21">Bela, Beka, Ashbel, Gera, Neeman, Ehi, Rosh, Mupim, Hupim na Aad.<verse eid="GEN 46:21"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 46:22"/>Ndị a bụ ndị ikom nke Rechel mụụrụ Jekọb. Ha dị iri na anọ.<verse eid="GEN 46:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 46:23"/>Nwa nwoke nke Dan mụrụ bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:23">Hushim.<verse eid="GEN 46:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 46:24"/>Ụmụ ndị ikom Naftalị bụ,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="GEN 46:24">Jaziil, na Guni, na Jeza, na Shilem.<verse eid="GEN 46:24"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 46:25"/>Ndị a bụ ụmụ ndị ikom a mụụrụ Jekọb site na Bilha, odibo nwanyị ahụ Leban kpọnyere nwa ya nwanyị Rechel. Ha niile dị asaa.<verse eid="GEN 46:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 46:26"/>Ya mere, ndị niile so Jekọb gaa Ijipt, ndị bụ ụmụ ụmụ ya, na-agụghị ndị nwunye ụmụ Jekọb niile, dị iri mmadụ isii na isii. <verse eid="GEN 46:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 46:27"/>Tinyere ụmụ ndị ikom abụọ amụtara nye Josef nʼIjipt, ndị si nʼezinaụlọ Jekọb gara Ijipt dị iri asaa.<verse eid="GEN 46:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 46:28"/>Jekọb zipụrụ Juda ka jekwuru Josef ịjụta ya ụzọ Goshen. Mgbe ha rutere nʼala Goshen, <verse eid="GEN 46:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 46:29"/>Josef kwadoro ịnyịnya ụgbọ ya gawa Goshen izute nna ya Izrel. Mgbe Josef bịara nʼihu nna ya, ọ makụrụ ya, bee akwa ogologo oge.<verse eid="GEN 46:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 46:30"/>Izrel gwara Josef sị, “Ugbu a ejikerela m ịnwụ, ebe m hụrụ ihu gị anya ọzọ, mata na ị ka dị ndụ.”<verse eid="GEN 46:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 46:31"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef gwara ụmụnne ya na ndị ezinaụlọ nna ya niile sị, “Ka m gaa kọọrọ Fero. Ka m gaa sị ya, ‘Ụmụnne m na ezinaụlọ nna m, ndị bi nʼala Kenan abịakwutela m. <verse eid="GEN 46:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 46:32"/>Ha bụ ndị ọzụzụ atụrụ, ndị na-elekọta anụ ụlọ. Ha chị igwe ewu na atụrụ ha, na igwe ehi ha, na ihe niile ha ji biri.’ <verse eid="GEN 46:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 46:33"/>Ya mere, ọ bụrụ na Fero akpọ unu jụọ unu ajụjụ sị, ‘Gịnị bụ ọrụ aka unu?’ <verse eid="GEN 46:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="GEN 46:34"/>Unu ga-asị ya, ‘Ndị ohu gị bụ ndị ọzụzụ anụ ụlọ site na mgbe anyị bụ ụmụnta, dịka nna nna anyị ha bụ.’ Mgbe ahụ, ọ ga-ekwe ka unu biri nʼala Goshen. Nʼihi na ndị niile na-azụ ewu na atụrụ bụ ndị akpọrọ asị nʼala Ijipt.”<verse eid="GEN 46:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 46"/>
  <chapter number="47" style="c" sid="GEN 47"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 47:1"/>Josef gara gwa Fero sị, “Nna m na ụmụnne m ejirila igwe ewu na atụrụ ha, igwe ehi ha na ihe niile ha nwere site nʼala Kenan bịa nʼebe a. Ha nọ nʼala Goshen.” <verse eid="GEN 47:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 47:2"/>Mgbe ọ gara ịgwa Fero okwu, o duuru mmadụ ise nʼetiti ụmụnne ya ndị ikom gosi ha Fero.<verse eid="GEN 47:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 47:3"/>Fero jụrụ ụmụnne ya ajụjụ sị ha, “Gịnị bụ ọrụ aka unu?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 47:3">Ha zara sị ya, “Ndị ohu gị bụ ndị ọzụzụ atụrụ dịka nna nna anyị ha.” <verse eid="GEN 47:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 47:4"/>Ha kwukwara sị, “Anyị bịara ịnọ dịka ọbịa nʼala a nʼihi na ụnwụ a siri oke ike nʼala Kenan. O nweghị nri igwe ewu na atụrụ anyị nwere iri nʼala ahụ. Ya mere, anyị na-arịọ ka i nye ndị ohu gị ike ka ha biri nʼala Goshen.”<verse eid="GEN 47:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 47:5"/>Fero gwara Josef sị, “Nna gị na ụmụnne gị abịakwutela gị. Ha biri nʼala Goshen. <verse eid="GEN 47:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 47:6"/>Ala Ijipt dịkwa gị nʼihu. Họrọ ebe ọbụla masịrị gị nke dịkwa ezi mma nye nna gị na ụmụnne gị ka ha biri. Ka ha biri na Goshen. Ọ bụrụkwa na ị maara ndị ikom nʼetiti ha ndị nwere ike, mee ha ndị na-elekọta igwe anụ ụlọ m.”<verse eid="GEN 47:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 47:7"/>Josef kpọtara nna ya Jekọb, mee ka o guzo nʼihu Fero. Jekọb nọ nʼebe ahụ gọzie Fero. <verse eid="GEN 47:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 47:8"/>Fero jụrụ Jekọb sị, “Ị gbaala afọ ole ugbu a?”<verse eid="GEN 47:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 47:9"/>Jekọb zara Fero sị ya: “Ebiela m dịka onye ọbịa narị afọ na iri afọ atọ. Ọnụọgụgụ afọ ndị a ehighị nne, ma ha jupụtara nʼahụhụ na nsogbu. Ma a nọrubeghị m ọnụọgụgụ afọ nna m ha gbara mgbe ha biri nʼụwa dịka ọbịa.” <verse eid="GEN 47:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 47:10"/>Jekọb gọziri Fero, site nʼihu ya pụọ.<verse eid="GEN 47:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 47:11"/>Ya mere, Josef mere ka nna ya na ụmụnne ya biri nʼala Ijipt. O nyere ha ala kachasị mma nʼala ahụ na mpaghara Ramesis, dịka Fero nyere nʼiwu. <verse eid="GEN 47:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 47:12"/>Josef nyere nna ya na ụmụnne ya na ezinaụlọ nna ya nri dịka ọnụọgụgụ nke ụmụ ha si dị.<verse eid="GEN 47:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ụnwụ na ụkọ nri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 47:13"/>Ma nri adịghị nʼala ahụ niile nʼihi na ụnwụ ahụ dị nnọọ njọ. Ihe siri ike nʼala Ijipt ma nʼala Kenan nʼihi ụnwụ a. <verse eid="GEN 47:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 47:14"/>Josef chịkọtara ego niile dị nʼala Ijipt, na nʼala Kenan, nke ndị mmadụ ji kwụọ ụgwọ nri ha zụrụ webata ha nʼụlọeze Fero. <verse eid="GEN 47:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 47:15"/>Mgbe ego niile dị ndị mmadụ nʼaka gwụchara nʼala Ijipt ma nʼala Kenan, ndị Ijipt niile bịakwutere Josef sị ya, “Nye anyị nri, gịnị mere anyị ga-eji nwụọ nʼihu gị? Ego anyị agwụla.”<verse eid="GEN 47:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 47:16"/>Mgbe ahụ Josef zara sị ha: “Jirinụ anụ ụlọ unu kwụọ ụgwọ nri m ga-enye unu, ebe ọ bụ na ego unu agwụla.” <verse eid="GEN 47:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 47:17"/>Ya mere, ha kpụtaara Josef anụ ụlọ ha. Josef nyere ha nri nʼọnọdụ ịnyịnya ha, na atụrụ ha, na ewu ha, na ehi, na ịnyịnya ibu ha. O were nri zụọ ha nʼafọ ahụ nʼọnọdụ anụ ụlọ ha niile.<verse eid="GEN 47:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 47:18"/>Mgbe afọ ahụ gafesịrị, ha bịakwutekwara ya nʼafọ nke ọzọ sị ya, “Anyị agaghị ezoro onyenwe anyị na ego anyị agwụla, na igwe anụ ụlọ anyị bụkwa nke gị. O nweghị ihe ọzọ fọdụrụ anyị karịa ahụ anyị na ala anyị. <verse eid="GEN 47:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 47:19"/>Gịnị mere anyị ga-eji nọọ nʼagụụ nʼihu gị? Zụrụ anyị na ala anyị nʼọnọdụ ụgwọ anyị ga-akwụ maka nri ị ga-enye anyị. Ka anyị na ala anyị bụrụ ndị ohu Fero. Nye anyị mkpụrụ ubi ka anyị dịrị ndụ ghara ịnwụ, ka ala a ghara ịbụ ihe tọgbọrọ nʼefu.”<verse eid="GEN 47:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 47:20"/>Ya mere, Josef zụtaara Fero ala Ijipt niile. Ndị Ijipt niile nʼotu nʼotu rere ala ha nʼihi oke ụnwụ ahụ dakwasịrị ha. Mgbe ahụ, ala ha niile ghọrọ nke Fero. <verse eid="GEN 47:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 47:21"/>Ya mere, Josef si otu a mee ka ndị Ijipt niile ghọọ ndị ohu Fero, site nʼotu obodo nʼala ahụ ruo na nke ọzọ ya. <verse eid="GEN 47:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 47:22"/>Ala nke Josef na-azụtaghị nʼoge a bụ naanị ala ndị nchụaja. Nʼihi na ndị nchụaja si nʼaka Fero na-enweta nri ha site nʼoge ruo nʼoge. Ha nwekwara nri na-ezuru ha site na oke ahụ Fero na-enye ha. Ya mere ha ereghị ala ha.<verse eid="GEN 47:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 47:23"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef gwara ndị mmadụ ahụ niile okwu sị, “Lee, azụọla unu taa, zụkwaa a ala unu nye Fero. <verse eid="GEN 47:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 47:24"/>Nʼoge owuwe ihe ubi, otu ụzọ nʼime ụzọ ise nke ihe unu nwetara nʼubi unu bụ nke Fero. Deberenụ onwe unu ụzọ anọ fọdụrụ ka ọ bụrụ ihe unu ga-akụ nʼubi na ihe unu ga-eri na ihe ndị ezinaụlọ unu, na nke ụmụntakịrị unu ga-eri.”<verse eid="GEN 47:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 47:25"/>Ha zara sị ya, “Ị zọpụtala ndụ anyị. Ka anyị hụta amara nʼihu nna anyị ukwu. Anyị ga-abụ ndị ohu Fero.”<verse eid="GEN 47:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 47:26"/>Josef mere ka nke a bụrụ iwu nʼala Ijipt niile ruo taa, na Fero ga-ewe otu ụzọ nʼime ụzọ ise nke ihe ọbụla si nʼala. Naanị ihe si nʼala ndị nchụaja bụ nke na-esoghị nʼiwu a.<verse eid="GEN 47:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 47:27"/>Izrel biri na Goshen nke dị nʼala Ijipt. Ha kpatara akụ hie nne, mụbaa nʼọmụmụ, ma nʼọnụọgụgụ.<verse eid="GEN 47:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 47:28"/>Jekọb biri nʼala Ijipt afọ iri na asaa. Ya mere, afọ niile Jekọb gbara bụ narị afọ na iri afọ anọ na asaa. <verse eid="GEN 47:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 47:29"/>Mgbe ụbọchị ọnwụ Izrel na-abịaru nso, ọ kpọrọ Josef nwa ya sị ya, “Ọ bụrụ na m ahụtala amara nʼihu gị, tinye aka gị nʼokpuru apata m, kwee m nkwa na ị ga-egosi m obi ebere na ezi ntụkwasị obi. Elila m nʼala nʼIjipt. <verse eid="GEN 47:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 47:30"/>Kama, mgbe m nwụrụ, site nʼala Ijipt bupụ m. Buru ozu m gaa lie ya ebe e liri nna m ha.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 47:30">Ọ zara, “Aga m eme dịka i kwuru.”<verse eid="GEN 47:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 47:31"/>Ọ sịrị ya, “Ṅụọrọ m iyi na ị ga-eme ya.” Josef ṅụọrọ ya iyi. Izrel nʼonwe ya, kpọrọ isiala dịka ọ dabere nʼelu mkpanaka ya.<verse eid="GEN 47:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 47"/>
  <chapter number="48" style="c" sid="GEN 48"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb agọzie ụmụ Josef</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 48:1"/>Mgbe ihe ndị a gasịrị, a gwara Josef sị, “Lee nna gị na-arịa ọrịa.” Josef biliri duru ụmụ ya ndị ikom abụọ bụ Manase na Ifrem gawa ileta ya. <verse eid="GEN 48:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 48:2"/>Mgbe a gwara Jekọb okwu sị ya, “Nwa gị nwoke Josef abịala ileta gị.” Izrel chịkọtara ume ya, jisie ike, nọdụ ala nʼelu akwa ya.<verse eid="GEN 48:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 48:3"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb sịrị Josef, “Chineke, Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile gosiri m onwe ya na Luz, nʼala Kenan, ma gọziekwa m. <verse eid="GEN 48:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 48:4"/>Ọ sịrị m, ‘Lee, aga m eme ka ị mịa mkpụrụ, baakwa ụba nʼọnụọgụgụ. Aga m eme ka ị ghọọ ọgbakọ ọtụtụ mba. Aga m enye gị ala a ka ọ bụrụ ihe nketa ebighị ebi maka agbụrụ gị ndị ga-esote gị.’<verse eid="GEN 48:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 48:5"/>“Ugbu a, ana m eme ụmụ gị ndị ikom abụọ ndị a, ndị a mụtaara gị nʼala Ijipt, ụmụ nke m. Ha abụọ, Ifrem na Manase, ga-abụ ụmụ m, dịka Ruben na Simiọn si bụrụ ụmụ m. <verse eid="GEN 48:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 48:6"/>Ma ụmụ ọzọ a ga-amụtara gị ga-abụ nke gị. Ọ bụ aha ụmụnne ha ndị a ka a ga-eji mara ha nʼala nketa nke ha. <verse eid="GEN 48:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 48:7"/>Ana m eme nke a nʼihi na mgbe m si Padan Aram pụta, nne unu Rechel, nwụrụ nʼala Kenan mgbe anyị ka nọ nʼụzọ ije anyị nʼebe dịtụ anya site na Efrat. Nʼakụkụ ụzọ e si aga Efrat, ya bụ Betlehem, ka m likwara ya.”<verse eid="GEN 48:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 48:8"/>Mgbe Izrel hụrụ ụmụ ndị ikom abụọ Josef kpọ bịa, ọ jụrụ Josef ajụjụ sị, “Ndị a, bụ ndị ole?”<verse eid="GEN 48:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 48:9"/>Josef zara nna ya sị, “Ha bụ ụmụ ndị ikom ndị Chineke nyere m nʼebe a.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="GEN 48:9">Ya mere, Jekọb gwara ya sị, “Kpọtara m ha, ka m gọzie ha.”<verse eid="GEN 48:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 48:10"/>Nʼoge a, Izrel adịghị ahụzikwa ụzọ nke ọma nʼihi ime agadi ya. Ya mere, Josef duuru ụmụ ya ndị ikom ndị ahụ bịa nso ebe nna ya nọ. Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb suturu ha ọnụ, makụọ ha.<verse eid="GEN 48:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 48:11"/>Izrel sịrị Josef, “O nweghị mgbe m lere anya na m ga-ahụ ihu gị ọzọ. Ma Chineke emeela ka m hụkwa ụmụ gị.”<verse eid="GEN 48:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 48:12"/>Josef sitere nʼikpere<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">48:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ị kuu mmadụ nʼikpere, bụ mmemme iji gosipụta na onye ahụ eku nʼikpere, a bụrụla nwa onye ahụ kuu ya.</char></note> Jekọb kupu ụmụ ya, bịa hulata isi ala. O kpuru ihu ya nʼala mgbe o mere nke a. <verse eid="GEN 48:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 48:13"/>Josef kpọọrọ ha abụọ, Ifrem nʼaka nri ya nke bụ aka ekpe Izrel, na Manase nʼaka ekpe ya nke bụ aka nri Izrel, kpọta ha bịa nna ya nso. <verse eid="GEN 48:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 48:14"/>Ma Izrel setịrị aka nri bikwasị ya nʼisi Ifrem, nwa nke nta. Ma aka ekpe ya ka o setịpụrụ bikwasị nʼisi Manase bụ ọkpara.<verse eid="GEN 48:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 48:15"/>Mgbe ahụ, ọ gọziri Josef sị ya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 48:15">“Ka Chineke, onye nna m ha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:15">Ebraham na Aịzik jere ije nʼihu ya</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 48:15">Chineke onye bụrịị Onye zụrụ m dịka atụrụ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:15">ogologo ndụ m niile ruo taa,<verse eid="GEN 48:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 48:16"/>Mmụọ ozi ahụ napụtara m site nʼihe egwu niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:16">ya gọzie ụmụ ndị ikom ndị a.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 48:16">Ka ha bụrụ ndị a kpọkwasịrị aha m</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:16">na aha nna m ha Ebraham na Aịzik,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 48:16">ka ha mụbaa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:16">hie nne nʼelu ụwa.”<verse eid="GEN 48:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 48:17"/>O wutere Josef mgbe ọ hụrụ na nna ya bikwasịrị aka nri ya nʼisi Ifrem. O jidere aka nna ya iwepụ ya nʼisi Ifrem, ka ọ tụkwasị ya nʼisi Manase. <verse eid="GEN 48:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 48:18"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef sịrị nna ya, “I bikwasịjọrọ aka gị. Onye a bụ ọkpara, bikwasị aka nri gị nʼisi ya.”<verse eid="GEN 48:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 48:19"/>Ma nna ya jụrụ, sị ya, “Amaara m ihe m na-eme nwa m, Manase ga-aghọ oke obodo, ma nwanne ya nke nta ga-akarị ya ịdị ukwuu, nʼihi na ụmụ ụmụ ya ga-aghọ ọtụtụ mba dị iche iche.” <verse eid="GEN 48:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 48:20"/>Ọ gọziri ha nʼụbọchị ahụ sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 48:20">“Nʼaha gị ka Izrel ga-ekwupụta ngọzị a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 48:20">‘Ka Chineke mee gị dịka Ifrem na Manase.’ ”</para>
  <para style="m" vid="GEN 48:20">Ya mere o buru ụzọ kpọọ Ifrem tupu Manase.<verse eid="GEN 48:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 48:21"/>Mgbe ahụ, Izrel gwara Josef okwu sị ya, “Lee, mụ onwe m na-aga ịnwụ. Ma Chineke ga-anọnyere unu, kpọghachikwa unu azụ nʼala nna unu ha. <verse eid="GEN 48:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 48:22"/>Mụ onwe m na-enye gị otu akụkụ ugwu karịa nke ụmụnne gị, bụ ala ugwu ahụ m sitere na mma agha m na ụta m napụta ndị Amọrait ka ọ bụrụ nke gị.”<verse eid="GEN 48:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 48"/>
  <chapter number="49" style="c" sid="GEN 49"/>
  <para style="s1">Jekọb agọzie ụmụ ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 49:1"/>Mgbe ahụ, Jekọb kpọkọtara ụmụ ya ndị ikom niile nʼotu sị ha, “Zukọọnụ ka m gwa unu ihe ga-adakwasị unu nʼụbọchị dị nʼihu.<verse eid="GEN 49:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 49:2"/>“Zukọọnụ nụrụ, ụmụ ndị ikom Jekọb</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:2">nụrụ okwu nna unu Izrel.<verse eid="GEN 49:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 49:3"/>“Ruben, ọkpara m ka ị bụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:3">ume m, ihe ngosi mbụ nke ike m,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:3">onye nsọpụrụ kwesiri, onye mbụ nʼịdị ike.<verse eid="GEN 49:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 49:4"/>Onye na-agbanwe agbanwe dịka mmiri dị nʼiyi, ị gaghị abụkwa onye mbụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:4">nʼihi na ị banyere nʼihe ndina nna gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:4">i dinara nʼihe ndina m, merụọ ya.<verse eid="GEN 49:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 49:5"/>“Simiọn na Livayị bụ ụmụnne.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:5">Mma agha ha bụ ngwa ihe ike.<verse eid="GEN 49:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 49:6"/>Ka obi m ghara isonye nʼizuzu ha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:6">ka m ghara isonye nʼọgbakọ ha,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:6">nʼihi na ha gburu mmadụ nʼoge iwe ha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:6">bipụkwa nkwonkwo ụkwụ ụmụ ehi na-echeghị echiche.<verse eid="GEN 49:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 49:7"/>Ihe a bụrụ ọnụ ka iwe ha bụ, nʼihi na ọ dị njọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:7">Ọnụma ha, ọ jọbigara njọ oke.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:7">Aga m ekesa ha nʼetiti ụmụ Jekọb</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:7">Kpasaa ha nʼetiti ndị Izrel.<verse eid="GEN 49:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 49:8"/>“Gị, Juda, ụmụnne gị ga-eto gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:8">Aka gị ga-adị nʼolu ndị iro gị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:8">Ụmụ ndị ikom nna gị ga-akpọ isiala nye gị.<verse eid="GEN 49:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 49:9"/>Ị bụ nwa ọdụm, gị, Juda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:9">i si nʼịchụ nta lọta, nwa m.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:9">Dịka ọdụm, ọ na-amakpu, na-edina ala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:9">dịka nne ọdụm, onye ga-anwa anwa kpọtee ya?<verse eid="GEN 49:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 49:10"/>Mkpanaka eze agaghị esite nʼebe Juda nọ wezuga onwe ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:10">maọbụ mkpanaka onyendu esi nʼagbata ụkwụ ya pụọ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:10">tutuu ruo mgbe eze ahụ nwe ya ga-abịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:10">irube isi nke mba niile ga-abụ nke ya.<verse eid="GEN 49:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 49:11"/>Ọ ga-ekenye ịnyịnya ibu ya nʼosisi vaịnị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:11">nʼalaka kachasị mma ka ọ ga-ekenye nwa ịnyịnya ibu ya.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">49:11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Nke a na-egosipụta ịba ụba nʼebe ọ dị ukwuu, maọbụ mmadụ ịbụ ọgaranya.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:11">Ọ ga-asakwa uwe ya na mmanya.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:11">Uwe mwụda ya ka ọ ga-asụkwa nʼọbara mkpụrụ vaịnị.<verse eid="GEN 49:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 49:12"/>Anya ya ga-acha uhie uhie karịa mmanya vaịnị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:12">Eze ya ga-enwupụkwa ọcha karịa mmiri ara ehi.<verse eid="GEN 49:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 49:13"/>“Zebụlọn ga-ebi nʼakụkụ osimiri.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:13">Ọ ga-abụ ebe izuike nye ụgbọ mmiri.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:13">Oke ala ya ga-agbatịpụ ruo Saịdọn.<verse eid="GEN 49:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 49:14"/>“Isaka dị ike dịka ịnyịnya ibu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:14">na-amakpu nʼetiti ọgba atụrụ.<verse eid="GEN 49:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 49:15"/>Mgbe ọ hụrụ otu ebe izuike ya si dị mma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:15">hụ otu ala ya si maa mma,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:15">ọ ga-ehudata isi ya ibu ibu arụ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:15">were onwe ya nye ịrụ ọrụ ike.<verse eid="GEN 49:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 49:16"/>“Dan ga-eme ka ikpe ziri ezi rute ndị ya aka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:16">dịka otu nʼime ebo Izrel.<verse eid="GEN 49:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 49:17"/>Dan ga-adị ka agwọ dị nʼakụkụ okporoụzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:17">dịka ajụala dị nʼụzọ ọhịa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:17">nke na-ata ịnyịnya nʼikiri ụkwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:17">si otu a mee ka onye na-agba ịnyịnya dalaa azụ.<verse eid="GEN 49:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 49:18"/>“O <char style="nd">Onyenwe anyị</char>, ana m ele anya nnapụta gị.<verse eid="GEN 49:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 49:19"/>“Gad bụ onye usuu ndị o-ji-egbe-aga ga-abịakwasị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:19">ma ọ ga-alụso ha ọgụ, chụọkwa ha ọsọ.<verse eid="GEN 49:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 49:20"/>“Asha ga-esi nʼubi ya wepụta nri gbara abụba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:20">nke na-adị ndị eze mma.<verse eid="GEN 49:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 49:21"/>“Naftalị dịka nne ele a hapụrụ ahapụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:21">nke na-amụpụta ụmụ ele mara mma.<verse eid="GEN 49:21"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 49:22"/>“Dịka osisi vaịnị a kụrụ nʼakụkụ iyi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:22">nke alaka ya na-awasa rigoro nʼelu mgbidi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:22">na nke na-amị ezi mkpụrụ, otu a ka Josef dị.<verse eid="GEN 49:22"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 49:23"/>Ndị na-agbata ụta sitere nʼobi ilu lụso ya agha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:23">ha gbara ya àkụ site nʼịkpọ asị.<verse eid="GEN 49:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 49:24"/>Ma aka o ji jide ụta nke ya adaghị mba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:24">ike agwụghị ogwe aka ya,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:24">nʼihi aka Onye dị ike nke Jekọb,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:24">nʼihi Onye ọzụzụ atụrụ, Oke Nkume Izrel,<verse eid="GEN 49:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 49:25"/>nʼihi Chineke nna gị, onye na-enyere gị aka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:25">nʼihi Onye pụrụ ime ihe niile, ka ọ gọzie gị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:25">site na ngọzị nke eluigwe site nʼelu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:25">ngọzị nke osimiri dị nʼokpuru ala,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:25">ngọzị nke ara na akpanwa.<verse eid="GEN 49:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 49:26"/>Ngọzị niile nke nna gị, dị ukwu karịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:26">ngọzị niile nke ugwu ukwu mgbe ochie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:26">karịakwa ngọzị nke ugwu nta mgbe ochie,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="GEN 49:26">Ka ngọzị ndị a dị iche dịkwasị nʼisi Josef,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:26">dịkwasị nʼegedege ihu Josef, onye bụ onyendu nʼetiti ụmụnne ya.<verse eid="GEN 49:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="GEN 49:27"/>“Benjamin dịka nkịta ọhịa nke na-adọgbu anụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:27">Nʼụtụtụ, ọ na-eri anụ ọ dọgburu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="GEN 49:27">Nʼanyasị ọ na-ekesakwa ihe o gbutere.”<verse eid="GEN 49:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="GEN 49:28"/>Ndị a bụ ebo iri na abụọ dị nʼIzrel. Ihe ndị a bụkwa ihe nna ha gwara ha mgbe ọ gọziri ha, nye onye ọbụla nʼime ha ngọzị nke ruuru ya.<verse eid="GEN 49:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụ Jekọb</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="GEN 49:29"/>Emesịa, o nyere ha ndụmọdụ sị ha, “Nʼoge na-adịghị anya site ugbu a, aga m anwụ. Unu aghaghị ili m nʼebe e liri nna m ha, nʼala Kenan, nʼime ọgba ahụ dị nʼọhịa Efrọn, onye Het. <verse eid="GEN 49:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="GEN 49:30"/>Nʼime ọgba dị nʼọhịa Makipela, nke dị nso na Mamre, nʼala Kenan, ọhịa Ebraham zụtara site nʼaka Efrọn onye Het, maka ili ozu. <verse eid="GEN 49:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="GEN 49:31"/>Nʼebe ahụ ka e liri Ebraham na Sera nwunye ya. Nʼebe ahụ kwa ka e liri Aịzik na Ribeka nwunye ya. Nʼebe ahụ ka m liri Lịa. <verse eid="GEN 49:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="GEN 49:32"/>Ebraham nna nna m zụrụ ala ahụ na ọgba dị nʼime ya site nʼaka ụmụ Het.”<verse eid="GEN 49:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="GEN 49:33"/>Mgbe Jekọb kwuchara okwu ndụmọdụ ikpeazụ ndị a nye ụmụ ya ndị ikom, ọ chịkọtara ụkwụ ya nʼelu akwa, kuo ume ikpeazụ. A chịkọtara ya na ndị ya.<verse eid="GEN 49:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 49"/>
  <chapter number="50" style="c" sid="GEN 50"/>
  <para style="s1">Olili Jekọb</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="GEN 50:1"/>Josef dakwasịrị nʼihu nna ya, kwaa akwa, sutukwa ya ọnụ. <verse eid="GEN 50:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="GEN 50:2"/>Josef nyere iwu, ka ndị dibịa na-ejere ya ozi gbasie ozu nna ya. Ya mere, ndị dibịa ahụ gbasikwara Izrel. <verse eid="GEN 50:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="GEN 50:3"/>O were ha iri ụbọchị anọ ịgbasi ozu, nʼihi na nke a bụ oge o kwesiri iwe ha ime ya. Mgbe nke a gasịrị, a kwara ya nʼala Ijipt iri ụbọchị asaa.<verse eid="GEN 50:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="GEN 50:4"/>Mgbe oge iru ụjụ gafesịrị, Josef gwara ndị ụlọ Fero sị ha, “Ọ bụrụ na m ahụtala amara nʼihu unu, biko, gwaranụ m Fero otu a, sị ya, <verse eid="GEN 50:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="GEN 50:5"/>‘Nna m mere ka m ṅụọra ya iyi mgbe ọ na-anwụ, sị, “Lee, agala m ịnwụ, ị ga-eli m nʼili m, nke m gwuuru onwe m nʼala Kenan.” Ugbu a, biko ka m gaa lie nna m, ma lọghachikwa.’ ”<verse eid="GEN 50:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="GEN 50:6"/>Fero zara sị ya, “Gaa lie nna gị dịka o mere ka ị ṅụọ iyi na ị ga-eme.”<verse eid="GEN 50:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="GEN 50:7"/>Ya mere, Josef gara ili nna ya. Ọtụtụ ndị mmadụ sokwa ya. Ndịisi ọchịchị Fero, na ndị okenye ụlọ ya, na ndị okenye a ma ama nʼala Ijipt. <verse eid="GEN 50:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="GEN 50:8"/>Ndị ọzọ bụkwa ndị ụlọ Josef niile, ụmụnne ya, na ndị ụlọ nna ya. Naanị ụmụntakịrị, na igwe ewu na atụrụ ha, na igwe ehi ha, ka ha hapụrụ nʼala Goshen. <verse eid="GEN 50:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="GEN 50:9"/>Ma ịnyịnya ụgbọ na ndị na-agba ịnyịnya, so ya gaa. Igwe mmadụ gara ije a buru ibu nke ukwuu.<verse eid="GEN 50:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="GEN 50:10"/>Mgbe ha ruru ebe ịzọcha ọka nke Atad, nʼofe ọzọ nke Jọdan, ha weere iti aka nʼobi dị ukwuu tie aka nʼobi ha nʼebe ahụ. Josef ruru ụjụ ụbọchị asaa maka nna ya nʼebe ahụ. <verse eid="GEN 50:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="GEN 50:11"/>Mgbe ndị bi nʼala Kenan hụrụ oke iru ụjụ nke ebe ịzọcha ọka nke Atad ahụ, ha sịrị, “Nke a bụụrụ ndị Ijipt iru ụjụ dị ukwuu.” Nʼihi nke a, ha kpọrọ ebe ahụ dị nso na Jọdan Ebel-Mizraim.<verse eid="GEN 50:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="GEN 50:12"/>Ụmụ Jekọb mere dịka nna ha gwara ha. <verse eid="GEN 50:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="GEN 50:13"/>Nʼihi na ha buuru ozu ya laa nʼala Kenan, lie ya nʼọgba ahụ dị nʼọhịa Makipela, nke bụ ala ubi Ebraham zụrụ dịka ala olili ozu, site nʼaka Efrọn, onye Het; nʼakụkụ Mamre. <verse eid="GEN 50:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="GEN 50:14"/>Emesịa, Josef laghachiri Ijipt ya na ụmụnne ya, na ndị niile sooro ya gaa olili ozu nna ya, ngwangwa elichara nna ya.<verse eid="GEN 50:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Josef agbaghara ụmụnne ya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="GEN 50:15"/>Mgbe ụmụnne Josef hụrụ na nna ha anwụọla, ha sịrị, “Eleghị anya Josef ga-akpọ anyị asị, kwụghachi anyị ụgwọ ihe ọjọọ niile anyị mere ya?” <verse eid="GEN 50:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="GEN 50:16"/>Nʼihi nke a, ha zipụrụ Josef ozi sị, “Nna gị nyere iwu a tupu ọ nwụọ. <verse eid="GEN 50:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="GEN 50:17"/>‘Gwa Josef sị ya, Arịọọ m gị, gbaghara ihe ọjọọ niile ụmụnne gị mere, na mmehie ha mere megide gị.’ Ugbu a, gbaghara mmehie anyị bụ ndị ohu Chineke nna gị.” Mgbe Josef nụrụ ihe ha kwuru, ọ kwara akwa.<verse eid="GEN 50:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="GEN 50:18"/>Ụmụnne ya bịakwara daa nʼihu ya, sị, “Anyị bụ ndị ohu gị.”<verse eid="GEN 50:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="GEN 50:19"/>Ma Josef sịrị ha, “Unu atụla egwu. Abụ m Chineke onye na-ekpe ikpe nke m ga-eji taa unu ahụhụ? <verse eid="GEN 50:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="GEN 50:20"/>Ọ bụ ezie na unu chere ime m ihe ọjọọ, ma Chineke chere ya ka ọ bụrụ ezi ihe, iji debe ọtụtụ ndụ dịka ọ na-eme taa. <verse eid="GEN 50:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="GEN 50:21"/>Ya mere, ụjọ atụla unu. Mụ onwe m ga-azụ unu na ụmụntakịrị unu.” Ọ kasịrị ha obi, gwa ha okwu bara ha nʼobi.<verse eid="GEN 50:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọnwụ Josef</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="GEN 50:22"/>Josef biri nʼIjipt, ya na ụmụnne ya, na ndị ụlọ ha. Josef gbara narị afọ na iri. <verse eid="GEN 50:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="GEN 50:23"/>Josef hụrụ ụmụ Ifrem, na ụmụ ụmụ ya. Ọ nọkwa ndụ hụ ụmụ Makia nwa Manase, ndị e kukwasịrị nʼikpere ya.<verse eid="GEN 50:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="GEN 50:24"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef sịrị ụmụnne ya, “Agala m ịnwụ, ma Chineke ga-abịa ileta unu. Ọ ga-esi nʼala a kpọpụta unu kpọgakwa unu nʼala ahụ ọ ṅụụrụ Ebraham na Aịzik na Jekọb iyi, na ọ ga-enye ha.” <verse eid="GEN 50:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="GEN 50:25"/>Mgbe ahụ, Josef mere ka ụmụ Izrel ṅụọrọ ya iyi sị, “Mgbe Chineke bịara ileta unu, unu aghaghị ị site nʼebe a chịkọrọ ọkpụkpụ m.”<verse eid="GEN 50:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="GEN 50:26"/>Josef nwụrụ mgbe ọ gbara narị afọ na iri. Ha gbasiri ozu ya, tinye ya nʼime igbe ozu, nʼala Ijipt.<verse eid="GEN 50:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="GEN 50"/>
